\id GEN  
\h Semtilbu 
\toc1 Semtilbu 
\toc2 Semtilbu 
\toc3 Semtilbu 
\is1 Mose Lekhabu Khatna  
\mt1 SEMTILBU  
\mt3 Semtilbu asung thu umdan  
\ip Hinkho hi ipi ham, ti thua semtilbu hin ijakai ahung kipatna thudol donbutna apen ahi. Semtil thudol tampi aseiyin: Thingphung ho le gancha ho, mihem masa pasal le numei chule Pathen mi huhhingna thudol jong ajaovin ahi. Pathen toh Noah, Abraham, Joseph le adang dang ho toh akiloi khomna thudol jong aumin ahi.  
\ip Semtilbu hi thanop umtah chule thusim suhmil theilou tampi jong ajaovin, chule hiche lekhabu hi thupi tah ahi. Ajeh chu Pathen le mihem kiguijopna thudol aseiyin honsunga kitepna suhkeh a um chule athahbeh a kilhaina toh thoa Pathen henga kipehlutna thudol jong aseiyin ahi. Semtilbu thusim ho a kon hin chonset jeh a avel vel'a kisihna toh thoa tantih nei louva Pathen tohgon lolhinna ding muchet ahi.  
\ip Pathen'in vannoi leiset le asunga um thil jouse ana sem chai phat chun aven pha asa lheh jenge, ahin vannoiya chonset ahung luttan; chuin Pathen thilsem ho jouse chu asesoh tai, hichun Pathen'in huhdohna dingin tohgon khat ahin neiyin ahi. Chule Semtilbu hin, Vannoi leiset semtil'a pat Israel chate Egypt gam ahung lhun chan gei ule, nam khat ahung lhin chan gei'u ahop in hichu 1800 BC vel ahi.  
\is1 Lekhabu jihpa, akijih kum chule koi henga ajih ham?  
\ip Semtilbu hi Mose'n 1446-1406 BC sunga anajih ahi. Hiche hi, vannoiya mijouse phatthei achan theina diuva anajih ahi (Gen 12:3).  
\c 1  
\s1 Leiset le mihem kisem  
\p
\v 1 \x + \xo 1:1 \xt \x*Pathen'in Semtilin van le leiset asem tai.  
\v 2 Leiset chu agong bei le ahomkeu ahin, muthim chun twipi thuh tah chu akhukhum ahin, Hiche twipi chung'a chu Pathen Lhagao chu ana lhale ahi.  
\v 3 Pathen'in; “Vah hung umhen,” atin, Vah chu aumtai. \x + \xo 1:3 \xt 2 Crth 4:6\x*  
\v 4 Pathen'in vah chu aven pha asah e. Chule Pathen'in vah chu muthim a kon'in asep khen tai.  
\v 5 Pathen'in vah chu sun asah in muthim chu jan asah tai. Hiche apat chun nilhah le jingkah ahung umdoh tan hichu nikho masa pen ahung hitai.  
\v 6 Hichun Pathen'in aseiyin, “Twipi sukhen dingin, vanthamjol hung kidal hen lang Van, twipi le leiset twipi chu alang alang ah sukhen hen,” atin. \x + \xo 1:6 \xt 2 Pet 3:5\x*  
\v 7 Hiti chun asei bangin aum in, van twipi le leiset twipi chu alang alang ah asukhen tai.”  
\v 8 Pathen'in onghom chu vanthamjol asah in, hichun nilhah le jingkah achedoh kit in ahileh nikho nina ahitai.  
\v 9 Chule Pathen'in aseiye, “Vantham jol'a twi um jouse chu mun khat a kikhol khom hen lang chule tolgo lai um doh hen,” ati. Asei bang chun aum jeng tai.  
\v 10 Pathen'in tolgo lai chu leiset asah in chule twi jouse kikhol na mun chu twikhanglen asah e. Pathen'in aven pha asa lheh jengin ahi.  
\v 11 Chuin Pathen'in aseiye, “Leiset in hamphung ho, amu nei hamphung, agathei hamhing chi chom chom leh thingphung aga amunei ho, hiche ho chun ama ama chi dungjui cheh ahin sepdoh kit diu ahi,” ati. Hiti chun ahung kehdoh tauve.  
\v 12 Leiset a hamphung thingphung ama ama chi dungjuijin ahung kehdoh in, agathei amu nei thingphung ama ama chi dungjuijin ahung kehdoh tauvin ahi. Pathen'in aven pha asalheh jengin ahi.  
\v 13 Nilhah khat le jingkah khat achekit in nithum alhing tai.  
\v 14 Chuin Pathen'in aseiye, “Sun le jan sepkhen dingin vanthomjol'a avah thei vahho hung kigol uhenlang, hiche ho chu kum kihei chin melchihnan jong, nikho simtoh nan jong chule kum simtoh nan jong pang'u hen.  
\v 15 Chujongleh hiche ho chu van'a vanthamjol'a kon'in leiset salvah-in pang uhen,’’ atin ahileh, hiti chun aumtai.  
\v 16 Hiche achun Pathen'in vah alen cheh ni asemin, vah alenjo chu sunlaiya thunei dingin apansah-in, chule vah aneojo chu janlaiya thunei dingin apansah tai; hiti chun ahsi ho jong ahin sem tai.  
\v 17 Pathen'in vahho chu vanthamjol'a pat in leiset salvah din apansah tai.  
\v 18 Sunlaiya thunei ding, janlaiya thunei ding, chule khovah le muthim sepkhen dingin apansah tan ahi. Pathen'in aven ahileh pha asa lheh jengin ahi.  
\v 19 Hichu nikho li alhin ni ahi.  
\v 20 Pathen'in aseiye, “Twija kon'in nga ho leh ganhing ahingthei dang ho umhen, chuleh vanthamjol'a jong vachate ajat kimsoh in hung leng leu hen,’’ati.  
\v 21 Hiti chun Pathen'in twikhanglen'a ganhing ahing thei jouse ahon'a kijot le dingin asemin, hiche ho chun twi a kidil sah sah uvin, ama ama jat cheh in alha uvin ahi, chujongleh ajat jat in alhanei vachate jong asemin ahi. Hichu Pathen'in aven pha asalheh jengin ahi.  
\v 22 Pathen'in abonchauvin phatthei aboh in, “Hinpha uvin lang chule pung uvin, twikhanglen'a twi lah dimset uvin, chule leiset chunga vachate jong pung uhen,’’ ati.  
\v 23 Chuin nilhah khat le jingkah khat achen ni nga lhinna ahitai.  
\v 24 Chuin Pathen'in aseiye, “Leiset in ama a kon'in sa jat chom chom hin hingdoh hen! Ama ama jat dungjui cheh in, vah ngoi thei gancha, tol'a kithol ganhing leh gamsa ho jong hihen” ati. Hiti chun aum jeng tai.  
\v 25 Chuin leiset chunga gamsa ho ama ama jat cheh in chule gancha ho jong ama ama jat cheh in a-opma kithol ajat jat in asem e. Pathen'in hiche ho chu aven pha asa lheh jengin ahi.  
\v 26 Hichun Pathen'in aseiye, “Eihon mihem ho, eiho lim pu'in sem'u hitin. Amaho chu twikhanglen sunga nga ho jouse chunga thunei diu, vanlai jol'a leng le vacha ho chule vah ngoi thei gancha ho le gamsa ho, chule a op a kithol chengse chung'a thunei vaihom in pang uhen,” ati.  
\v 27 \x + \xo 1:27 \xt Matt 19:4; Mk 10:6\x*Hiti chun Pathen'in ama lim mong mong in mihem chu asemin, Pathen lim tobang banginama lim chu asem tai, pasal le numei asem doh tan ahi. \x + \xo 1:27 \xt Semtilbu 5:1,2\x*  
\v 28 Pathen'in amani chu phatthei aboh in amani jah a aseiye, “Chipha lhonin chule pung jing lhonin simsen louvin leiset chung hinlo dimset un, chule nangni noiya vaihomna umhen, vanlaijol a leng vachate chunga jong chule twikhanglen'a ahingthei jouse chunga hijongleh aboncha ganhing namkim hihen chule leiset chunga lhale ganhing jouse hile achung uva thunei vaihom in pang lhon tan,’’ ati.  
\v 29 Pathen'in hitin jong seiye, “Ve lhonnin keiman leiset chunga muchi gathei phung jouse le thingphung gathei jouse aboncha hi nangni kihinso theina dinga kapeh lhon nahitai.  
\v 30 Chule leiset chunga um gamsa jouse hihen chunga leng vachate ho hijongleh tol'a aop'a kithol ganhing jouse hijongleh ahaithei hinna nei jousen aneh ding uva hamhing jouse kapeh doh ahitai,’’ atile, hitobang chun aumtai.  
\v 31 Chuin Pathen'in asemsa chengse chu abonchan aven, “Apha lheh jengin ahi,” hichea chun nilhah le jingkah khat ahung um doh in nigup lhinni ahung hitai.   
\c 2  
\p
\v 1 Hiti chun van le leiset chule asunga thil um jouse chu loupi tah a sem chai ahitai.  
\v 2 \x + \xo 2:2 \xt Heb 4:4,10\x*Hichun nisagi lhin nin Pathen'in athilsem chu abonchan achaiyin, hiti chun a thilsem ho jouse a kon'in ama akicholdo tai. \x + \xo 2:2 \xt Potdohbu 20:11\x*  
\v 3 Hiche nisagi lhinni chu Pathen'in phatthei aboh in chule atheng ahi tin aphongdoh tai, ajeh chu athilsem le anatoh jousea kon'a akicholdo ni ahi.  
\v 4 Hiche hi van le leiset ahung kisemdoh a akhanggui hung kipatdoh dan ho chu hiti hi anahi. Pathen'in leiset le van ahinsem patni chun,  
\v 5 Leiset chunga tollhang a jong hamphung keh doh loulai ahi. Ajeh chu Pathen'in gotwi leiset chunga ajuhsah loulai ahin chule hia chu koima natong ding umlou lai anahi.  
\v 6 Ahin leiset a kon'in twimei ahung kaiyin chule leichung jouse chu twiyin achap nouvin ahi.  
\v 7 Chuin Pathen'in lei chunga kon'in vutvai achun mihem asemin, chule anahhom'a hinna hu alhakhum a ahile mihem chu hinna nei ahung hitai. \x + \xo 2:7 \xt 1 Crth 15:45\x*   
\s1 Eden hon thusim  
\p
\v 8 Chuphat in Pathen'injong niso lama Eden hon aphut doh in hiche achun asem sa mihem chu akoitai.  
\v 9 Chuin Pathen'in leichung'a kon'in vetnom nom um le neh ding thingga namkim akedoh sah in ahi, chule honlai lung'a chun hinna thingphung jong chule ase le apha hetna thingphung jong akesah in ahi. \x + \xo 2:9 \xt Rev 2:7; 22:2,14\x*   
\s1 Eden hon'a vadung li ho  
\p
\v 10 Hiche Eden hon'a kon chun honlei chapnou jing dingin vadung alongin, vadung chu vadung li in ahung long khenin vadung li asohdoh e.  
\v 11 Vadung khatna chu ahile Pishon ahin, hiche chu sana kimuna vadung ahin Havilah gam pumpia long kimvel ahi.  
\v 12 Hiche gam'a sana kimu ho chu ahoi thei lheh in anamtui jah nom umtah chule song namtui jong akimui.  
\v 13 Vadung ni lhinna chu amin Gihon ahin, hiche vadung chu Cush gam pumpia long kimvel ahi.  
\v 14 Vadung thum lhinna chu ahile Tigris ahin, hiche vadung hi sah solam gam'a Asshur gam pumpia long ahin, chule vadung li lhinna chu Euphrates ahi.  
\v 15 Chuin Pakai Pathen'in ami semdohpa chu Eden honsunga apuilut in hiche hon'a natong ding le avetup dingin apansah tai.  
\v 16 Ahin Pathen'in mipa kom'a athupeh chu, “Nangman hiche honsunga theiga ho khu nadei dei naneh thei cheh ahi.  
\v 17 Hinlah nangman hon lailung'a ase le apha hetna theiga vang naneh lou beh ding, hichu naneh nini, nathi teitei ding,’’ ahi.  
\v 18 Chujongleh Pathen'in aseiye, “Mihempa achanga aum hi apha poi hijeh chun keiman aum khompi ding khat sempeh ing kate,’’ ati.  
\v 19 Chuin Pathen'in leivui chu leingan asosah in lei chunga ganhing namkim asemin chule vacha ho chung lam'a alensah in chuin hiche ho jouse hi amin ipi pi asah em tin mihempa kom'a ahinpui khom in hiche a mihem pan aminvona jouse chu tuni geiya amin a pang den ahitai.  
\v 20 Hiti chun mihempa in ganhing namkim chu aminvo cheh in, chunga lengthei vachate ho leh gamsa jouse jong aminvo sohkeiyin ahi. Ahinlah mihempa kithopi ding akimu doh hih laiye.  
\v 21 Hijeh chun Pathen'in mihempa chu a imutmil sah in a imutmil kah chun Pathen'in anahgu khat aladoh in anung chu aphe in atomjol peh in ahi.  
\v 22 Chuin Pathen'in Adam nahgu alah doh a kon chun numei khat asemdoh in amanu chu Adam kom'a ahin puilut in ahi.  
\v 23 Hichun mihem pan aseiye, “Amanu hi keima gu akon'a kisemdoh ahin, chule aphevou jeng jong keima phevou ahin, amanu hi tu apat a numei kiti ding ahi, ajeh chu amanu hi pasal'a konna kiladoh ahi,” ati.  
\v 24 Hijeh a chu pasal in anu le apa adalhah aji a beh ding chule amani chu tipum khat kiti lhon ding ahiye. \x + \xo 2:24 \xt Matt 19:5; Mk 10:7,8; 1 Crth 6:16; Eph 5:31\x*  
\v 25 Ahin hiche pet chun pasalpa ahin numeinu ahin ani gel lhon a sagoh keuva um lhon ahin, ahi vangin jachatna anei lhon pon ahi.   
\c 3  
\s1 Mihem chonsetna alhah  
\p
\v 1 Pakai Pathen thilsem jouse lah a gul hi alungthim thempen ahi. Nikhat chu aman numeinu adongin, “Pathen'in honsunga theiga jouse naneh thei lhon lou beh ding ahi tia asei mong em?” ati. \x + \xo 3:1 \xt Rev 12:9; 20:2\x*  
\v 2 Numei nu chun gul jah a keini'n “Eden honsunga theiga jouse kaneh thei lhon ding ahi nai.”  
\v 3 Ahin Pathen'in hitin aseiye, “Hon lailung a theiga vangkhu naneh lhon louhel ding, lo jong nalo lhon louhel ding ahi. Ahin iti ham khat a nalo lhon a naneh lhon le nathi jeng lhon ding ahi,” tin aseiye.  
\v 4 Hinlah Satan in numeinu jah a aseiyin, “Nathi lhon loubeh ding ahi.  
\v 5 Ajeh chu Pathen'in ahet ahi hichu naneh nini lhon le namit lhon hung hahdoh intin Pathen toh nabah lhon ding thilpha le thilse hetheiya naum lhon ding ahi ti Pathen'in ahet jeh a asei ahi bouve,” atitai.  
\v 6 Hiche a chun numei nun theiga chu aven ahile neh dinga tui chule mitvet dinga jong vetnom nom um, chule mi achihsah jeng ding jeh chun aha duchat cheh tai. Hijeh chun numei nun theiga chu akilo in anetan chule a pasalpa jong them khat apen amapan jong ala in ane tai.  
\v 7 Hiche apat chun amit lhon chu ahung hahdoh in tahsa sagoh keo ahilhon chu aki hechen lhon tai. Hichun thingna akilo lhonin atahsa lhon chu akiselna lhon tan ahi.  
\v 8 Chuin nisa dai lhah lamin honsunga Pakai Pathen awgin chu ajalhonin hijeh chun hon lailung'a thinglah a chun amani tah Pakai Pathen masanga akisel mang lhon tai.  
\v 9 Ahivangin Pakai Pathen'in mihempa chu akouvin, “Adam hoiya um nahi hitam?” atile,  
\v 10 Adam in jong adonbut in “Keiman nangma honsung'a na hung chu kahen ahile ka sagoh keo kahi jeh a ka kichat a kisela kahi,” ati.  
\v 11 Hichun Pakai Pathen'in jong aseiye, koi ham nangma sagoh keova na um'e tia na seipeh a chu? Honsung'a theiga nehih in kati chu naneh hitam? atile,  
\v 12 Adam in adonbut in, “Keiman kaum khompi dinga nangman neipeh numeinu hin theiga chu themkhat eipen keiman kana netai,” ati.  
\v 13 Chuphat in Pakai Pathen'in numeinu jah a aseiye, “Nangin ipi dinga hitobang pihi nabol hitam!” atile numei nun adonbut in, “Hiche gul hin eijol jol phat a kaneh ahi bouve,” ati. \x + \xo 3:13 \xt 2 Crth 11:3; 1 Tim 2:14\x*  
\v 14 Hichun Pakai Pathen'in gul jah a, “Nangman hiche nana boldoh jeh in, ganhing jouse lah a nang hi sapset nachan ding na hinkho lhung keiya na oipoh a na kithol tho ding, chule na hinkho sunga leivui naneh ding ahi.  
\v 15 Keiman nang le numeinu chilhah kah a kidouna kakoi ding, amapa chun nangma hi na luchang avohchip a, nangman amapa kengphang na chuh peh ding ahi,” ati. \x + \xo 3:15 \xt Rev 12:17\x*  
\v 16 Pathen'in numeinu jah a chun hitin aseiye, “Keiman na naovop hahsatna kabe peh ding, naosonat gentheiya cha nahin doh ding ahi. Najipa chung'a vai nahom nom jing ding, ahi vang'a najipan nang chunga vai ahop ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 17 Chuin Pakai Pathen'in Adam jah a hitin ati, “Nangman naji thu na ngaiya naneh louhel ding ahi tia ka thupehsa theiga naneh tah jeh in nangma jeh a leiset hi sapset chang ahitai. Chule na hinkho damlai sungse a gimna le genthei thohpum pum'a neh na kihol a naneh ding ahi. \x + \xo 3:17 \xt Heb 6:8\x*  
\v 18 Chule nang doudin ling le mi-at thei jong hung kehdoh intin, chule nangma anche louhing a nakivah ding ahi.  
\v 19 Na ti-ul namaija long pum'a anneh na kihol'a na neh ding, chule nangma leiset a kisemdoh nahin leiset naleso kit ding ahiye,” ati.  
\v 20 Hichun Adam in ajinu chu amin Eve asah tai. Ajeh chu amanu mijouse hung pen dohna minu ahi tan ahi.  
\v 21 Hichun Pakai Pathen'in savun a kon'in Adam le Eve ding von akhui peh in amani chu asilpeh in ahi.  
\v 22 Hichun Pathen'in aseiye, “Tu apat a hi Adam hi eiho lah a khat tobang ahung hitan, thilpha le thilse hetheijin aumtai, chule tunjong aman hinna thingphung ga khu kilo intin hin ne lhon leh tonsot a hing den ding ahitai ati.” \x + \xo 3:22 \xt Rev 22:14\x*  
\v 23 Hiche a pat chun Pakai Pathen'in Amani chu Eden hon a kon'in anodoh in, Chuleh Adam chu ahung kisemdohna leiset loulhou dingin asoldoh tan ahi.  
\v 24 Hiti chun Pathen'in Adam anodoh jouvin, Eden hon nisolam'a hinna thingphung ngah dingin vantil Cherub chu achen sah in, chule chemjam kou jeju chu akipei kimvel le sahtan ahi.   
\c 4  
\s1 Cain le Abel  
\p
\v 1 Chujouvin Adam le Eve akitimat lhonin ahile Eve in nao ahin vop in Cain chu ahung peng tai, hiche a chun amanu'n hitin aseiye, Pathen phatthei bohna jal in cha pasal khat kanei tai ati.  
\v 2 Phat chomkhat jou chun Eve chun chapa Abel ahing kit tai, hichun khonungin chapang teni chu ahung khanglen lhon tan, Abel chu kelngoi ching in ahung pang in, Cain vang chu loubol mi ahung hitan ahi.  
\v 3 Phat phabep jouvin Cain in alousohga alhun phat in alousohga phabep ahin pon Pathen a dingin kilhaina ahung sem tai.  
\v 4 Hitobang ma chun Abel in jong akelngoi lah a apeng masa athao pen tah khat chu Pathen a dingin ahin pedoh tai, Hichun Pathen'in Abel lam joh aven athilto jong kipah tah in asanpeh tai. \x + \xo 4:4 \xt Heb 11:4\x*  
\v 5 Hinlah Pathen'in Cain thilto maicham chu asanpeh tapoi, hijeh chun Cain chu hatah in alunghang in akaiku jengin ahi.  
\v 6 Hiche phat chun Pathen'in Cain jah a, “Ibola nang le nang ki lunghannahi ham? Chule ibola namai thim jeng a ham?  
\v 7 Thilpha bol dinga kilom ho chu nabol le na kisan pehda ding ham? Ahin thilpha bol dinga kilom ho chu na bolnom louleh kichih theiyin chonset nan naval lhum ding ahitai. Hiche ho hi na chinpha ding joh ahi,” ati.  
\v 8 Nikhat chu Cain in asopipa Abel jah a “Eini thinglhang lam'a che hite atin, gamlang agei lhon phat in Cain chu asopipa Abel chunga achun athat tai.” \x + \xo 4:8 \xt Matt 23:35; Lk 11:51; 1 Jn 3:12\x*  
\v 9 Phat chomkhat jouvin, Pakaiyin Cain jah a, “Nasopipa Abel hoiya um hitam?” atile Cain'in jong adonbut in, “Kahepoi, Keima hi ka sopipa Abel ching tup kahim?” ati.  
\v 10 Hichun Pathen'in jong Cain jah a “Ipi nabol hitam? Na sopipa Abel thisan chu tol'a kon'in keima angsung gei in ahung peng in ahi. \x + \xo 4:10 \xt Heb 12:24\x*  
\v 11 Hijeh chun tu apatna nangma hi leiset chunga sapsetna noija uma nahitai, na sopipa Abel thisan in na chup ahitai.  
\v 12 Leiset a konna nangma dinga ga imacha pung ding ahi tapoi, itobanginnatong jong lechun nangman leiset a in mun neilou gamvah mangpa na kiti ding ahi.”  
\v 13 Chuphat in Cain chun Pathen henga aseiye, “Keima gotna kachan hi kei thoh jou hoi ahipoi.  
\v 14 Vetan tunin nangma a kon'in neidel mangtai, nangin lei chunga umna neilou nei hisah tai, tu apat a hi koi hijongleh eitoh khapen pen chun eitha ding ahitai.”  
\v 15 Pathen'in adonbut in, “Ahipoi koi tobang nangma hinkho sumang dinga kigo a aum le keiman ama chunga sagi vei ka phulah ding ahi.” Hichea chun Pathen'in Cain chu koiman atha louna dingin Cain chunga melchihna khat akoipeh in ahi.  
\v 16 Hichea kon chun Cain in Pathen kom adalhan Eden niso lam a Nod mun'a chun acheng tai.   
\s1 Cain chilhah ho  
\p
\v 17 Cain chun ajinu aki timatpin ahile nao ahin vop kit tan hiche nao chu Enoch ahi. Chuin Cain in phat phabep jouvin khopi khat ahinsem doh in, achapa min aput sah in hiche khopi min chu Enoch asah tai.  
\v 18 Enoch in chapa Irad ahingin, Irad chun Mehujael ahingin, Mehujael chun Methushael ahingin, Methushael chun Lamech ahing'e.  
\v 19 Lamech chun ji ni aneiyin amasa nu chu ahile Adah ahin chule anina nu chu Zillah ahiye.  
\v 20 Adah in Jabal ahingin, ama hi ahiye, khoilupon in a chenga gancha chingho dinga apau chu.  
\v 21 Chule asopi pa min chu Jubal ahin, ama chu lathem gosem mut them masa pen ahiye.  
\v 22 Zillah jong chun Tubal-cain ahingin, ama chun manchah ding abonchan sum-eng jong thih jong ahin kheng'e. Chule Tubal-cain chun sopi numei khat aneiyin amin Naamah ahi.  
\v 23 Chujouvin nikhat chu Lamech chun ajite ni jah a hitin aseiye , “Vo Adah le Zillah ka aw kasei ngai lhonin, ‘Ajeh chu pasal khat in eimavo jeh in ka that in gollhang khat in eiden jeh in ka that tai.  
\v 24 Koi tobang mikhat in Cain chu atha le sagi vei gotna chang ding ahile keima hinkho lading koi tobang aum le som sagi vei gotna chang ding joh ahiye.”   
\s1 Seth chillhah ho  
\p
\v 25 Chuin Adam chun ajinu akitimatpi kit in ahile amanun chapa khat ahing kit in, amin Seth asah tai; ijeh inem itile amanun hitin aseiye, “Pathen'in chapa eipeh kit hi Abel khel a ei kipe ah ahi, ajeh chu Cain thapa khel dingin eipe tai,” ati.  
\v 26 Seth chu mipi lhing ahung hiphat in chapa khat aneiyin amin Enosh asah e. Hiche apat chun mipi hon Pathen chu amin pan in ahou pan tauvin ahi.   
\c 5  
\s1 Adam chilhah ho  
\p
\v 1 Hiche ho hi Adam te insung khanggui umdan kijihna lekhabu ahi. Pathen'in mihem asem chu ama lim tobang din asemin ahi. \x + \xo 5:1 \xt Semtilbu 1:27,28\x*  
\v 2 Pathen'in numei le pasal ana semdoh in aman amisem doh teni chu phatthei aboh in chuin amani chu mihem asah tai. \x + \xo 5:2 \xt Matt 19:4; Mk 10:6\x*  
\v 3 Adam chu kum jakhat le kum somthum alhinin ama lim le ama mel to kilou cha khat ahingin hiche pa chu amin Seth asah tai.  
\v 4 Seth apen jou chun Adam chu kum jaget tobang ahin be kit in, chu achun Adam in cha numei le pasal anei be nalaiye.  
\v 5 Adam chu kum jako le kum somthum ahing nomsel in hiche jou chun ama athi tai.  
\v 6 Seth chu kum jakhat le kum nga ahi chun ama chu Enosh pa ahung hi tai.  
\v 7 Enosh pen jou chun Seth chu kum jaget le kum sagi ahin be nalai in chu achun aman cha numei le pasal adang ahin be nalaiye.  
\v 8 Hichun Seth chu kum jako le kumsom le kumni ahingin hiche jou chun aleiset hinkho abeitai.  
\v 9 Enosh chu kum somko ahi chun ama chu Kenan pa ahung hitai.  
\v 10 Kenan pen jou chun, Enosh chu kum jaget le kum som le kum nga ahing nalaiyin chujou chun cha numei le cha pasal ahing nalaiye.  
\v 11 Enosh chu kum jako le kum nga ahingin ama athi tai.  
\v 12 Kenan chu kum som sagi alhing in ama chu Mahalalel pa ahung hitai.  
\v 13 Mahalalel pen jou chun, Kenan chu kum jaget le kum somli ahing nalaiyin, chule aman chapa dang le chanu dang jong anei be nalaiye.  
\v 14 Kenan chu kum jako le kum som gei ahingin chuin ama hinkho abeitai.  
\v 15 Hichun Mahalalel chu kum somgup le kum nga alhing in ama chu Jared pa ahung hitai.  
\v 16 Jared pen jou chun, Mahalalel chu kum jaget le kum som thum jen ahing nalaiyin chule cha pasal le cha numei tamtah ahin be nalaiye.  
\v 17 Hichun Mahalalel kum jaget le kum somko le kum nga gei ahingin hichun ama leiset hinkho abeitai.  
\v 18 Jared chu kum jakhat le kum somgup le kum ni alhin in ama chu Enoch pa ahung hitai.  
\v 19 Enoch pen jou chun, Jared chu kum jaget gei ahingin, chuban in chapa le chanu dang jong ahing nalaiye.  
\v 20 Jared chu kum jako le kum som gup le kumni ahingin, hichun ama aleiset hinkho abeitai.  
\v 21 Enoch chu kum som gup le kum nga alhin in ama chu Methuselah pa ahung hitai.  
\v 22 Methuselah pen jou kum jathum sungin Enoch chu Pathen toh kinai tah in aum jing jengin chule chapa dang le chanu dang tampi jong ahinbe nalaiye.  
\v 23 Hiti chun Enoch chu kum jathum le kum somgup le kum nga ahingin ahi.  
\v 24 Pathen toh kinai tah a um jing ahin nikhat chu ama akimu tapon Pathen'in akoudoh ahitai. \x + \xo 5:24 \xt Heb 11:5; Jde 1:14\x*  
\v 25 Methuselah chu kum jakhat le kum somget le kum sagi alhin in, ama chu Lamech pa ahung hitai.  
\v 26 Lamech pen jou chun, Methuselah chu kum jasagi le kum somget le kumni ahingin, hichun aman chapa le chanu dang tamtah anei be nalaiyin ahi.  
\v 27 Methuselah chu kum jako le kum somgup le kum ko ahingin hichun ama ahinkho abeitai.  
\v 28 Hichun Lamech chu kum jakhat le kum somget le kumni alhinin chapa khat ahingin,  
\v 29 Ama min chu Noah asah in hitin aseiye, “Pathen'in agaosapsa gim genthei thoh a ikhut uva itohgim nau hiche leiset a konna ama hin eitha olsah ding'u ahi,”ati.  
\v 30 Noah pen jou chun, Lamech chu kum ja nga le kum somko le kum nga ahingin hijou chun cha pasal le numei tamtah ahing nalaiyin ahi.  
\v 31 Lamech chu kum jasagi le kum somsagi le kum sagi ahingin, hichun aleiset hinkho abeitai.  
\v 32 Noah chu kum ja nga alhin'in, ama chun Shem, Ham, chule Japheth ahingin ahi.   
\c 6  
\s1 Namtin vaipi gitlouna  
\p
\v 1 Hiche achun leiset chunga mihem ahung pung pan tan ahile alah uva chanu jong tampi ahing tauve. \x + \xo 6:1 \xt Job 1:6; 2:1\x*  
\v 2 Chuin Pathen chapa te chun numei hoitah ho chu amu uvin ama hon adei thei lheh jeng uvin, hijeh chun adei dei akilhen uvin ajinu dingin akipui tauvin ahi.  
\v 3 Hichun Pathen'in aseiye, “Ka lhagao mihem sunga atonsot kumkho in chengden thei deh ponte, ajeh chu ama tahsaphe bou ahin, ahin nikho jong kum jakhat le kum somni bou hi ding ahiye,” ati.  
\v 4 Hiche lai chun leiset chunga Nephilim miho ana um uvin, chujongleh Pathen chapa te mihem Chanute henga ahunglut nung'u chun ama hon jong cha ahin peh tauve; hiche ho chu khanglui laiya mihat te ana hiuvin, chule mi minthang ho chu ana hiuvin ahi. \x + \xo 6:4 \xt Minbu 13:33\x*  
\v 5 Pathen'in leiset chunga mihem ho setna chu akhol chen jingin, chule Pathen'in mihem hon thil phalou agel'u ahilou le lungthima ase abolnom ho'u chu aboncha aphalou jeng ahi chu amu doh tai. \x + \xo 6:5 \xt Matt 24:37; Lk 17:26; 1 Pet 3:20\x*  
\v 6 Hichun Pakaiyin mihem asem'a leiset chung'a aumsah hatah in akisih tai.  
\v 7 Hichun Pakaiyin aseiye, “Keiman kasem doh mihem ho hi leiset chunga kon'a ka suhmang ding ahitai, mihem jouse alen aneo, gancha alen aneo tolgo chunga lamjot thei jouse chule chunglam a leng vachate ahiuvin, ajeh chu hicheng pi kana semdoh hi ka kisih lheh tai,” ati.  
\v 8 Hinlah Noah chu Pathen lungdei lam in aum jingin ahi.   
\s1 Noah khanggui  
\p
\v 9 Hiche hi Noah le a insung mite umchan thusim ahiye, Noah chu mi chonpha, hiche khanglaiya chu leichung'a mona nei louva um chu Noah bou anahi, chule Noah chu Pathen toh ki lhakang louhel le Pathen toh kihou mat jing mi ahi. \x + \xo 6:9 \xt 2 Pet 2:5\x*  
\v 10 Noah chun chate thum aneiyin amaho chu ahi le Shem, Ham, chule Japheth ahiuve.  
\v 11 Hichun Pathen'in leiset chung ahinven ahile mihem ho phatlouna le kitahlouna jeng amudoh tan ahi.  
\v 12 Pathen'in jong thil phalou jouse le thudih louva vannoi pumpia mihemte khat cheh a jong asetnau chu amudoh sohhel tai.  
\v 13 Hichun Pathen'in Noah jah a aseiyin, “Keiman tua hi hinna neiya avahle thei jouse ka suhmang ding ahitai. Ajeh chu amaho jeh hin leiset chunga pumhat a kinona jeng adim tan ahi, vetan keiman aboncha uva leiset toh ka suhmang tha ding ahi tauve.  
\v 14 Nangman Gopher thingin kong innei lentah khat kisem inlang, kong innei sunga chun indan adan adan in khah tanin, chuteng asung le apo twilutna thei lai jouse na huhbing sohkei ding ahi.  
\v 15 Hiche kong chu tong jali le somnga sao hi ding, chule asan dan chu tong somsagi le nga a sang hi ding, chule avai lam chu tong somli le nga a len hi ding ahi.  
\v 16 Kong innei chu bangkot hong inlang achunglam chu khap som le get in sem inlang kong abanga kotpi hongin lang, indan noi nung danni lhinna, chule dan thum lhinna geiya nasem ding ahi.  
\v 17 Tun ven keiman leichung jouse hi twisanglen a ka chupsah ding, hichu ganhing ahai thei jouse ahinkho kalah mang ding ahitai. Chule leichung'a um jouse ka suhmang ding ahi.  
\v 18 Hinlah keiman nangma toh kitepna khat nei ing kating, chujou tengleh kongsunga nang nahin, na chapa te ahiuvin, najinu chule namoute toh na boncha uva kong sunga lut tauvin,  
\v 19 Chule tahsa neiya hing gamsa namkim anu khat le achal khat cheh in kongsunga hin puilut un, ajeh chu twisang hatah a ahung let teng na hinso jou theina diu ahi.  
\v 20 Vacha ho akop toni, gancha ho lah a jong ama ama jat dungjuiya, tol'a aop'a kithol tho lah a jong ama ama jat dung jui cheh a anu khat le achal khat cheh navah hing dinga na henga hung kitollut ding ahiuve.  
\v 21 Chule na suhmil theilou ding chu kong sunga naneh dingu an naneh diu ninglhingset a nakipohlut diu nakikhol khom diu ahi, ajeh chu hiche anneh ding ho chu nangho le gancha ho jouse ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 22 Hichun Noah in jong Pathen'in aseipeh bang bangin abolpan tan ahi. \x + \xo 6:22 \xt Heb 11:7\x*   
\c 7  
\s1 Twisang let  
\p
\v 1 Chuin ima jouse ahina ding bang ahijou phat in Pathen'in Noah chu ahoulimpi tai. “Nangma le na insung mite kongsunga lut tauvin ajeh chu leiset chunga mihem holah a michonpha thudih a chon nangbou nahi”ati.  
\v 2 Nangman gancha theng lah a kon'in kop sagi, kop khat a achal khat le anu khat cheh, chule gancha thenglou lah a kon a jong kop sagi ma kop khat a achal khat le anu khat cheh ki kailut inlang,  
\v 3 Chule chunga leng vachate lah a jong kop sagi cheh na puilut ding amaho lah a chu achal khat le anu khat akopto cheh a na puilut ding hichengse chu twisang let a konna nahinso theina dinga navah a chikhai dinga nahing hoi ding ahi.  
\v 4 Nisagi jouva pat go hatah a leiset chunga ka juhsah pan ding ahitai, chule go chu ni somli le jan somli sunga ka juhsah ding leiset chunga um jouse le ahing thei jouse ka suhmang hel ding ahitai,”ati.  
\v 5 Hiti chun Noah injong Pathen'in athupeh bang bang chun abonchan abolsohkei tan ahi.  
\v 6 Leiset chunga twisang ahunglet chun Noah chu kum jagup ana lhing tan ahi.  
\v 7 Hichun Noah chu achapa te toh, ajinu toh, chule amoute toh twisanglen na kon'a ahoidoh theina diuvin kong sunga alut tauve. \x + \xo 7:7 \xt Matt 24:38,39; Lk 17:27\x*  
\v 8 Satheng ho lah a ahin, sa thenglou ho lah a kon'in jong tol'a kithol tho ho lah a kon'in jong,  
\v 9 Akop kop a anu khat le achal khat cheh, Pathen'in Noah ahoulimpina bang chun kong sunga chun Noah kom'a avahlut cheh tauvin ahi.  
\v 10 Chuin nisagi lhin jou chun twisanglen go ahung jupan tan, leiset chung chu gotwi in achup tai.  
\v 11 Noah chu kum jagup alhin kum lhani lhinna ah, leinoija twi um jouse ahung put tan, chule vanthamjol apat in hatah in go alon tho tai. \x + \xo 7:11 \xt 2 Pet 3:6\x*  
\v 12 Ni somli le jan somli sungin go chu tang louhel'in hatah in ajujom jing tan ahi.  
\v 13 Hicheni tah chun Noah ahin, Noah chapa te Shem, Ham, chule Japheth ahiuvin, Noah jinu ahin, amoute thum ahiuvin abonchauvin kong sunga alut tauve.  
\v 14 Amaho ahiuvin, kong sunga um gamsa hang ahin insa gancha alen aneo chule tol'a aop'a kitholtho ho jong ama ama jat dungjui cheh in, vachate jong ama ama chilhah dungjui a vacha namkim a kon ahiuve.  
\v 15 Akop akop in amaho chun kongsung ahin jon cheh un, hichun avetsah chu ahile hinna neiya tahsa hing ahiuve ti photchetna ahi.  
\v 16 Hichu gancha ho lah a anu khat le achal khat ahung lut soh phat un Pathen'in Noah ateppeh bang chun, Pakaiyin kot akhah tai.  
\v 17 Chujouvin ni somli le jan somli sungin hatah in twisanglen chu akhang in leiset chung jouse achup tan, hichun kong chu twi in ahin potou cheh cheh tan leiset sanga sang jon alet dohtai.  
\v 18 Twi chu nasa tah in akhang tul tul jeng tan ahile kong chu twi chunga akitol le len ahi.  
\v 19 Achaina geiyin twi chun mol jouse lah a asangpen geiyin abonchan achup sohhel tai.  
\v 20 Twi chu akhanbe jingin mol jouse lah a asangpen jong chu tong som ni jen thuh-in achup manghel tai.  
\v 21 Hijeh chun leiset chunga um ahing thei ahaithei jouse, chunga leng vachate ahin, in na kivah gancha ho ahin, gam'a gamsa ho ahiuvin, ahon hon a kiloiya leiset chung'a kitol le ganhing namkim ahiuvin chule mihemte geiyin agam sohhel tai.  
\v 22 Ima jouse leiset chunga um kiti pou anahhom a hinna hu neiya haithei jouse abonchan athigam soh tan ahi.  
\v 23 Pathen'in leiset chunga thil ahing thei jouse asumang sohhel tai. Mihem ho jouse, gancha ho, ganhing gamsa ho, tolgo chunga lamjot thei jouse, chunga leng vachate jouse abonin athi sohhel tai. Ahin hichea sohcha a hing doh Noah le a insung mite chule kong sunga um ganhing anu khat le achal khat um ho bou ahiuve.  
\v 24 Hiche twisanglen chun leiset chung ni jakhat le nisom nga sung achup e.   
\c 8  
\s1 Noah sochat  
\p
\v 1 Hinlah Pathen'in Noah le gamsaho le gancha ho kong sunga um jouse ageldoh jingin, leiset chunga huipi hattah ahin nunsah in ahile twisanglen chu ahung kem lheh tai.  
\v 2 Leinoi lam a twi ho jong along kang tan, chule chunglam'a van'a konna go nasa tah a ju jong athip tan ahi.  
\v 3 Hichun twisanglen chu leiset chunga kon'in ni jakhat le ni somnga jouvin akang heihoi tan ahi.  
\v 4 Hiti chun nisom le nisagi lhinni lha sagi channa chun kong chu Ararat molchunga ahung kinga tai.  
\v 5 Lhani le akeh jouvin twi chu ahung kemtul tul'in mol dang dang ho jong molvum ahung kimu pan tan ahi.  
\v 6 Chujouvin ni somli jou chun Noah in huikot kong sunga asem chu ahin hong doh tan,  
\v 7 Hichun va-ah khat alha doh in ahile, leiset chung adung avaiyin aleng len, leiset chunga twi akan loulai jeh in ahung kinungle kit tai.  
\v 8 Chuin Noah in jong leiset chunga twi kang soh tam ti vetna dingin vakhu khat alendoh sah kit in ahi.  
\v 9 Hinlah vakhu chun kingah na ding mun amu hihlaiye, ajeh chu twijin leiset achup nahlai jeh in ahung kinungle kit in, hichun Noah in vakhu chu akhut a adomlhan kong sunga akoilut kit tai.  
\v 10 Chuin nisagi akho ngaiyin, chujouvin kong'a kon chun vakhu chu alha doh kit'a ahile,  
\v 11 Vakhu chu nilhah langin ama henglam'a ahung kile kit in, vetau amuh achun athah beh a kiloulha Olive thingna khat ahin pon, hijeh chun Noah in jong leiset chunga twipi akangsoh tai, ti ahedoh paijin ahi.  
\v 12 Chujouvin Noah jong nisagi ma akho ngai kit in vakhu chu alha doh kit in ahile vakhu chu ahung kinung le kit tapoi.  
\v 13 Noah hinkho chu kum jagup le kum khatna lha masapen, chu che lha nimasapen ni chun leiset chunga twipi abonchan akang sohhel tan, hijeh chun Noah in jong kong husin chu ahoh lhan agahven ahile leiset chung chu ana gohel tan ahi.  
\v 14 Hiti chun lhani jou don chun leiset chung hoitah in agohel tai.  
\v 15 Hichun Pathen'in ahoulimpin hitin ati,  
\v 16 “Nabon chauvin kong sunga kon chun potdoh tauvin, nangma nahin, na jinu ahin, na chapa te ahiuvin, chule na moute ahiuvin kilhon dohpi'n.  
\v 17 Tahsa a hing ganhing jouse, naum khompi ho vachate ahiuvin, gancha ho ahiuvin, leiset chunga a op'a kithol tho ho ahiuvin, hiche ho chu leiset letthe thua ahung chikhai uva, ahung hin phat uva chule ahung punjalna ding uvin hin puidoh tan,” ati.  
\v 18 Hichun Noah ahin, ajinu ahin, achapa te ho ahin amoute toh konga kon chun ahung potdoh tai.  
\v 19 Chuin gancha jouse alen aneo abonchauvin vacha ho ahiuvin ni ni in akop kop in anu khat le achal khat konga kon'in ahung potdoh un ahi.   
\s1 Thilsem ho chunga Pathen kitepna  
\p
\v 20 Hichun Noah in maicham Pathen henga asemin, hi a chun aman kipehdohna maicham pumgo thilto saho chule vacha ho amaho akipehdohna dung jui cheh in pumgo thilto dingin agouvam in ahi.  
\v 21 Chuin anamtui maicham ahung kisem jeh chun Pathen alung lhai lheh jengin hitin ama akihoulim in aseiye, “Mihem lung ngaitona hi achapan laiya kipat a hung gilou pan hita jongleh mihem jeh in keiman leiset hi gaosap kit tapong'e; chule ganhing ka semsa ho jong hi sumang kit tapong'e.  
\v 22 Iti nama jongleh leiset aum laisen muchi tuphat, chang aat phat, gam dap phat, gamsat phat, nipi lai le phalbi lai, sunlai le jan beilou ding ahi,” ati.   
\c 9  
\s1 Pathen'in Noah toh kitepna asem  
\p
\v 1 Hichun Pathen'in Noah le achapa te phatthei aboh in hitin ahoulimpi in hitin aseiye, “Cha le nao hing uvin, pung uvin lang leiset lochan sohkei uvin ati. \x + \xo 9:1 \xt Semtilbu 1:28\x*  
\v 2 Leiset chunga um sa jouse ahin chunga leng vachate jouse ahin chule gamsa a op'a kithol tho ho ahiuvin chule twikhanglen'a nga ho ahiuvin abonchauva nangho naki chat cheh dingu ahi, abon chauva nangho khut a kapeh doh ahitai.  
\v 3 Ahing theiya avahle thei jouse nangho dinga anneh a pang thei cheh ahiuve, anche louhing kapeh ma banga chu aboncha kapeh doh nahi tauve.  
\v 4 Hinlah nangman naneh theilou ding chu sahing athisan pum pum a naneh loubeh ding ahi. \x + \xo 9:4 \xt Thempu Dan 7:26,27; 17:10-14; 19:26; Danbu Ni Na 12:16,23; 15:23\x*  
\v 5 Hinlah keiman kakhol chil ding chu koi tobang khat touvin mihem hinkho asuhbeiya thisan aso le, iti ham khat a gamsan mihem atha le hiche gamsa chu thadoh pai ding chule koitobanginmihem hinkho asuhbei leh ama hinkho hitobang ma a chu suhbei ding ahiye.  
\v 6 Koitobanginmihem hinkho asuhbei le hiche mihem hinkho sumang pa chu ama hinkho jong hi tobang'a chu kisumang ding ahiye, ajeh chu Pathen'in mihem hi ama lim bang banga asem doh ahiye. \x + \xo 9:6 \xt Potdohbu 20:13; Semtilbu 1:26\x*  
\v 7 Tuhin nangho hatah in pungnuvin lang leiset le asung dimset in cha le nao hing uvin lang, pung uvin chule hinlo chan sohkei uvin,” ati. \x + \xo 9:7 \xt Semtilbu 1:28\x*  
\v 8 Hichun Pathen'in Noah le achate ahoulim pin hitin aseiye.  
\v 9 “Keiman kakitepna avel'in ka sudet nom lheh tai, nang toh na chilhah te chengse dingin jong,  
\v 10 Chule gancha nam kim nangma toh kong sunga um chengse toh vacha ho ahin, insa ho ahin, chule gamsa hang ho jouse ahin chule leiset chunga atoi thei avah thei jouse dinga hi  
\v 11 Keiman nangho toh ka kitepna ka phudohna ajeh pentah chu hiche hi ahi, tahsa a hingho twisanglen a kisumang kit louhel ding ahin, chule leiset suhmangna dinga jong twisang letna um kit louhel ding ahitai,” ati.  
\v 12 Hichun Pathen'in aseiye, “Keiman ka kitepna ka phudoh hi nangho le nalhat khom piu ganhing nam kim ho ahiuvin chule tonsot a khangguija mite ding ahin, ikah uva amelchihna hiche hi ding ahi.  
\v 13 Keiman ka semdohsa nisa vah emsel chu vantham jol'a ka koiye, hichu leiset le kei kikah a kitepna khat a um melchihna hi ding ahi.  
\v 14 Keiman meibol lhang lei chunga kahin sol teng nisa vah emsel ho chu meilhang lah a hung kilang ding ahiye.  
\v 15 Hiche phat le chun keiman nangho le ikah uva ka kitepna chu hin geldoh kit ingting, chutengleh gotwi chu tahsa hingte sumang dinga twi sanga hunglen kit louhel ding ahiye.  
\v 16 Keiman nisa vah emsel meilhang lah a kamuji tengleh Pathen le leiset chunga tahsa a ahing thei jouse kah a tonsot kumkho a dinga kitepna chu kagel doh ding ahi,”ati.  
\v 17 Hichun Pathen'in Noah ahoulim pin hitin aseiye, “Hiche hi leiset chunga tahsa ahing thei jouse toh kei kikah a kitepna ka phudoh chu amelchihna hi ding ahi,” ati.   
\s1 Noah chapa te  
\p
\v 18 Noah chate ho kong sunga kon'a hung potdoh ho chu ahileh Shem, Ham chule Japheth ahiuve, Ham kiti pa hi Canaan pa ahiye.  
\v 19 Noah chate thum ho a konna vannoi hi mihem hung dim ahi.  
\v 20 Chuin twisanglet kichai jou chun Noah in tolgo lah achun lou abol pan tan hia chun lengpi phung aphut doh tai.  
\v 21 Chujouvin nikhat chu Noah chun lengpitwi adonin ahile akham tan khoilupon buh sungah chun asagoh keovin alum tai.  
\v 22 Ham Canaan pa chun apa Noah sagoh keova aum chu amun apotdoh paiyin asopi teni aga hetsah in ahile,  
\v 23 Hichun Shem le Japheth in ponsil achoi lhonin alengkouva adom gel lhonin nunglam ngan anung toi lhonin apa akeova um chu agakhu khum lhonin, amai lhon vang ahei manggel lhonin apa akeova um amulhon poi.  
\v 24 Hichun alupna a kon'in Noah ahung khah doh phat in achapa neopen in ana limbol chu ahedoh tai.  
\v 25 Hichun Noah in aseiyin: “Canaan vang gaosap chang hen, Asopi teni henga soh jouse soh in hung pang hen,” atin,  
\v 26 Hichun Noah in hitin aseiye, “Pathen'in Shem phatthei boh maihen, ahin Canaan vang asopi soh himai hen,  
\v 27 Pathen'in Japheth gam chu hatah in kehlet peh hen, chule Japheth in Shem ponbuh sung dunga jong chen sah hen, ahin Canaan vang asopipa soh hijing maihen,” ati.  
\v 28 Twisanglen kichai jouvin Noah chu kum jathum le kum somnga ahing nalaiye.  
\v 29 Hiti chun Noah hin nikho abon bonin kum jako le kum somnga alhingin, chujouvin ama athi tai.   
\c 10  
\s1 Noah chapa te chilhah ho  
\p
\v 1 Hiche thusim ho hi Noah chapa te Shem, Ham chule Japheth chilhah thusim chu ahiye; Twisang let jou chun amaho a kon'in cha tamtah ahung punbe in ahi.  
\v 2 Japheth chilhah ho chu Gomer, Magog, Madai, Javan, Tubal, Meshech chule Tiras ahiuve.  
\v 3 Gomer chilhah ho chu Ashkenaz, Riphath chule Togarmath ahiuve.  
\v 4 Javan chilhah ho chu Elishah, Tarshish, Kittim, chule Rodanim ahiuve.  
\v 5 Hiche apat chun amaho chilhah chengse chun leiset ahin toupha pan tauvin ama ama hitheina leh aphung achang akaidol cheh in ama nam hina dol cheh in acheng tauvin ahi.  
\v 6 Ham chilhah ho chu Cush, Mizraim, Put, chule Canaan ahiuve.  
\v 7 Cush chilhah ho chu Seba, Havilah, Sabtah, Raamah, chule Sabteca ahiuve.  
\v 8 Cush kitipa hin leiset chunga mihat a hung pang masapen Nimrod chu ahing'in ahi.  
\v 9 Hiche phat laiya chun vannoiya gamleng hat sakap them pen ahung hin, chule Pathen ging tah mi jong ana hi'e, hijeh chun mihon Nimrod banga gamlen hat sakap thempen ahi tin asei uve.  
\v 10 Hichun Cush chun alenggam chu Babylon khopi sunga Babylonia tin ahin semdoh in, hiche khopi ho chu Erech, Akkad, chule Calneh ahiuve.  
\v 11 Aman hiche a kon chun Assyria ajonin hikom achun Nineveh khopi aphut doh in aban'a Rehobothir khopi ahin Calah khopi jong ahin phut doh kit e.  
\v 12 Chuban chun Nineveh le Calah khopi teni kikah achun Resen khopi aphut doh in khopi lentah ahi.  
\v 13 Mizraim chu Ludite, Anamite, Naphuhite chule Lehabite ho cheng pa ahi.  
\v 14 Pathrusi ho, Casluhi ho, chule Caphtori ho chu Philistine te hung kon dohna ho chu ahi.  
\v 15 Canaan chapa tahpen chu Sidon, Sidon chilhah te hung kon dohna ho chu ahiuvin chule Hit chilhah ho jong Canaan akon ahiuve.  
\v 16 Jebus ho, Amor ho, Girgash ho ahin,  
\v 17 Hivi teho, Arki ho, Sin ho ahin,  
\v 18 Arvad ho, Zemar ho, chule Hamath ho jouse hi ama hinsa cheh ahiuve, ahin khonungin Canaan insung kon mite chu gamtin'a akithe cheh sohkei uvin ahi.  
\v 19 Hiche apat chun Canaan gamgi chu Sidon apat Gerar lang jonin Gaza geiyin aki lhung lut peh in, Sodom lang jonin aki lhungin, Gomorrah aphan, Admah ahin phan, chule Zeboiim ahop in Lasha geiyin akilhung lut peh-e.  
\v 20 Amaho cheng hi Ham chilhah ho ahiuvin, ama ama insung dungjui le, apao dungjui le, agam dungjui chuleh ajat dungjui uva ahiye.  
\v 21 Shem chate pasal ho jouse apunbe in ama chu Japheth upa ahin, Ebel chilhah ho jouse hi Shem'a konna hung kondoh cheh ahiuve.  
\v 22 Shem chilhah ho chu ahile Elam, Asshur, Arphaxed, Lud chule Ram ahiuve.  
\v 23 Ram chilhah ho chu ahile Uz, Hul, Gether, chule Mash ahiuve.  
\v 24 Arphaxad chu Shelah pa ahin, chule Shelah chu Ebel pa ahiye.  
\v 25 Ebel chun cha ni aneiyin amasapa chu Peleg (Hichu kisuh khenna tina ahi) ahi, ijeh inem itile ama phatlai a chu vannoi chu ama ama paotho doh dungjuiya ahung umdoh laitah chu ahi, chule asopipa min chu Joktan ahi.  
\v 26 Joktan chapa chu Almodad ahin, Sheleph ahin, Hazarmaveth ahin, Jerah ahin,  
\v 27 Hadoram ahin, Uzal ahin, Diklah ahin,  
\v 28 Obal ahin, Abimael ahin, Sheba ahin,  
\v 29 Ophir ahin, Havilah ahin chule Jobab ahiuve. Amaho chengse hi Joktan chilhah cheh ahiuve.  
\v 30 Ama hon gam kivaipohna atoupha uchu Mesha apat in Sephar lang jonin ahung kilhungin, nisolam'a thinglhang gamsung geiyin ahung kilhunglut peh in ahi.  
\v 31 Amaho jouse hi Shem chilhah ahiuvin, aphung le achang, apao tho'u dungjui, agam dung jui le ajat dungjui uva Shem chilhah te ahiuve.  
\v 32 Hiche phung le chang hung kimin phah se hi Noah chate a kon'a chi le nam hung kisem doh ama gui penna dungjuiya vannoiya nam jouse hi hiche phungpi a kon'a twisanglet jouva patna hung um doh ahi.   
\c 11  
\s1 Babel insang kisah  
\p
\v 1 Phatkhat lai tah chun vannoiya mihem jousen pao khat bou ana tho uvin, apao cheng manu jong thakhat cheh ana hi.  
\v 2 Hiche lai chun miho chu nisolama kon'in ahung kichon uvin ahile Babylonia gamsunga chun phaicham mun ong lentah ahin mudoh uvin, hikom'a chun acheng tauve.  
\v 3 Hichun amaho khat le khat akihouvun, “Eihon cheh gadengu hitin goutah lheng'u hite,” akitiuvin; hiti chun song panna pang dingin cheh amang uvin, songlou dingin leingan amang uve.  
\v 4 Hichun ama hon hitin asei uve, “Hungun eihon khopi khat kisah uhitin, chule in sangtah khat atingvum vantoh kibang khat sadoh uhitin, vannoiya imin'u kithansah uhite, achuti louleh leiset chunga iki moh thethang gam ding'u ahi,” atiuve.  
\v 5 Hinlah Pakai chu mihem ten khopi asah'u le insang asah doh'u vedingin ahung kumlha tai.  
\v 6 Hichun aseiye, “Vetan mipi ho hi aki pumkhat thei lheh jeng uvin chule pao khat seh bou atho uvin, hijeh chun phat chomkhat jou tengleh amaho hin ipi hijongleh abolgot ho'u chu ajolel loubeh dingu ahi.  
\v 7 Hijeh chun hungun eiho ga kumsuh'u hitin apao'u ga suhkhen peh uhite, chutile khat le khat athusei kihet mon um tauvinte,” ati.  
\v 8 Hiti chun Pakaiyin leiset chungah abon uvin, athe cheh soh hel'in hiche apat a chu khopi insah chu hung bouiya ahiuve.  
\v 9 Hijeh a chu hiche kopi insang kisah chu Babel kiti ahi, ajeh chu Pakaiyin mipi ho lung asuhboui a paochom paochom athosah a hitia hi vannoiya ana thecheh'u ahi.   
\s1 Shem chilhah ho  
\p
\v 10 Hiche hi Shem insung mite thusim ahi e. Twisang let kum ni jouvin Shem chu atahsa kum jakhat alhing in achapa Arphaxad chu ahing'e;  
\v 11 Arphaxad apen jou chun Shem chu kum ja nga ahingin, hichun aman cha numei le pasal tamtah ahinbei.  
\v 12 Hichun Arphaxad chu kum som thum le kum nga alhinin ama chu Shelah pa ahung hitan ahi.  
\v 13 Shelah ahung pen jou chun Arphaxad chu kum jali le kum thum ahingin, chuin aman cha pasal le numei tamtah ahinbei.  
\v 14 Shelah kum som thum alhin in ama chu Eber penna pa ahung hitai.  
\v 15 Eber pen jou chun, Shelah chu kum jali le kum thum ahinbe in chuin cha pasal le cha numei jong ahin be nalaiye.  
\v 16 Eber kum som thum le kum li alhinin ama chu Peleg pa ahung hitan ahi.  
\v 17 Peleg pen jou chun Eber chu kum jali le kum somthum ahing nalaiyin, hiche jou chun aman cha pasal le cha numei tamtah ahinbe nalaiye.  
\v 18 Peleg chu kum som thum alhinin, ama chu Reu pa ahung hitan ahi.  
\v 19 Reu pen jou nungin Peleg chu kum jani le kum ko ahin be nalaiyin, cha pasal le cha numei tamtah ahinbe nalaiye.  
\v 20 Reu chu kum som thum le kum ni bou alhinin Serug penna pa ahung hitai.  
\v 21 Serug pen jou chun, Reu chu kum jani le kum sagi ahinbe nalaiyin, hiche jou chun aman cha pasal le cha numei tamtah aneibe nalaiye.  
\v 22 Serug kiti pa chu kum som thum alhinin Nahor pa ahung hitai.  
\v 23 Nahor pen jou chun Serug chu kum jani ahinbe nalaiyin, hiche jou chun aman cha pasal le cha numei phachompi ahinbe nalaiye.  
\v 24 Nahor chu kum som ni le kum ko bou alhin in Terah apeng tai.  
\v 25 Terah pen jou chun Nahor chu kum jakhat le kum som le kum ko ahing nalaiyin, hichun aman cha pasal le cha numei simsen lou ahinbe nalaiye.  
\v 26 Terah vang chu kum som sagi jen ahung lhinin Abram, Nahor, chule Haran ahin hingin ahi.   
\s1 Terah chilhah ho  
\p
\v 27 Hiche hi Terahte thusim kisei ahi. Terah chun Abram, Nahor, chule Haran pa ahin, chule Haran chu Lot pa ahiye.  
\v 28 Ahin Haran chu apa Terah thi masang'in, apenna Chaldea gam'a Ur khopi achun athitai.  
\v 29 Ahin chutobang lai chun Abram le Nahor chun ji anei gel lhonin, Abram jinu min chu Sarai ahin, Nahor jinu min chu ahile Milcah ahin, Haran chanu ahiye; (Milcah le a sopi nu Iscah chu Nahor sopi pa Haran chanute ahi lhon e).  
\v 30 Ahin Sarai chu achiing in naovop thei louvin cha hing louvin aumtai.  
\v 31 Nikhat Terah chun achapa Abram le amounu Sarai chule Haran chapa atupa Lot akipuiyin abonchauvin Chaldea gam khopi Ur a kon chun Canaan gam jon dingin ache tauve; Ahin Haran khopi ahin phah phat uvin hiche mun'a chun acheng den tauve.  
\v 32 Hichun Terah hinkho chu kum jani le kum nga alhing in, chujouvin Haran khoa chun Terah athi den tai.   
\c 12  
\s1 Pathen'in Abram akou  
\p
\v 1 Pathen'in Abram chu ana houlimpi in “Na gam, na insung mite, na sopiho chule napa sopi ho dalhan keiman gamthah ka musah ding khu jon tan,” ati. \x + \xo 12:1 \xt Act 7:2,3; Heb 11:8\x*  
\v 2 Keiman nang hi nam lentah kaso ding nahiye; chule keiman nangma phatthei kaboh ding chule namin kaki than sah ding chule midang ho phatthei channa nahi ding ahi.  
\v 3 Chule nangman phatthei naboh ho chu phatthei chang diu, chule nangman na sapset te chu ka sapset ding; chule nangma jeh a leiset chunga phung nam kim phatthei chang ding ahiuve. \x + \xo 12:3 \xt Gal 3:8\x*  
\v 4 Hichun Pathen'in athu mop dung jui chun Abram chu akichon in, chule Lot in ama aki lhonpi in. Abram chu Haran dalha a akichon doh chun akum kum somsagi le kum nga ana lhing tan ahi.  
\v 5 Aji ngaitah Sarai, asopi pa Lot, anei agou, agam jouse toh, agancha jouse, chule Haran a ana um laiya a insungmi ana kisemdoh chengse chu aki puiyin Canaan lam ajon tauve.  
\v 6 Abram in alamjotna a Shechem chu ahopa in saotah ajot un, hiche achun ngahmun Moreh thingphung kom'ah akingauvin hiche mun chu Canaan mihon ana lodimun ahi.  
\v 7 Hichun Pakaiyin Abram chu akimupi'n “Keiman hiche gam hi na chilhah te kapeh ding ahiye,” hichun Abram injong ahenga hung kilah Pakaiya dingin hiche mun'a chun maicham khat asemin ahi. \x + \xo 12:7 \xt Act 7:5; Gal 3:16\x*  
\v 8 Phat chomkhat jou chun, Abram in noilam gam ahin jon'in kingahna mun ding thinglhang lam'ah asem doh in hichu nilhum lama Bethel khopi, niso lam'a Ai khopi, akah achun ponbuh akison in akinga in, hiche mun'a chun aman Pakaiya dingin maicham khat asemin chule Pakai min'in atao tai.  
\v 9 Hichun Abram chu noilam'a ahung chalbe ben Negev lam jonin ache paiye.   
\s1 Egypt gam'a Abram le Sarai  
\p
\v 10 Hiche lai phat dontah chun Canaan gamsunga nasatah in kel alhan, Abram chu Egypt ma chelou thei ahi tapon, hikom achun Abram chu gampam mi in ana um'in ahi.  
\v 11 Abram chu ahung suh deuvin Egypt gamgi ahung lhun phat chun, Abram'in ajinu Sarai jah achun aseiyin, Sarai “Ven, nangma hi numei mel-hoitah nahi.”  
\v 12 Egypt miten namu tengu leh, ama hon hitia asei diu, “Ama hi ajinu ahi, amapa hi that doh'u hitin hiche teng chule ajinu hi eiho ichan thei ding'u ahi ati ding'u ahi!”  
\v 13 Hijeh chun nang chu kei sopinu hi kahi tin kiseijin lang hile chun kei dingin phapen intin chule nangma jal'a chu kei jong ei hinghoi ding'u ahi,” ati. \x + \xo 12:13 \xt Semtilbu 20:2; 26:7\x*  
\v 14 Thudihtah khat chu ahile Abram chu Egypt ahung lhun chun mipi ho chun Sarai chu amel-hoi chu amudoh soh tauvin ahi.  
\v 15 Chule Pharaoh lengpa chapa ten amudoh phat uvin Pharaoh kom'a amanu chu aphat sei lheh jeng tauve. Hichun Sarai chu Pharaoh insunga apuilut tauvin ahi.  
\v 16 Hichun Sarai jeh chun Pharaoh in Abram chu thil mantam tah apen, kelngoi hon ahin, bong chalte ahin, sangan chal ho ahiuvin; soh pasal hihen soh numei ho hileh, sangongsao ho ahin sangongsao api ho ahiuvin anei doh sah lotai.  
\v 17 Hinlah Pathen'in Pharaoh le a insung mite chu Abram jinu Sarai jeh chun het phahlou thoh hah tah chun abolgim lheh jeng tan ahi.  
\v 18 Hichun Pharaoh in Abram chu nasatah in ahousal in, “Ipi bol'a kingaito nahim,” atin, “I bolla na jinu ahi chu nei seipeh lou ham?”  
\v 19 Ibola ka sopinu ahi natia kaji dinga nei kipuisah ham? Hijeh chun ven tunjong hikom'a na jinu aum'e kipuiyin lang gangtah in chedoh tan!” ati.  
\v 20 Hichun Pharaoh in asemang pachong ho thu apetan, “Abram ahin ajinu ahin chule anei agou abonchan hiche gam'a kon'in gathah doh un,” ati.   
\c 13  
\s1 Abram leh Lot kikhen  
\p
\v 1 Hichun Abram'in ajinu Sarai, asopipa Lot toh, Egypt gam chu adalha uvin chunglam Negev mun lang jonin achetou tai.  
\v 2 Abram chun gancha anei lheh jeng tan, hiche keo hilouvin sana le dangka jong ahao lheh jengtan ahi.  
\v 3 Hiti chun Negev apat Bethel geiyin ahung cheng un, chuleh Bethel le Ai kikah a phat masa a ana sonjiu banginkhoilupon in asong uve.  
\v 4 Hiche mun chu ahile Abram in maicham anasem dohna mun ahin hikom achun Pathen'in avel in ana hou kit tai.  
\v 5 Lot, Abram toh kilhon jing pa jong chu ahung hao lheh tan kelngoi hon ahin kelcha hon ahin tamtah ahin nei tan chule khoilupon in jong ahin nei doh tan ahi.  
\v 6 Hinlah achen nau gam chu Abram le Lot dingin ahung neo lheh jeng tai, ajeh chu akelngoi hon ho le kelcha hon ho ahin gancha dang ho aum khom thei tapouve.  
\v 7 Hijeh chun Abram le Lot gancha chingho kahlah a kihet khelna ahung um doh tan hiche phatlai chun Canaaan mite le Periz mite jong ana cheng khom uve.  
\v 8 Achaina keiyin Abram in Lot jah a hitin aseiye, “Eini kiheto themsel hite nangma le kei gancha ching ho kahlah a, ajeh chu eini hi kinaicha ihi bouve.  
\v 9 Ven na masanga gam-ong lenpitah hi nanga ahiye, nangman kilhen in hoilam hi nadei ham kilhen in ikihop ding ahi. Leiset gam ong veilam nadei le keiman gam ong jetlam kaki lah ding, nangman jetlam aphajoi nati le keiman na dei lou lang chu kaki lhen mai ding ahitai,” ati.  
\v 10 Lot chun phat sottah gam chu aven gam pha leithao potna mun Jordan phaicham lang chu Zoar lang toh kinai lang deu, hilang chu ahile aphat seh a twiyin achapnou na mun gam Pakai honlei tobang twi chap nou jing ahilouleh Egypt te honlei banga hoitah ahi. Hiche phatlai chu Pakaiyin Sodom le Gomorrah asuhmang masang ana hi. \x + \xo 13:10 \xt Semtilbu 2:10\x*  
\v 11 Hijeh chun Lot in jong Jordan vadung phaicham pumpi chu akilhen in, hiti chun Lot chu niso lam jonin akitol tai; hitobang hin amani aki inkhen lhon tan ahi.  
\v 12 Hichun Abram Canaan gam'a cheng din aumtai. Chua chun Lot in ama khoilupon buh chu Sodom gam toh kinai phaicham geiyin aga songdoh peh in ahi.  
\v 13 Hinlah hiche Sodom mite chu aphamo thei lheh un, chule agilou thei lheh un Pakai douna in akisa chavai lheh un ahi.  
\v 14 Lot apotdoh jou phat in Pakaiyin Abram chu ahoulimpi in, “Vetem in namit a namu phah chan gam ninggei achunglam anoilam, solam le lhumlam.  
\v 15 Keiman nangma hiche gam jouse namit a namu phah jouse nangma le na chilhah te jouse tonsot a nei le gouva kapeh nahitai. \x + \xo 13:15 \xt Act 7:5\x*  
\v 16 Keiman nason na chilhah te chu leiset a leivui jat ka phahsah ding, leiset leivui jat sim joulou banga nang son le chilhah te jong simjou lou ahi bouve.  
\v 17 Hijeh chun kipatdoh inlang agamsung hi adung avai asuh atungin ga kholtoh in, ajeh chu ken nangma kapeh ding ahi.”  
\v 18 Hichun Abram'in aumna chu Hebron mun a achon in gangpithing kena kom Mamre kiti mun chu ahi. Chule Abram in hiche mun'a chun Pakaiya dingin maicham khat asemin ahi.   
\c 14  
\s1 Abram in Lot ahuhdoh  
\p
\v 1 Hiche phat laitah chun gal kinah kiboina ana um'in, hiche a ana kiboi ho chu ahile Babylon lengpa Amraphel, Arioch lengpa Ellasar, Kedorlaomer lengpa Elam, chule Goiim lengpa Tidal ahiuve.  
\v 2 Chule akidoupi ho'u chu Sodom gam lengpa Bera, Gomorrah lengpa Birsha , Admah lengpa Shinab, Zeboiim lengpa Shemeber, chule Bela lengpa (Zoar kitipa) ahiuve.  
\v 3 Hiche anunung'a lengho hi Siddim phaicham (twithi kol phaicham) a apang un ahi.  
\v 4 Kumsom le kumni sung'a amaho hi Kedorlaomer lengpa noiya ana kun jing'u ahin, amavang kum som le kum thum lhin kum'in adouvin ahung pang tauve.  
\v 5 Kum khat jou chun Kedorlaomer lengpa le ama pankhompi lengho chu ahung kon uvin, Rephaim mite chu Ashteroth-Karnaim achun ajou un, Zuz mite chu Ham achun ajou un, Emim mite chu Shaveh-kiriathaim achun anajou un,  
\v 6 Chule Hor mite chu amolsangu Seir apat gamthip lang gamgi El-Paran chan geiyin aga joupeh uvin ahi.  
\v 7 Hichun amaho hikom'a kon chun (Kadesh kiti) a akinung lekit uvin , tuhin En-mishpat achun Hazazon-tamar a cheng Amor mite leh Amalek mite chu agamsung pumpin ajou tauve.  
\v 8 Hichun leng phalou akiphin ho sese chu Sodom, Gomorrah, Admah, Zeboiim, chule Bela (Zoar kitipa) galkon din akigong un twipi-thi phaicham achun gal asat uvin,  
\v 9 Elam gam lengpa Chedorlaomer le Goiim lengpa Tidal toh, Babylon lengpa Amraphel toh chule Arioch lengpa Ellasar chutoh akisat uvin, hicheng leng li ho chun leng nga ho chu anadou un ahi.  
\v 10 Amaho se gal akisat jou uchun Twipi-thi kol phaicham achun thih e meichang adim jengin ahi. Hichun Sodom lengpa le Gomorrah lengpa sepai ho chu ajamdoh un, amaho loi khat chu kotong sunga alut un, amaho lah a loikhat chu thing lhang lama ajam cheh tauve.  
\v 11 Gal hangsan mihat ho chun Sodom le Gomorrah alonkhum un gal manchah ho jouse chule neh le chah ho jouse akichom khomun ache tauve.  
\v 12 Amaho chun Lot, Abram sopipa jong chu aman uvin Sodom a chengpa chu anei thil le gou jouse jong alahpeh tauve.  
\v 13 Hinlah Lot insung mite khat ana sohcha in, amapa chun Abram Hebrew mipa aga seipeh tai, hiche lai chun Abram chu Eshcol le Aner sopipa, Amor mi Mamre gangpi thingphung vel dunga chun ana cheng nalaiye, amaho jong chu Abram toh ana pangkhom ahiuve.  
\v 14 Hichun Abram in asopipa Lot kimat ajahdoh phat chun aman tohgon ahin neitan, mihem jathum le som le get phatah a galbol kithem chuhsa ama insunga peng cheh ahin lhengdoh in ama tah in alamkaiyin amaho chu Kedarlaomer sepai ho chu Dan geiyin aga nungdel peh in ahi.  
\v 15 Hichun Abram in amaho chu ahom khenin jankim laitah in abulu'un Kedarlaomer sepai ho chu ajam cheh tauve, Abram in amaho sepai ho chu gamla tah in anojam'in Damascus khopi sah lang Hobah chan geiyin agadel peh-uvin ahi.  
\v 16 Hiti chun Abram injong asopipa Lot jong, athilkeo chengse toh, numeiho ahiuvin mipi ahiuvin abonchan ahin nungpui soh tai.  
\v 17 Abram chun Kedarlaomer chuleh apankhom pi leng ho aga jo a ahung kinungle lam chun Sodom lengpan Shaveh phaicham (Shaveh tichu lengpa phaicham tina ahi), achun alamto dingin ahunge.  
\v 18 Hichun Melchizedek Salem lengpa chule Pathen Thempu Chungnungpen a pang pan Abram chu lengpitwi chuleh changlhah ahin pohpeh e. \x + \xo 14:18 \xt Heb 7:1-10\x*  
\v 19 Melchizedek in Abram chu hiti hin phatthei aboh in hitin aseiye, “Van le leiset hin phutdoh a Pathen chungnung pen kom'a, Abram phattheiboh chang hen,  
\v 20 Chule nagalte nangma khut lum'a lousah a, chungnungpen Pathen chu loupi hen,” ati. Chuin Abram in Melchizedek chu thil jousea kon'in hopsom a hopkhat khat apesoh keiye.  
\v 21 Sodom lengpan Abram jah a hitin aseiye, “Kanam mite na hentup ho chu nei nungpeh tan, amavang thilkeo ho chengse nangin na matdoh ho vang chu nangma adin na kikoi theiye,” atile,  
\v 22 Abram in Sodom lengpa hitin adonbut in, “Van le leiset hin phutdoh Pakai Pathen chungnung pen kom'a kakihahsel ahitai,  
\v 23 Keiman patse jangkhat cha hihen lang, kengchot khao jeng cha hijongleh nang thil kiti poupou khatcha kalah louhel ding ahi, nangman Abram ka haodoh sah tai,” tia nasei thei louna dingin;  
\v 24 Ahin keiman kalah ding chu gollhang hon aneh doh ule mihon ana nehchai ho bou chu ahi, chule keiman ka deilhen pentah chu ahile achan ding uva kilom thil le gouho chu kaloi kamite Aner, Eshcol chule Mamre amaho petan.   
\c 15  
\s1 Abram kom'a Pakai kitepna  
\p
\v 1 Phat chomkhat jou nung hin, Pakaiyin gaovin Abram akihoulimpin hitin aseipeh e. “Abram imacha kicha hih in, ajeh chu keiman kahuh ding, kipaman jong atam a tam na chan ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 2 Abram in adonbut in, “O Pakai, loupipen nangma phatna na phatthei ho hi keiman chapa kaneipoi, ajeh chu nangman chapa nei pehlou jeh in, ka insunga soh a pang, Eliezer Damascus amapa bou hin ka gou alo ding joh in aumtai.  
\v 3 Nangman keima chilhah ding a chikhai ding, neipe tapon, hijeh a chu ka sohte lah a khat hin ka gou alo ding ahitai.  
\v 4 Pakaiyin ama chu ahoulim pin, “Ahipoi, nangma soh hon na gou alo ahi, nangma a konna chapa um ding ama chun na gou alo ding ahi.”  
\v 5 Hichun Pakaiyin Abram chu polama akoudoh in akihou pin, “Vanchung lam ven Ahsi ho khu simtem in nasim jou nah em. Hitobang chu ahi na chilhah atam ding dan chu,” ati. \x + \xo 15:5 \xt Rm 4:18; Heb 11:12\x*  
\v 6 Chuin Abram in jong Pakai tahsan na dihtah in aneitan ahile hichu ama dingin dihchan nan akisimpeh tai. \x + \xo 15:6 \xt Rm 4:3; Gal 3:6; Jac 2:23\x*  
\v 7 Chujouvin Pakaiyin Abram ahoulimpi kit in, “Hiche gam hi nalo dingin nape ing'e tia Chaldea gam Ur khopia konna nangma nahin puidoh a Pakai chu keima kahi,” ati.  
\v 8 Hichun Abram in adonbut in, “O Pakai hiche hi kalo ding ahi ti ipia iti kahet doh thei ding ham?” ati.  
\v 9 Hichun Pakaiyin Abram ahou lim pin ajah a, “Bongnou kum thum lhingsa khat toh, kelngoi chal kum thum lhingsa khat toh, chule vahui nou khat le vapal nou khat ka henga hin choi tan,” ati peh e.  
\v 10 Hichun Abram in hichengse chu apedoh in athat in, hichun ahapsat cheh in, ahap lang ton alupsah in hinlah vacha ho vang chu asemkeh poi.  
\v 11 Chuin muthongho ahung lenglhauvin hiche sa kikoi ho chu ane kigo uvin ahile Abram in muthongho chu anodoh jin ahi.  
\v 12 Chuin nisa alhum ding kon'in Abram ahung imut soh tan, chujongleh tijat umtah muthim lhangkhal ahung jingin amapa chu ahin jinkhum tai. \x + \xo 15:12 \xt Job 4:13,14\x*  
\v 13 Hichun Pakaiyin Abram ahoulimpi in, “Nangman thonlou dinga nahet ding chu na chilhah ho hi gam danga hung mah thah diu ahiye, amaho se chu kum jali sunga mi bol genthei thoh a ga um ding ahiuve. \x + \xo 15:13 \xt Potdohbu 1:1-14; Act 7:6\x*  
\v 14 Ahin keiman hiche nam sugenthei ho chu ka phulah ding ahi, chule phat ahung sot a achaina teng amaho chun hatah a nei le gou ahin nei diu ahi. \x + \xo 15:14 \xt Potdohbu 12:40,41; Act 7:7\x*  
\v 15 (Nangman vang lungmong sel'a na pute heng na jot ding, chule na kum lhingset a na hinkho kichaiya na kivui ding ahiye.)  
\v 16 Chule amaho hi khangli ahung lhin phat le hiche gam'a hi hung kinung lekit diu ahi, ajeh chu tuchan gei hin Amor mite khan gitlouna hi pilhing loulai ahiye,” ati.  
\v 17 Chuin nisa alhum phat in mu athim tan ahile, meikhu belsung khat ah mei al-lenglung khat le meivah tobang khat ahung kitol in, hiche pi chu sa kihapsat a kikoi teni kah achun ahung kitollelen ahi.  
\v 18 Hichun Patkaiyin Abram chu hitin a kihoulimpi in, kinoptona anei lhonin hiche nichun, “Keiman nason na chilhah te kapeh gam chu hiche hi ahi, Egypt gamgi apat luipi dung gei Euphrate vadung gei, \x + \xo 15:18 \xt Act 7:5\x*   
\p
\v 19 Gamsung tutua Ken mite, Keniz mite chule Kadmon miten atoupha se,   
\p
\v 20 Hit mite, Perizz mite chule Rephaim mite,   
\p
\v 21 Amor mite ahiuvin, Canaan mite ahiuvin, Girgash miho ahiuvin, chule Jebus miho gam ahiuve,” ati.   
\c 16  
\s1 Ishmael Pen  
\p
\v 1 Tun, Abram jinu Sarai, chun cha anei thei tapoi. Ahinlah Sarai chun Egypt mi soh numei khat ana neiyin amanu chu Hagar ahi.  
\v 2 Chuin Sarai in jong Abram jah a aseiye, “Ven Pakaiyin kei la cha eihin sah tapon, lungset tah in ka sohnu kom'a galut tan; ijem itile amanua konna khu ka inchen dohsah thei nahi,” atile, Abram in jong Sarai thu angai tai.  
\v 3 Hichun Sarai Abram inneipin Hagar chu apuiyin Abram ji din apetai, hiche phat laitah chu ahile Abram kum som Canaan na achen jou don ahitai.  
\v 4 Hichun Abram toh Hagar chu akitimat lhon tan, chuin Hagar chun nao ahin vop tan hichun apinu Sarai chu noise tah in ahin vepan tan ahi.  
\v 5 Hijeh chun Sarai in Abram jah a aseitai, “Hiche ho jouse hi nang suhkhel ahi, ka sohnu hi nangma dan noiya ka koi ahin, hinlah tuhin amanun nao avop tan keima noise tah in eive tan hijeh chun kei le nang kah a Pakai thutan in hung pang jeng hen!” atitai.  
\v 6 Abram'in adonbut in “Ven, amanu khu nasoh hilou ham, nangman pha nasah dungjuijin bol tang em” ati. Hichun Sarai in Hagar hatah in ahin sugenthei pan tan hichun amanun (Hagar) ajamsan tai.  
\v 7 Pakai Vantil in gamthip a twikhuh phungkhat a Hagar chu aga mudoh in ahi, hiche twikhuh chu Shur jotna lampia um ahiye.  
\v 8 Pakai Vantil chun aseiye, “Hagar, Sarai sohnu hoilanga konna hoilam jon ding nahim? ” atile Hagar in adonbut in, “Kapinu, Sarai kom'a konna hung jam doh kahi,” ati.  
\v 9 Hichun Pakai Vantil chun amanu ahoulimpi in, “Nangma napinu kom'a kinungle in chule amanu dan noiya nakun angaiye.”  
\v 10 Hichun Pakai Vantil chun ahoulimpi nalaiyin, “Keiman na chilhah te tamtah kapehbe ding nahi, sim jong na sim joulou ding ahiye,” ati.  
\v 11 Pakai Vantil chun ahoulimpi nalaiyin, “Tua hi nangma naovop nahi tan chapa khat nahin ding, hiche naosen chu amin Ishmael nasah ding ahi. (Pathen'in angailhi jing'e tina ahi), ijeh inem itile Pakaiyin na gimna chu na khongai peh tai.  
\v 12 Chule nachapa hi mihem lah a gam'a sangan lungthim bei bang ding, mitin douna khut ahinlap a chule mitin khut ama chunga hung chu ding, chuleh aphunggol jouse toh kidou toa hung khosa ding ahi.”  
\v 13 Hiche jou chun Hagar in ajah a thu hinsei Pakai chu aminvo in, “Nangma hi keima eimudoh a Pathen nahi,” ati. Ajeh chu amanu'n “Tahbeh monga keiman Pathen kamu a chule ama kamu nunga ka hing'a kaum nahlai ham?” atin ahi.  
\v 14 Hichun twisam putna chu amin Beer-lahai-roi asah tai, (hichu “Eimudoh Pa Hingjing twikhuh” tina ahi), Hiche Twikhuh hi Kadesh le Bered kikah a um ahiye.  
\v 15 Hichun Hagar in Abram chu chapa khat ahin peh tai. Hichun Abram in achapa min chu Ishmael asah tai. \x + \xo 16:15 \xt Gal 4:22\x*  
\v 16 Hagar in Abram dinga Ishmael ahin peh chun Abram chu kum som get le kum gup alhing tan ahi.   
\c 17  
\s1 Abram chu Abraham kisahta  
\p
\v 1 Abram chu kum somko le kumko alhinin Pakaiyin ahoulimpi in hitin aseipeh e, “Keima El-Shaddai____ 'Pathen chungnung kahi.' Hijeh chun lunglhaisel in nei hou jingin lang, chule thenna hinkho mang jingin,” ati.  
\v 2 Keiman nangma to ikikah a kitepna nape ingting hichu thon louhel'a nangma chilhah simsen lou kapeh ding nahi.  
\v 3 Hichun Abram in amai tol lang aven hichun Pathen'in ahin houvin hitin aseiye,  
\v 4 Hiche hi keima le nangma kinoptona ahi, keiman nangma hi nam jouse pa kaso ding nahi, ati.  
\v 5 Abanna namin jong kakhel peh ding, Abram nahi tah louding, Abraham na kiti ding ahitai, ajeh chu nangma hi nam jouse dia mipa nahi ding ahitai. \x + \xo 17:5 \xt Rm 4:17\x*  
\v 6 Keiman nangma hatah a kagasah ding, na chilhah ten nam tamtah ahin sondoh diu, chule leng thupi tah tah jong amaho lah a hung umdoh ding ahiye.  
\v 7 “Keiman athah a nangma to iki noptona chu na chilhah te to kakitepna avel'a ka phudoh kit ding nangma nunga na chilhah te a dinga jong, khang le khang kikah ajong, hiche hi atonsot a hi ding, keima na Pathen'u kahi jing ding chule nanam, na chilhah te Pathen jong kahi jing ding ahi. \x + \xo 17:7 \xt Lk 1:55\x*  
\v 8 Keiman Canaan gam pumpi ahin, tua na chenna gam kholjin banga nachen nau hi nason na chilhah te atonsot a goulo dinga kapeh ding, chule amaho dinga jong a Pathen'u kahi jing ding ahi,” ati. \x + \xo 17:8 \xt Act 7:5\x*  
\v 9 Hichun Pathen'in Abraham ahoulimpin, “Nangma tah in jong kinoptona hi najui ding, chule na nunga nason na chilhah te dinga jong akhang lhum kei uva ajui ding'u ahi.  
\v 10 Hiche hi ahi kinoptona nangma le na chilhah te jousen ajui cheh ding, nangho lah a pasal jousen chep akitan sohkei ding'u ahi. \x + \xo 17:10 \xt Act 7:8; Rm 4:11\x*  
\v 11 Nangman na bollou a hitheilou chu natahsa vunval abohlai chu nachelhah sohkei ding, hichun avetsah chu ahile keima le nangma kikah a kinoptona hijing ding ahi.  
\v 12 Hiche hi nangma insung mite seh hilouvin, koi tobang nasoh nakol nangma insunga dinga nachoh doh ho jouse jong ahop tha cheh ding,  
\v 13 Abonchauva chep nakitan cheh diu, na tahsauva maha napoh uchu keima toh atonsotna iki nopto na'uva um jing ding ahiye.  
\v 14 Koi tobang pasal khat tou hiche kinoptona cheptan hi bollou aum le ama chu kinoptona insunga kon'a paimanga um ding ahi, ajeh chu kinoptona ajuilou jeh ahi.  
\v 15 Hichun Pathen'in Abraham ahoulimpi'n “Na inneipi Sarai jong Sarai na ti tahlou ding ahi, ijeh inem itile amanu min jong hi tu apatna Sarah hi ding ahitai.  
\v 16 Keiman amanu hi phatthei kaboh a chujongleh amanu a konna hi chapa khat kapeh ding nahi, hitia chu keiman amanu hi phatthei kaboh a ama jong “Sarah” chitin namtin nu hung hi ding mitin vaipi leng ding ho jeng jong amanu a konna hung peng doh ding ahiuve,” ati.  
\v 17 Hichun Abraham jong akun in tol lang aven anui tai, chuin alungthim in ama le ama akihouvin, Keima hi kum jakhat kahi nunga mipa kahi thei ding ham? Chule ka inneipi Sarah jong kum som ko le kum ko ahi jouva naosen iti anei thei ding ham? ati.  
\v 18 Abraham'in Pathen heng'a aseijin, “Ahi thei ding le Ishmael hi nangma phatthei bohna noiya um jing tahen.”  
\v 19 Hinlah Pathen'in adonbut in, “ahipoi Sarah, na inneipi in nangma a dinga chapa khat nahin peh ding, nangman hiche chapang chu amin Isaac nasah ding ahi. Chule keiman ama le ama nunga ason achilhah te dinga kinoptona chu atonsot geiya kinoptona a um jing dinga ka phudoh ding ahi.  
\v 20 Ishmael jong chu phatthei kaboh ding nangman nathum ma bang'a ama jeng jong hatah a kapun sah ding, chule ama chilhah te ho jong hatah a pung dingu ahi.  
\v 21 Hinlah keima kitepna vang chu Sarah in khovei tulai phat a hi nahin ding Isaac chuto bou ka phudoh ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 22 Pathen'in thu aseijou phat chun Abraham chu adalhatai.  
\v 23 Hichun Abraham'in jong achapa Ishmael ahin, asoh pasal ama insunga peng den hihen, sum a achoh tho hijongleh, Abraham mite lah a pasal jouse chu apuikhom in, Pathen'in aseipeh bang bang chun hiche nikho mama chun chep atan peh sohkeiyin ahi.  
\v 24 Abraham'in chep akitan chun akum kum som ko le kum ko ana lhing tai.  
\v 25 Chule achapa Ishmael in chep akitan chun kum som le kum thum ana lhing tan ahi.  
\v 26 Ani lhonin Abraham le achapa Ishmael chun nikhat in chep atan gel lhonin ahi.  
\v 27 Chule a insunga pasal jouse, insunga pengden hihen lang gam dang mi soh dinga akichoh tho hijongleh aboncha ama toh thakhat a chep kitan tha cheh ahiuve.   
\c 18  
\s1 Thutep chapa Isaac  
\p
\v 1 Mamre munna gangpi phung kom'a chun Pakai chu Abraham henga ahung kilah in ahi. Nikhat hi nichangsat pettah hin Abraham chu aponbuh maiya ana touvin ahi.  
\v 2 Ama ahung dahdoh in ahile akom'a mithum ana din amun ahi. Amaho chu amu phat in ama alhai jelin amaho lemnan tol ah abohkhup in ahi. \x + \xo 18:2 \xt Heb 13:2\x*  
\v 3 Chuin Abraham'in “Ka Pakai,” tin adonbut in, “Nang hon pha nasah uleh phat chomkhat naki ngah thei diu ham.  
\v 4 Nakeng silna ding'u kahin choi kah in hiche thing limnoiya hin ana kicholdo tadiuvin.  
\v 5 Chule nang hon na lhacha pa hi khotona neitah a nei hungvil ngal'u ahileh na kholjin na mano masangun na tha kidona dingun naneh ding'u them khat nahin gon peh unge, ama hon aphai, nasei bang chun hin boltan atiuve.  
\v 6 Hichun Abraham chu aponbuh kom langa alhai jel'in Sarah kom'ah asei tan ahi, “Kinloi tah in changbong atena dim thum tedoh inlang twi toh mehnangin, chule changlhah hin kang loi temin,” aga tin ahi.  
\v 7 Hichun Abraham'in gancha ho kivahna lang ajonin bongnou athao pen asohte ho apen, gangtah in ahin hon sah in ahi.  
\v 8 Anneh ding ho amin phat in Abraham'in bongnoi ha le bongnoi toh chule bongnou sa ahon uchu amaho angsung'ah aneh diuvin aga luipeh in ama hon anneh laisen ama jong thinglim a chun ading jinge.  
\v 9 Chuin ama hon Abraham jah a “Na loinu Sarah hoilam a um aham?” atiu leh Abraham'in ponbuh sunga aum nai, ati.  
\v 10 Chuin amaho lah a khat chun aseiyin, “Keima hi khovei tulai phat mama le kahung kinung lekit ding ahi, vetan hiche phat teng chule na inneipi Sarah khun chapa khat ana hin ding ahi,” ati chu anunga ponbuh sunglam a um Sarah chun angai lhin ahi. \x + \xo 18:10 \xt Rm 9:9\x*  
\v 11 Abraham le Sarah chu atahsa kum lhon chu atam gel lhon tan, chule Sarah jong nao nei phat kum akhel ahitai.  
\v 12 Hichun Sarah guhthim in ama le ama aki nuisat in hitin aseiye, “Iti hithei ding ham, kei tobang aching sa numeijin kipana thil phalou kamu ding ham, ka jipa jeng jong akum atam lheh tai,” ati. \x + \xo 18:12 \xt 1 Pet 3:6\x*  
\v 13 Pakaiyin Abraham jah achun aseiye, “Ipi dinga Sarah khu nuiya ka teh nunga keiman cha kanei tahbeh mong ding hinam,” ati ham?  
\v 14 Pakaiya dinga ipi ahahsa um ham? Keima khovei tulai phat na kahung kit ding chule Sarah in cha pasal khat anei ding ahi.” \x + \xo 18:14 \xt Lk 1:37\x*  
\v 15 Chuphat in Sarah chu atija tan hichun Sarah in aseilep tan, “Keima ka nuipoi” atin ahinla, “Pakaiyin adonbut in nangma na nui nai,” ati.   
\s1 Sadom dinga Abraham taona  
\p
\v 16 Hichun pasal thum ho chu an aneh jouvun ading doh un Sodom lang chu agaldot un, ama hon adalha uvin, Abraham chu amaho thah doh ding tin lampi gei aga kilhonpin ahi.  
\v 17 Pakai chun aseiye, “Keiman katoh gon ho hi Abraham kom'a kasel ding ham?” ati.  
\v 18 Ajeh chu Abraham chu lentah le nam hattah chule vannoiya nam jouse ama jeh a phatthei chang ding ahi ngal'in,  
\v 19 Chule achapa te le ama ban a a insung mi aman thu apeh a, chutia chu adih abol thei uva, thu adih a atan theina ding uva Pakai lampi ajui thei uva, chutengleh Pakaiyin Abraham chung chang'a akitepnasa chu ahin molso theina dinga ama hi kilheng doh ahi tila kahenan,” ati.  
\v 20 Hichun Pakaiyin Abraham ahoulimpi in “Sodom le Gomorrah douna thu kisei asangval tan chule achonset nau jong aseval tai,” ati.  
\v 21 Keima chesuh ing kating ka henga thu hung kisei dungjuiya hi abol cheh uham, hilou ham gapho chen inge,” ati.  
\v 22 Hichun miho chu chukom'a kon'in akiheiyun Sodom lang chu ajonun ache tauve, ahinlah Abraham chu Pakai masanga chun ading chah den jingin ahi.  
\v 23 Abraham'in anailut in hitin aseiye, “Nangman michonpha atheng chule mi phalou agilouho aboncha na suhmang tha ding ham,” ati.  
\v 24 Ijem tin khopi sunga chun michonpha som nga bang um ta le, asunga michonpha somnga ho jal'a jong chu akhomun chu khen dehlou hel'a na suhmang jeng ding ham?  
\v 25 Nang dinga hitobang thil nabol a, michonpha le migilou agoma natha cheh a, michonpha le migilou akibah ding chu bolda hel jeng le chun kati! Leiset thutan pan adih a atan louding ham?” atile.  
\v 26 Hichun Pakaiyin adonbut in, “Keiman mi somnga thudih thil phalou bol Sodom khopi a kamu doh thei le, amaho jal'a chu khopi ka huhdoh ding ahi.”  
\v 27 Hichun Abraham'in aseikit in, “Ka Pakai nangman neiphal peh thei ding le kasei ban ho kajom nom in keima vang bohse vutvai tobang kahin,  
\v 28 Ijem tin mi somli le nga tobang chonpha mitheng mi somnga sanga lhomjo namu le amaho jeh a chu khopi hi na suhmang ding ham, mi nga lhahsam jeh chun? Pakaiyin adonbut in, Keiman hiche khopi a hi mi som li le nga kamu doh jouva ahile sumang ponge,” ati.  
\v 29 Hichun Abraham'in adeichat angaichat avel in aseiyin, “Ijem tin mi som li bou umta le,” atin chuin Pakaiyin ahoulimpi kit in, “Keiman amaho mi somli jeh a chu ka suhmang louhel ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 30 Ka Pakai, “Lungset tah in lunghanglou jenin,” Abraham atao kit leovin, “Nei phalpeh thei lechun kasei nom na laiye, Ijemtin mi som thum muta le chun,” atile Pakaiyin ahoulimpi in “Keiman mi somthum hijongleh ka suhmang louding ahi,” ati.  
\v 31 Hichun Abraham'in aseikit in, “Nangman nei phalpeh thei le ka thusei hi kajom nom'e, “Ijem tin mi somni hijongleh atile,” Pakaiyin adonbut in, “Mi somni kamu jong le ka suhmang louding ahi,” ati.  
\v 32 Abraham'in achaina in aseipeh tan, “Pakai, nei lunghan hihbeh inlang, khatvei neisei sah kit le tia katao ahi, mi som muta le chun” hichun Pakaiyin aseiye, “Mi som kamu doh jong le ka suhmang louding ahi,” ati.  
\v 33 Hichun Abraham henga athusei ding aboncha aseisoh phat in Pakai chu ache tan, Abraham vang chu a inmun lam'a ahung kile kittai.   
\c 19  
\s1 Sadom le Gomorrah kisuh mang  
\p
\v 1 Hiche ni nilhah lam in vantil ni ahung lhonin ahile Lot chu Sodom khopi kelkot a anatou pet ahin Lot in vantil teni amu phat chun alamto dingin akipat doh in amani masanga tol ah abohkhup in ahi.  
\v 2 Chuin Lot in hitin aseiye, “Ka Pakai hung lhonin ka insunga nakeng hung kisop lhonin, chule tujan kain a geh lhon inlang, jingpi matah in thou lhon inlang na kholchena lhon aban najom thei lhon ahi,” atile, amanin “Ahipoi, hithei ponte,” ati lhonin “Keini tujan hiche mun a ong dunga geh mai lhon tange,” ati.  
\v 3 Hinlah Lot in aha sei behset jeh chun amani jong Lot inlanga geh din ache tauve, hichun Lot in amani neh ding chol kisolou changlhah akanpeh in amanin jong ane lhon tai.  
\v 4 Hinlah anehjou don khojin masang chun Sodom khopi sunga khangthah, tehse, kiti jouse ahung kikhom un amaho gena in chu aum kimvel tauvin ahi.  
\v 5 Amaho chun Lot henga asam tauvin “Nangma kom'a ageh dinga hung ho chu hoilam a nakoi hitam? amani chu hinpui doh in amani chutoh ka lupkhom diu ahi, tin athum tauve.” \x + \xo 19:5 \xt Thutan Vaihom Ho 19:22-24\x*  
\v 6 Hichun Lot chu amaho toh kihoulim din ahung potdoh in , anung lam a kot chu akhah in ahi.  
\v 7 “Lungset tah in sopi te ho” tin ama atao tan, “Hitobang Thil phalou hi bol hihbeh uvin.”  
\v 8 Veuvin, keiman chanu nungah thengsel ni kaneiye. Keiman ka chanu teni hin puidoh ing ting nangho kom'a, amani chu nadei dei a nabol theiyu ahi.  
\v 9 Hinlah ama hon Lot chu “Kinung chen,” atiuvin, chujongleh ama hon aseiyun “Hiche pa hi ahung khopem len chule eiho thutanna pang ding akigo vehta! Tua amaho (Vantil teni), kigimbolna ding sanga nangma agilou cheh a kabol ding'u nahi,” atiuve. Hiti chun Lot chu hatah in avouvin kotpi jong chu phutjal dingin ahin go tauve.  
\v 10 Hichun vantil teni chun Lot chu akhut na aman lhonin akailut lhonin insunga kot chu akhah tauve.  
\v 11 Hichun vantil teni chun kotpi phunga miho chu ateh jong akhangthah jong abonchauvin amit'u achotsah lhonin ahile abonchauvin kotphung holmon akisu lungdong gam tauve. \x + \xo 19:11 \xt 2 Lengte 6:18\x*  
\v 12 Phat chomkhat jouvin vantil teni chun Lot jah a hitin asei lhon e, “Hiche khopi a hi sopi ule nao adang nanei nahlai em? na chanu jipa ho hihen, na chapa te hihen, na chanu ho hihen lang koi dang dang hijongleh hiche khopi sunga nangma mi poupou chu abonchauvin hiche mun a kon hin puidoh tan.”  
\v 13 Ajeh chu hiche khopi hi pumsuh mang ding kati lhon ahitai. Awgin hung kithong hi aphatmo na alen lheh tan Pakai kom ahin phatai, chujeh a chu keini hi asumang dia eihin sol lhon ahi.  
\v 14 Hijeh chun Lot chu apotdoh in achanu teni jipa ding teni jah a chun, “Kinloi tah in hiche khopi akon hin potdoh loi lhonin, ajeh chu Pakaiyin hiche khopi asuhmang ding ahitai,” agati leh, achanu teni jipa ding teni chun atot dan in ana gel lhon e.  
\v 15 Kho ahung vahlhah a jingkah chun vantil teni chu ahung kino lheh lhon tan, “Gang in Lot,” tin aseipeh lhon e, “Na jinu chule na chanute tutu hin puidoh in. Hikom'a kon'in potdoh un, achuti louleh nangma hiche khopi toh suhmang tha a naum ding ahiye,” ati lhon e.  
\v 16 Lot chu akhongai nalaiyin, vantil teni chun ama khut, ajinu khut, chule achanu teni khutna aman lhonin khopi pam lam ah ajamdohpi lhonin ahi, ajeh chu Pakaiyin amaho angailut lheh jeng ahi. \x + \xo 19:16 \xt 2 Pet 2:7\x*  
\v 17 Amaho khopi pam langa ahin puidoh lhon phat in Vantil teni in thu amop in “Naki hinso theina ding uvin jamdoh loiyun hung jong hung kinung hei hih uvin phaicham dunga jong kibangpa hihhel uvin, thinglhang lam'a jam doh loiyun achuti louleh nangma jong suhmanga naum tha khah ding ahi,” ati peh lhon e.  
\v 18 Hichun Lot chun amani jah a “Ahipoi ka Pakai!” atin  
\v 19 Nangman neina ngailu lheh in chule ka hinkho jong neina huhdoh in chukeo hilouvin ngailutna sangtah jong nei musah in, hinlah molsang langa kache jou louding ahiye, thinan eiphah lo ding ahi, ka hinkho kichai ding ahi.  
\v 20 Vetemin, khoneo phaicham khat muthei in aum'e, jamlutna dingin abailam in chule naicha bou ahi; kaki hinsona dingin lungset tah in hikom'a khun nei jamlut sah tan,” ati.  
\v 21 Vantil in adonbut in “Aphai tua nasei jong hi nanop peh ingting, chule keiman hiche phaicham gam'a um khopi nasei jong khu suhmang da tange.  
\v 22 Ahin kino gang un, jamdoh loiyun, Ajeh chu keiman ima ka bolthei louding nangma ho khulam nalhun kah seuvin,” (Hiche in avetsah ahilchet chu khopi min chu Zoar kiti ahin hiche chu ahile khomun neocha tina ahi).  
\v 23 Lot Zoar mun agah lhun chun jingkah nisa hungso doh jou tah ahi.  
\v 24 Hichun Pakaiyin vanthamjolla kon'in meikong chule hui thanei thina thei akongthei hui Sodom le Gomorrah chunga ajuh sah tai. \x + \xo 19:24 \xt Matt 10:15; 11:23,24; Lk 10:12; 17:29; 2 Pet 2:6; Jde 1:7\x*  
\v 25 Chule Pathen'in khopi teni jong, phaicham geiya akhopi teni sunga cheng jouse ahin, tolla kehdoh thingna louna abonchan asugam hel tai.  
\v 26 Hinlah Lot Inneipi chu akinung heijin anunglam agah vet leh chikhom asoh in akitung den tai. \x + \xo 19:26 \xt Lk 17:32\x*  
\v 27 Chule Abraham chu ajing jingkah matah in ache loijin Pakai angsunga adinna mun achun adingin,  
\v 28 Sodom le Gomorrah lam gam chu agah vesuh in ahile, vetan agam meikhu pi chu meihol kilhut bangin akhu akitun doh jen jun jeng chu amu tan ahi.  
\v 29 Hinlah Pathen'in Abraham taona ageldoh in hijeh chun asopipa Lot chu phaicham khopi asuhmang masang'in apuidoh in, chujouvin Lot chenna khopi teni chu a sumang tai.   
\s1 Moab mite le Amon mite penna  
\p
\v 30 Chuin phat chomkhat jouvin Lot le achanu tenin Zoar mun chu adalha uvin, thinglhang lam ajonun, songko sung khat a achanu teni chutoh acheng khom tauve.  
\v 31 Nikhat chu Lot chanu teni alenjo nu chun anaonu kom'a hitin aseiye “Hikom gamsunga pasal gollhang aum tapoi midang ho banga ji inei lhon louding ahitai. Chuleh eihing hon ipa jong hungvoija ateh lang ahitan, cha aneilou ding ahitai.  
\v 32 Hungin ipa hi khamna thei donsah hitin, akham teng ikitimatpi lhon ding ahiye, hiche a konna chu eiho insung hi ipa a konna chilhah inei doh lhon ding ahi bouve,” ati.  
\v 33 Hichun amanin hiche jan chun apa lengpitwi adonkham sah lhonin, chuin alenjo nu chu asunglhan apa to aga kiti mat lhon tan ahin apa chun achanu aluppet jong atho doh pet jong ahepoi.  
\v 34 Ajing nikho chun alenjo nun anaonu kom'ah hitin aseiye, “Keima janlhah chun ipa to kaki timat lhon tai, tujan jong lengpitwija khamsah hitin, tujan teng nangma gache inlang gaki timatpi in hiche a konna eiho chilhah hi ipa a konna bou ikisem doh thei ding bou ahi,” ati.  
\v 35 Hiche jan chun amanin apa lhon lengpitwi adonkham sah lhonin chuin aneojo nu aga sunglha kit in apa to aga kitimat kit tan, amasa a bang chun achanu aneonu ahung lup pet akithodoh pet jong ahepoi.  
\v 36 Hiche jeh chun Lot chanu tenin apa a kon'in nao ahin vop gel lhon tan ahi.  
\v 37 Achanu alenjo nu chun nao pasal khat ahing tan amin chu Moab asah tai, amapa chu nam khat ahung hitan tua Moab mite kiti ho hi ahiuve.  
\v 38 Aneojo nun nao pasal khat ahing kit in, amanun achapa min chu Ben-ammi asah tai. Ama hi nam khat mipa lamkai ahung hin tua Ammon mite ho hi ahiuve.   
\c 20  
\s1 Abraham le Abimelech  
\p
\v 1 Hiche akon chun Abraham chu Negev gam langa akichon'in Kadesh le Shur kikah a phat chomkhat ana chengin, chuin Gerar lang geijin aga chengin ahi.  
\v 2 Abraham'in a inneipi Sarah chu “Ka sopinu ahi,” tin ana phongdoh in ahile Gerar lengpa Abimelech chun mi asol'in Sarah chu aga puisah tai. \x + \xo 20:2 \xt Semtilbu 12:13; 26:7\x*  
\v 3 Hinlah hiche jan chun Pathen'in Abimelech amangin aki musah in hitin aseipeh e, “Nangma hi athisa nahi ahitai, ajeh chu numei na kipui hi ajinei numei ahi bouve!”  
\v 4 Ahin Abimelech chun amanu (Sarah), chu akitimatpi loulai ahi, hijeh chun Abimelech in “Pakai, nangin hiche imacha hechenlou nam hi na suhmang mong ding hitam?  
\v 5 Hitia chu Abraham tah in jong 'Ka sopinu ahi' tia eina houlimpi hilou ham? Chule amanun jong 'Ka sopipa ahi' atia, hijeh achu keiman ka lungthim'a jong themmona beihel a chule ka khut teni jong atheng ahi bouve” ati.  
\v 6 Hijeh chun Pathen'in amangin adonbut in, “Ahinai, keiman nangma hetthem louna ho chu ka henai. Hiche ho jeh achu nangma keima douna a chonset a konna kasuh khen'a chule hiche ho jeh a chu numeinu to kaki timatsah lou ahi.  
\v 7 Tun numeinu chu a inneipu kom'a soltan, a inneipun taona na manpeh ding ahi, ajeh chu ama themgao ahi, chuteng nangma nadam kit ding ahitai. Ahin nahet ding khat chu a inneipi nanung pehdoh louleh nangma chule na mite nathi gam diu ahi.  
\v 8 Hijeh chun Abimelech jong jingkah matah in akithou doh in chuin asoh ho jouse gangtah in akoukhom tan, chuin Abimelech in thusoh jouse chu asohte ho lah achun aseiyin tijatnan adim tauve.  
\v 9 Hichun Abimelech in Abraham chu akouvin ajah a “Ipibol a hiti pia hi nei hung bol'u hitam? Itobang'a nang douna a kana chonset hitam, hitia kei le ka lenggam chunga chonset nasatah hi nahin pohlut ham? Bol louhel ding thil nangman neibol khum ahitai,” ati.  
\v 10 Chuin Abimelech in Abraham kom'a aseiye, “Nangin ipi nabolna ham?”  
\v 11 Abraham'in adonbut in, “Hiche mun hi Pathen ginglou mihem tamna mun ahi tin kagel in, ka loinu chu ka sopinu ahi kiti leh amanu jeh a chu eitha lou diu ham kati ahi.”  
\v 12 Adihtah a sei dinga ka sopinu jong ahi nai, eihing lhonpa chu khat ahin kanu lhon vang achom chom ahi. Keiman kaji din kakipui tai.  
\v 13 Pathen'in eina koudoh chun kapa insung kana dalhah chun mun khat a patna mun chom a kana vale lhon lai chun kana seiye, thil ngaichat kaneiye katin, hoilang hijongleh iche le nangho gamsunga kasopipa tin miho lah a nei phondoh ding ahi tin kana seipeh e.”  
\v 14 Hichun Abimelech in akelcha ho le kelngoi hon ho chule abong hon chule numei pasal asoh ho chu Abraham apetai. Abimelech in a inneipi Sarah jong chu anungsol peh kit tai.  
\v 15 Hichun Abimelech in adonbut in, “Dah inlang vetem in kagamsung nangin nadei penna mun'a nachen thei ahiye.”  
\v 16 Abimelech in Sarah jah a aseiye, “Ven keiman na sopipa dangka sang khat kapen, hiche sum hi na kom'a um chengse mitmu a suhkhel kihetthem tona dinga kapeh ahi, chule japi angsunga nangma boina nanei tapoi,” ati.  
\v 17 Hichun Abraham'in Pathen kom'a taona amangin Pathen'in Abimelech asudam tan, chule a inneipi le asoh numei ho jouse naobu jouse jong cha anei theina diuvin akihong gam tai.  
\v 18 Ajeh chu Abraham jinu Sarah jeh a Pakaiyin Abimelech insunga numei naobu jouse ana khatan peh ahiye.   
\c 21  
\s1 Isaac pen thu  
\p
\v 1 Pakaiyin ana seisa bang chun Sarah ahung villin Sarah chunga asuh bulhit peh tai.  
\v 2 Hichun Sarah in nao ahin vop in, Abraham chu atehset nungin Pathen'in ateppeh phat dontah in chapa khat ahin petan ahi. \x + \xo 21:2 \xt Heb 11:11\x*  
\v 3 Abraham'in achapa chu amin Isaac asah tan ahi.  
\v 4 Chule Isaac pen jou niget alhin nin Abraham'in Pathen thupeh bangin achapa chu chep atanpeh tai. \x + \xo 21:4 \xt Semtilbu 17:12; Act 7:8\x*  
\v 5 Isaac ahung pen chun, Apa Abraham chu kum jakhat ana lhingtai.  
\v 6 Chuin Sarah in aphong doh in, “Pathen'in nuina eipei,” ati.  
\v 7 Chule aman, “Sarah hin cha le nao noi hin chepsah inte tin koipen in Abraham kom'a ana sei ngam dem? Ahinlah keiman atehset nungin chapa khat kahinpeh tai,” ati.   
\s1 Hagar le Ismael kisol mang  
\p
\v 8 Isaac chu ahung khanglen deuvin anneh masapen Abraham'in kipanan kikhopna asem e.  
\v 9 Hichun Sarah in jong achapa chu Egypt mi Hagar'in Abraham ahinpeh Ishmael to aki chep lhon chu amudoh tai.  
\v 10 Hichun amanun Abraham kom'ah hitin aseiye, “Hiche sohnu le achapa chu solmang in ajeh chu hiche chapang hin keima chapa toh chanvou anei khom lhon ding aumpoi; Isaac toh kikomto ahi.” \x + \xo 21:10 \xt Gal 4:29,30\x*  
\v 11 Hichun Abraham'in nopmo asa lheh jengin ajeh chu Ishmael jong chu achapa ahiye.  
\v 12 Hinlah Pathen'in Abraham chu ahoulimpi in, “Nangman chapang chung chang chule na sohnu jeh in ima lung phatmona nei hih in, Sarah in bol in atiho chu bol in ajeh chu Isaac a konna bou na chilhah te hung kisim ding bou ahi.” \x + \xo 21:12 \xt Rm 9:7; Heb 11:18\x*  
\v 13 Hinlah keiman Hagar chapa jong chu nam lentah khat kaso thou thou ding ahi. Ajeh chu amapa jong chu nangma chapa jong ahi thouve.”  
\v 14 Hichun Abraham ajingin matah in akithouvin, neh ding bu asutup in chule twipohna ding twibom Hagar chu apen alengkouva aledoh peh tan ahi, hichun amanu le achapa chu asolmang in, chuin Hagar chu suhna ding helouvin Beersheba gamthip noiya avahlelei.  
\v 15 Hichun twi ahung bei chun amanu (Hagar) chun naosen chu hampa nangboh limnoiyah akoitai.  
\v 16 Hichun amanu (Hagar) apotdoh in atoulha tan achang seh in lamsom tobang kikah in “Keiman hiche chapang thi hi kamu nompoi,” atin amanu chu alhi alongin akaptai.  
\v 17 Hinlah Pathen'in chapang ka awgin chu ajan chuin Pakai vantil in vanna kon'in Hagar chu ahin kouvin, “Hagar ipi boina nanei ham? Imacha kichatna nei hih in! Pathen'in aumna mun'a kon'in chapang ka awgin chu ajatai, ati.  
\v 18 Kipatdoh inlang nao khu gakidop loiyin nakhut in kipomchah jon, ijeh inem itile keiman ama khu nam lentah kahisah ding ahi.”  
\v 19 Hichun Pathen'in Hagar mit chu kho amusah in chua twi tamtah amusah tan, hichun amanun gangtah in twipai chu asudim in chapang chu adonsah tai.  
\v 20 Chule chapang chu Pathen'in ahin umpi jingin neocha ahi apat gamthipnoi jenga ahung chengin, thalpi kap ahung them lheh jengin ahi.  
\v 21 Chule Ishmael chu Paran gamthip noiya ana chengin, chule anun Egypt gam'a ama ji dingin numei khat aga puipeh in ahi.   
\s1 Abraham le Abimelech kah a kitepna  
\p
\v 22 Hiche phat laitah chun Abimelech le asepai jalamkai Phicol chu Abraham vil din ahung'e. “Pathen'in nangma hi na umpi jingin, na thilbolna jouse ah na kithopi jinge,” tin ahung seiye. \x + \xo 21:22 \xt Semtilbu 26:26\x*  
\v 23 Pathen min'in kitemin, chule nei joulhep louhel ding, ka chate jong ahilouleh ka chilhah ho jong, keivang nangma adia thilpha bolnom jing, chule tuhin na kihahsel ding, thilpha nabol jing ding hiche gamsunga maljin gampam nahi laisen,” ati.  
\v 24 Abraham'in adonbut in “Heng'e kakitem e,” ati.  
\v 25 Hichun Abraham'in Abimelech kom'a lunglhai louna aphong doh in Abimelech sohten twikul hunam a Abraham sohte ana lahpeh u thu chu ahi.  
\v 26 “Tuchung hi hiche thu kajah masah pen ahi,” tin Abimelech in adonbut'e. “Keiman hiche chung chang hi koi oimo a, koi ngoh ding ham kahepoi. Ajeh chu phat masan ima thu nana sei khapoi,” ati.  
\v 27 Abraham'in hichun akelngoi ho, kelcha ho, chule bonghon ho Abimelech apen kinoptona anei lhon'e.  
\v 28 Hichun Abraham'in kelngoi nou sagi ho chu achom a alhengdoh in ahi.  
\v 29 Abimelech in Abraham chu adongin “Adang ho a konna hiche sagi ho hi ipi dia nachom khen ham?” ati.  
\v 30 Abraham'in adonbut in, “Hiche twikhuh keiman kalaisa ahi, tia ahetoh a nei panpehna dinga hiche kelngoi sagi hi neisanpeh tei in” ati.  
\v 31 Hijeh chun ama in hiche mun chun Beersheba asah tai. Ajeh chu mihem teni akihettona mun lhon ahiye.  
\v 32 Beersheba munna kihettona mun'a akimuto jouvin, Abimelech le Phicol sepai lamkaipa chu Philistine mun lama akinung le lhon tan ahi.  
\v 33 Abraham'in Beersheba mun achun chahthing phung aphutdoh in, hiche achun aman Pathen chu tonsot Pathen ahi tin aphong doh e.  
\v 34 Hichun Abraham chu Phillistine mun'a chun phat sottah achengin ahi.   
\c 22  
\s1 Abraham tahsan kisuh detpeh  
\p
\v 1 Thil hijatpi kichai jouvin Pathen'in Abraham chu apatep in aman hitin aseiye, “Vo Abraham!” atile, “Hikom'a kaum'e, Pakai” ati. \x + \xo 22:1 \xt Heb 11:17-19\x*  
\v 2 Hichun Pathen'in aseiye, “Nangailut tah na chapa changkhat seh Isaac chu puijin lang Moriah gam'a chen keiman kahin seipeh ding molsang khat pen pen chunga chu pumgo thilto maicham adin pedoh tan,” ati. \x + \xo 22:2 \xt 2 Thusimbu 3:1\x*  
\v 3 Chuti chun Abraham chu jingkah matah in athoudoh in a sangan teni akigon tup in chule asoh pasal ni akipuiyin achapa Isaac apuiyin, pumgo thilto govamna dingin thing akipoh in akipat doh in Pathen'in aseipehna mun chu ajontai.  
\v 4 Ani thum lhinnin Abraham chu adah in aven ahile amun chu gal'a kon'in amutai.  
\v 5 Abraham'in asoh teni jah a aseiyin, “Nangni hikom'a hin sangan toh ana um tauvin, kei le ka chapa khulam akhun gache lhon tadinge, Pathen kaga hou lhon ding kahung kinung le vah lhon ding ahi.”  
\v 6 Abraham'in thinglom maicham a pumgo thilto halna ding chu Isaac aputsah in chule achempai achoijin amani hiti chun akijot lhonin achelhon tai.  
\v 7 Chuin Isaac in apa Abraham jah a “Hepa” atile Abraham'in jong “Hoijo, kachapa” ati. Hichun Isaac in “Mei le thinglom la aum tan, pumgo thilto kelngoi hoiba ham?”  
\v 8 Abraham'in adonbut in “Kachapa, Pathen ama tah in kelngoi pumgo maicham a ding hin gong nante” atin hichun amani achebe lhonin ahi.  
\v 9 Pathen'in Abraham aseipehna mun ahung lhun lhon phat in Abraham chun maicham khat asemin, thinglom chu agol chan ajam'in chuin achapa Isaac chu aheltum in maicham chunga alupsah tai. \x + \xo 22:9 \xt Jac 2:21\x*  
\v 10 Hichun aman achem chu apaiya kon'in aladoh in, achapa chu sut agon akilam tai,  
\v 11 Hinlah van'a kon'in Pakai vantil in “Abraham, Abraham” tin ahin kouvin ahile, Abraham'in “Pakai keima hikom'a kaum'e,” ati.  
\v 12 Ama chun “Chapang pa chunga na khut nalha louhel ding, imacha jong nalo louding ahi, ajeh chu Pathen nagin jeh in nangman na chapa chang khat seh jeng jong keima adin na khut kihpoi, tihi tun kichen tah in kahedoh tai,” ati.  
\v 13 Chuin Abraham adah doh in avet leh, “Vetan anung langa nanglom lah a kelngoi chal khat akia kihen amun ahi,” hichun Abraham jong achen kelngoi chal chu aga kaiyin achapa khel chun maicham thilto chun atoh in ahi.  
\v 14 Hijeh chun Abraham'in hiche mun chu Yahweh-Yireh (Pathen'in hin ngaito nante) tin asahtai. Tuni geihin hiche “Pathen'in amolsang chung ah hin kingaito nante,” ti thuchih hi akisei jing nalaiye.  
\v 15 Pakai vantil chun vanna kon'in Abraham tin aniveina a ahin koukit in ahi.  
\v 16 Hitin aseiye, “Keima ka tahsa tah a kakihahsel ahitai, hitobang a thil hi nabol ngam jenga na chapa chang khat seh chunga khutkih louva napan jeng phat in, tin Pakaiyin aseiye. \x + \xo 22:16 \xt Heb 6:13,14\x*  
\v 17 Keiman kitah tah a phatthei kaboh ding nahi, chule na chilhah te ahsi jat ka phahsah ding chule vadung panga neldi jat ka sosah ding nahi, na chilhah ten amelma teu kelkot ahin toupha diu ahiye. \x + \xo 22:17 \xt Heb 11:12\x*  
\v 18 Chule nangman ka thusei nangai jeh a leiset chunga namtin vaipi nason na chilhah te vanga phatthei hung kiboh ding ahiuve,” ati. \x + \xo 22:18 \xt Act 3:25\x*  
\v 19 Hichun Abraham asoh teni kom langa ahung kinungle in, chuin ama hon Beersheba lam ajon un, hichea chun Abraham chu Beersheba a aumtai.   
\s1 Nahor chilhah ho  
\p
\v 20 Phat chomkhat jou chun Abraham chu thu aseipeh un Milcah jong hin nasopi pa Nahor to cha pasal phachompi ahing lhone.  
\v 21 Uz chu atahpen ahin, Buz hi ani channa ahin, Ram hingpa Kemuel ahin,  
\v 22 Chesed ahin, Hazo ahin, Pildash ahin, Jidlaph ahin chule Bethuel ahiuve,” ati.  
\v 23 Bethuel chun Rebekah ahing'e. Abraham sopipa Nahor chu Milcah cha hicheng get hi ana hinpeh e.  
\v 24 Hicheng val in jong athaikemnu amin Reumah kiti nu jong chun Tebah toh, Gaham toh, Tahash toh chule Maacah ana hing'e.   
\c 23  
\s1 Abraham in Sarah lhanmun achoh  
\p
\v 1 Sarah chu kum jakhat le kum somni le kum sagi jen ahingin,  
\v 2 Sarah chu Kiriath-arba kiti mun'a athi tan, hichu Hebron kiti Canaan gamsunga um ahi, hichun Abraham chu Sarah umlou jeh a lunghel le mitlhi longin achup in ahi.  
\v 3 Hichun ajinu long adalhah ding jeh in Hit mite ho kom'a aseiyin,  
\v 4 “Keima gam chom mi kahin nangho lah a maljin bou kahi. Gambeh neo khat nei chohsah un, chuti le keiman ka jinu hi phaten kivui thei ing'e,” ati. \x + \xo 23:4 \xt Heb 11:9,13; Act 7:16\x*  
\v 5 Hit mite ho chun Abraham adonbut un,  
\v 6 Ja umtah kapu thuseiyu ngaiyin, nangma Pathen a leng chapa banga keiho lah a uma keiho lhan khuh aphapen khat a khun na thilong chu vui jengin, kalah uva mihem khatcha jong hi alhankhuh na itpeh a na thilong na vuisah louding aumpoi,” atiuve.  
\v 7 Hichun Abraham ading doh in agamsung mipite Hit miho chu salam bol din abohkhup tai.  
\v 8 Abraham'in aseiyin, “Nangman nei kithopi nom kahen ahithei ding le Ephron Zohar chapa kom'a nei seipeh uvin.”  
\v 9 “Ajeh chu agamgi chin a um ama Machpelah songlhan keo khu eipeh theiya ahile ken jong lhan mun'a kaman jing dingin nangho umpet tah hin aman alhingset in peng kate,” ati.  
\v 10 Ephron chu mipi lah a atoupet ahin, Abraham chu adonbut in midang hon jong athusei chu aja cheh un, Hit mite ho khopi sunga um jouse jah ah hitin aseiye.  
\v 11 “Hithei ponte ka Pakai,” tin Abraham chu adonbut e, “Lungset tah in ka thusei hi ngaiyin, keiman ka gamsunga adamlai, atonglai, kapeh ding nahi. Tuhin mipi ho masanga nangma kapeh ding nahi, chule nangman najinu alongdamsa navui thei ahi.”  
\v 12 Abraham chu agam mipi ho masang'a abohkhup kit in,  
\v 13 Hichun Abraham'in Ephron le mipi atou cheng ho jah a aseikit in, “Hithei ponte, lungset tah in ngaiyun, nangho kom'a ka choh nom lheh e, keiman gam man chu kapeh lhing nom e, ka loinu longdamsa kavui theina dingin,” ati.  
\v 14 Hichun Ephron in Abraham adonbut in,  
\v 15 Ka Pakai lungset tah in ngaiyin hiche gam man hi dangka jali ahiye, amavang eini golcha kingailutna hi mantam ahi? Che inlang na loinu longdamsa chu gavui tan ati.  
\v 16 Hichun Abraham chun Ephron in aseijat dangka jali chu apetan, hiche lai phat na kailhang thil man dungjuijin, thil kichoh dan ho chu Hit mite lah a tehse hon amu cheh uve.  
\v 17 Abraham'in Ephron kom'a gam Machpelah kiti Mamre kom'a um chu achodoh tai. Hiche mun in ahop chu ahile atong, adam sung, chule akom'a thingphung um jouse jong ahi.  
\v 18 Abraham dinga chu anei agou ahitan, hichea chun Hit mite kelkot kom'a cheng hon jong ahesoh un ahi.  
\v 19 Phat chomkhat jouvin Abraham'in ajinu Sarah long Machpelah a Mamre kom'a Hebron kiti Canaan gamsunga avuitan ahi.  
\v 20 Aleimun le aleilaiya songlhan keo chu Hit miten alhan mun dingin Abraham achansah tauve.   
\c 24  
\s1 Isaac jinu ding kipui  
\p
\v 1 Abraham chu akum ahung tam lheh tan Pathen'in hatah in anatohna jouse ah phatthei aboh sohkeiye.  
\v 2 Chuin Abraham'in nikhat chu asohte lah a atahpen insung vaihom pa heng ah hitin aseiye, “Nakhut chu kataigui noiya koiyin lang nakihahsel ding ahi.”  
\v 3 Chutengleh Pakai van le leiset sempa min'in kihahsel in hichu nangman kamou ding hi Canaan gamsung tua ichennau mun'a konna hi nahin puilou ding ahi.  
\v 4 Hinlah nangma che inlang keima umna lui gam ka sopiho lah a Isaac ji ding naga puipeh ding ahi ati.  
\v 5 Sohpan Abraham adonbut in “Ijemtin numeinu chu keiho toh hiche gam'a kanung hinjui ding da tale ikalo ding hitam? Ahilouleh keiman nachapa Isaac hi nangma hung kondohna gam a chu kanung puikit thei ding ham?” ati.  
\v 6 Abraham'in adonbut in “Hoitah in gelchen inlang ka chapa vang kholam a na nungpui loubeh ding ahi.”  
\v 7 Pakai van Pathen kanam mite le kapa insunga konna eipui dohpa, ka penna gam'a patna eihin puidoh pan kitepna aneiyin hitin eina seipeh e, nangma chilhah te hiche gam hi kapeh ding nahiuve.  
\v 8 Hinlah numeinu chun na hinjui nomlou le nangma keima dan kitepna a konna ongthol nahitai, thil khat chu ahile ka chapa vang khulam a nanungpui louhel ding ahi.”  
\v 9 Hichu Abraham sohpan apu Abraham taigui noiya akhut akoiyin apun ahilna thudol'a hin akihahsel tai.  
\v 10 Hichun asohpa chun sangongsao som apupa Abraham kom'ah alan thil mantam ajat jat apon Mesopotamia lama Nahor khopi jon din achetai.  
\v 11 Aman sangongsao ho chu twi veina kotong kom'a khopi pam a akichol sah in nilhah langkai ahiphat in numei ho chu twi khai dingin ahung potdoh un ahi.  
\v 12 Chuin Abraham sohpa chun, “O Pakai, kapu Abraham Pathen, tunia nei pilhin sahna dingin na angsunga kataove, kapu Abraham dingin khoto na hin neiyin.”  
\v 13 Vetan keima hiche twikhuh phunga hin kadinge, chule hiche khopi sunga miho chanu te twi khaiya hung ding ahiuve.  
\v 14 Hiche hi kangai chat ahi. Alah uva khatpen pen chu kadoh ding, 'Lungset tah in nakhon a twi chu nei donsah in.' Amanun hitia hi ahin donbut leh, 'Heng'e, donin, chule na sangongsao ho jong keiman hin donsah ing'e!' Hiche nu chu nangman Isaac inneipi a dinga na lhendoh hi ding ahi. Hiche akon a chu keiman ichan geiya kapu chunga guitanlou ngailutna nachan ham ti kahet ding ahi.  
\v 15 Asohpa taona achai masang'in Rebekah numei khangthah nu chun alengkouva twibel ahin pun ahung potdoh tan ahi, Amanu chu Bethuel chanu, Abraham sopipa Nahor le ajinu Milcah toh ahin lhon ahi.  
\v 16 Rebekah chu nungah mel-hoi vetnom nom a mel-hoi khat ahin, chule pasal toh jong kitimatna neikha loulai hel ahiye. Amanu chu twikhuh sunga achelut in a twibel dimset in twi aga kithal in chujouvin ahung kaldoh tai.  
\v 17 Abraham sohpa chu Rebekah kom lama alhai in hitin aseiye, “Lungset tah in nabel a twi chu themkhat nei donsah thei ding ham,” atile,  
\v 18 Rebekah in jong “Henge, kapu nadon thei ma ma ahi.” Chuin amanun a twi chu a lengkouva pat in ahin dom lhan Abraham sohpa chu adonsah tai.  
\v 19 Chuin Rebekah in twi adonsah jou chun, ana khongai tadin “Keiman na sangongsao ho ding jong twi gadom tading'e ati, chule na sangongsao hon adon chimkah sen keiman gathal peh ing'e,” ati.  
\v 20 Hichun Rebekah chu gangtah in atwi poh chu gancha ho twikong sunga alheilhan, twikhuh langa chun twithal dingin a lhaijel kit in amapa sangongsao ho abonchauvin twi adon chimsah sohkeiyin ahi.  
\v 21 Chuphat in sohpan thipbeh in Rebekah umchan chu aven ama akingaiton Pakaiyin kahung kholyin lonapen hi alolhin sah ding khat hitam, hilou ham tin phot chen ding gon Rebekah um chan chu thip beh chan ave ave jengin ahi.  
\v 22 Phat chomkhat jouvin sangongsao ho jousen twi ahin donva cheh tauvin, hichun sohpan sana bilba anah a budin ahin ladoh in chule sana chaojang ni lentah akhut cheng teni a bupeh din ahin ladoh tai.  
\v 23 Amapan adong tan, “Nangma hi koi chanu nahim? Lungset tah in eihin donbut in, napa inmun a chu tujan kaki ngah thei diu ham?” ati.  
\v 24 Amanu'n adonbut in, “Keima hi Bethuel chanu kahi atin, kapu le kapi chu Nahor le Milcah ahi.  
\v 25 Henge, adih e, keihon changpol tamtah kanei jun sangongsao ho nehthei ding, chule jinlhun-in jong kanei uve,” ati.  
\v 26 Hichun sohpa abohkhup in Pakai Pathen athangvah tai.  
\v 27 “Pathen vahchoiyin umhen, kapupa Abraham Pathen” atitai. “Pakaiyin a lungsetna longlou chule phatkimna kapupa amusah tai, ajeh chu ahile imacha boina umlouvin kapu sopite kom'a eipui lhungjel tai.”  
\v 28 Hichun khangthah nungahnu chu gangtah in a inlama alhaijel in ama chunga thilsoh um cheng a insung mite aga hetsah in ahi.  
\v 29 Rebekah chun sopi Laban aneiyin, amapa chun twikhuh lam'a chun ahung gamkon ho kimupi din ahung tai.  
\v 30 Laban chun anah a sana akiba a akhut a sana chaojang akibu chu amu tan, chuleh Rebekah in amaho chung chang thu asei chengse chu ajan, hichun ama alhaidoh pai jin twikhuh umna lama sangongsao ho nunga adin chu amun ahi.  
\v 31 Laban chun ama kom'a,“Nangho ding leh na sangongsao te ding uva mun gottup ahinung a khopam a iti nadin jeng uham? Pathen phatthei boh changho, hungin keiho kom'a hung umin” ati.  
\v 32 Hichun amapa chu Laban toh insung alut tauvin, Laban chun sangongsao ho chu alham lhan changpol ho apen aki choldona diu, chuleh aneh diu jong twi jong sohpa ding, chule sangongsao hoiya pang ho dinga akeng kisop ngimna dingun apen ahi.  
\v 33 Hichun aneh diu an ahung kiluidoh tan ahin Abraham sohpan aseiye, “Kahungna ajeh kasei masang'in imacha kaneh nompoi.” “Aphai,” tin Laban in adonbut in, “Nei seipeh un” ati.  
\v 34 “Keima hi Abraham sohpa kahi,” tin aman aseitai.  
\v 35 Chule Pathen'in kapupa hi hatah in phatthei aboh in ama nei le gou jong ahao thei lheh tan ahi. Chule Pathen'in kelngoi hon, le sa namkim jong anei sah tan, chule sana dangka le soh numei le pasal, sangongsao tamtah jong chule sangan tamtah apetan ahi.  
\v 36 Chuin kapupa loinu Sarah chu akum ahung teh jou nungin, kapupa chapa pasal khat ahingin, kapupan achapa chu anei agou jouse ama apedoh tai.  
\v 37 Hiche a chun kapu Abraham'in eikitep sah in, Aman hitin aseiye, “Nangman hiche ka chapa hi Canaan numei ho toh na kichensah louhel ding ahi.”  
\v 38 “Amavang kapate kom langa, ka insung mite kom lang joh a nache a ka chapa Isaac ji ding nei gapuipeh tan,” ati.  
\v 39 Hinlah keiman kapu ka donbut in “Keiman ipi kalo ding ham? Numei khangthah keima toh hung kinung le ding kamu theilou leh kati'e.  
\v 40 Aman ei donbut in, “Pakai ama umna limnoiya eiumpi pan avantil te nahin solpeh ding nakin jong thupitah a na lolhin sah ding ahi. Adih e! Hijeh a chu ka chapa aloinu ding keima insung miho lah a nahin pui tei ding ahi.  
\v 41 Hiche teng chule, keima a konna na onthol ding ahitai. Kasopi ho lah a naga che a ama hon achanu u chu nang toh hung ding anoplou ule hiche a chun nangma na themmo tapoi.  
\v 42 Hijeh chun tunnin, keima hilai twikhuh mun a hin kataove, O Pakai, kapupa Abraham Pathen tuchung hi kahung kigkonna kin hi lungset tah in nei lolhin sah in kati e.  
\v 43 Ven, keima hilaiya twikhuh kom'a kadin pet ahin, numei khangthah hon hiche twikhuh a twi thal a ahung teng ule hitia hi kasei ding, lungset tah in nakhon a chu twi themkhat nei donsah thei ding ham?  
\v 44 Amanun henge ati a chule keiman na sangongsao ho jouse jong twi ka donsah soh ding ahinti leh amanu chu kapupa chapa Isaac ji dingin nei petai tia kalah ding ahitai.  
\v 45 Keiman ka lungthima katao chai masang'in Rebekah in alengkouva twibel ahin pun twikhuh lam ahin jonin, hichun keiman amanu jah a hitin kaseiye, lungset tah in don ding twi neipen kati e.  
\v 46 Hichun Rebekah in jong gangtah in a lengkouva twibel a twi aput chu ahin domlhan hitin aseitai. Henge aphai, twi nadon thei ahiye chule keiman na gancha Sangongsao ho jouse jong twi donva sah cheh nange ati, hichun ken jong ka donin, sangongsao ho jong abonchauvin twi avahva cheh in ahi.  
\v 47 Hichun keiman ka dongin nangma hi koi chanu nahim katile aman eidonbut in, “Bethuel chanu kahin Nahor le Milcah chu kapu le kapi ahi, hichea chu keiman anah a sana bilba kaba peh a akhut teni a sana chaojang kabu peh ahi,” ati.  
\v 48 Hichun keima ka kunin ka bohkhup in Pakai kavah choiye, kapupa Abraham Pathen chu, ajeh chu Pathen'in lolhing tah in eipuijin ama sopi atute kom lama achapa ji puithei ding mun'a kaum tah jeh in ati.  
\v 49 Nei seipeh in, nangman kilungsetna longlou chule kingailut photchetna hi kapupa nasuh bulhit sah ding ham? Ahilouleh ipi neilo ding ham? Hiche teng chule keiman aban bolbe ding chu kigel tang kate.  
\v 50 Hichun Bethual le Laban in adonbut lhonin, “Pathen'in hikom'a hi nahin pui uchu kanom e keima ho imacha seibe ding kahe pouve.”  
\v 51 Rebekah hi kipuiyun che tauvin nadeima bangin napupa chapa inneipi din kipui tauvin, Pathen'in nahin pui ma bangin ati lhon'e.  
\v 52 Abraham sohpan hiche thu kisei ho jouse chu ajah phat chun tol'a abohkhup in Pathen athangvah tai.  
\v 53 Hichun Abraham sohpan dangka sum eng chule sana khivui, pon mantam ho chu Rebekah apen, hiche tilou chun thil thupi mantam tah Laban le anu jong apen ahi.  
\v 54 Hichun ama hon an ane khomun Abraham sohpa le ahin lhonpi ho jouse hiche jan chun ageh un, hinlah jingkah matah in Abraham sohpan hitin aseiye, “Kapupa kom'a kinungle din neisol tauvin,” ati.  
\v 55 Amavang Laban le anun, “Rebekah chu nisom tobang umbe dingin adei lhon nalaiye. Hiche jou teng amanu chethei tante,” atiuve.  
\v 56 Ahin sohpan nei nichon sah sah tahih un, ajeh chu ka Pakaiyin kahungna kin lenpen tah hi eilolhin sah ahitai. Lungset tah in kapupa kom'a din eiki nungle sah tauvin.  
\v 57 Ama hon aseiyun, “Aphai, Keihon Rebekah kouvung ting, aman ipi agel dong uving e” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 58 Hichun ama hon Rebekah akouvun, “Amapa toh hin nache ding hitam,” tin adong uve. Chuin amanun adonbut in “Henge kache ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 59 Hichun ama hon damsel tauvin tin Rebekah chu alhauvin, Abraham sohpa toh ahin kilhonpi hotoh asol tauvin ahi. Rebekah chu aneova patna ahin sasah nu jong asol peh thauvin amanu toh kilhon ding ahi.  
\v 60 Amaho Rebekah in adalhah kon un hitin phatthei aboh un “Ka sahtah u sopinu, nangman mi asang sang hin hing inlang, na chilhah te jong hat jing'u hen. Ama hon amelma teu kelkot hinkal lhah jing'u hen,” atiuve.  
\v 61 Hichun Rebekah le asoh numei ho chu sangonsao chunga akaldoh un, Abraham sohpa nung chu ajui tauve, Hiti chun Abraham sohpan Rebekah chu apuijin ahung tauve.  
\v 62 Hiche petna chu Isaac chu Beerlahai-roi apat achenna mun Negev lama ahung kinungle pettah ahi.  
\v 63 Nilhah khat Isaac chu avahlen atao dinga ache le pet in phailei lam agahven ahile sangongsang ho ahung chu amun ahi.  
\v 64 Chuin Rebekah agah khodah in ahile Isaac amu phat in sangongsao chunga kon'in ahung kumlha tai.  
\v 65 “Koiham khulanga phailei lama vahle a eiho eigal dot ukhu,” tin Rebekah in sohpa chu adongtan ahi. Chuin Abraham sohpan adonbut in “Ama khu kapupa ahi.” Hichun Rebekah in adel alan akikhu khume.  
\v 66 Hichun sohpan Isaac chu ima jouse thusoh ho chu aseipeh tan ahi.  
\v 67 Chuin Isaac in Rebekah chu anu Sarah ponbuh in na ahin puilut in, aman Rebekah chu aji din asang tan hatah in alungset in, amanu jallin Isaac anun adalhah jouvin alunghemna jouse jong amiltai.   
\c 25  
\s1 Keturah guija peng Abraham chillhah ho  
\p
\v 1 Abraham'in ji khat aneibe kit in, amanu min chu Keturah ahi.  
\v 2 Amanu chun cha hicheng hi ahingin, amaho se chu Zimran ahin, Jokshan ahin, Medan ahin, Midian ahin, Ishbak ahin, chule Shuah ahiuve.  
\v 3 Jokshan chun Sheba le Dedan ahingin, Dedan chilhah ho chu ahile Asshurim ho ahin, Letushim ho ahin, chule Leummim ho jouse jong ahiuve.  
\v 4 Midian chate ho chu Ephah ahin, Epher ahin, Hannoch ahin, Abida ahin chule Eldaah amaho jouse hi Abraham cha Keturah a konna peng ahiuve.  
\v 5 Chule Abraham'in anei jouse achapa Isaac chu apetan ahi.  
\v 6 Amavang Abraham'in athi masangin ajikopte cha ho jouse jong thilpeh anei sohkeiyin chule nisolam gam'a abon'un aki inchonsah tai.   
\s1 Abraham thi le akivui  
\p
\v 7 Abraham chu kum jakhat le kum som sagi le kum nga alhing in;  
\v 8 Hichun Abraham kum sottah ahingin lolhing tah in ahinkho amangin aleiset hinkho abeitai, chuin ama apu apa amite to akivuitha tai.  
\v 9 Chule acha teni Isaac le Ishmael in apa lhon Abraham chu songlhan keova Machpelah achun avui lhon tai. Hichu Mamre kom ahin hiche mun chu Ephron chapa Zohar Hit miho kom'a kichodoh anahi.  
\v 10 Hiche gam hi Abraham'in Hit miho kom'a a inneipi Sarah kivuina dinga ana choh dohna mun chu ahi. \x + \xo 25:10 \xt Semtilbu 23:3-16\x*  
\v 11 Abraham thijou chun, Pathen'in hatah in Isaac chu Negev gam'a Beerlahoi-roi mun a phatthei abohtan ahi.   
\s1 Ishmael chilhah ho  
\p
\v 12 Hiche ho hi Ishmael chilhah Abraham chapa Hagar a konna hung peng Egypt mite numei Sarah sohnu akon ahi.  
\v 13 Anoija ho hi Ishmael chilhah amin, anam, aphung dungjuiya kipe, apeng masa penpa Nebaioth ahin, Kedar ahin, Adbeel ahin, Mibsam ahin,  
\v 14 Mishma ahin, Dumah ahin, Massa ahin,  
\v 15 Hadad ahin, Tema ahin, Jetur ahin Naphish ahin chule Kedemah hicheng hi ahiuve.  
\v 16 Hichengse hi Ishmael chapa te ahiuvin, aminu jong akhotin a kisem a chuleh a ngahmun dungjuiya akilah le aphung khaijin haosa chapa cheh som le ni alhing uve.  
\v 17 Chule Ishmael chu kum jakhat le somthum le sagi ahingin, chuin ama aleiset hinkho abeitan hichun apu apate along lup nauva ama jong akicholdo tai.  
\v 18 Chule Ishmael chilhah te chun gam leiset Havilah apat Shur chan gei alodim un, hiche hi Assyria gam jotna Egypt gamto kinai Asshur a hung kipan ahi. Amaho chu asopi ule nao hotoh kivetda gunset in ana um jing uve.   
\s1 Esau le Jacob pen  
\p
\v 19 Hiche hi Isaac Abraham chapa insung chilhah thusim ahi.  
\v 20 Chuin Isaac kum som li alhin in aji dingin Rebekah Paddan-aram gam'a Bethuel chanu Aramea mi Laban sopinu chu akipuiyin ahi.  
\v 21 Isaac ajinu dingin Pathen heng'a ataovin ahi, ajeh chu ama chanei louva um ahi. Hichun Pathen'in Isaac taona chu asanpeh tan ahile Rebekah chu ahung kikopmo tan naosen ni ahung kijil tan ahi.  
\v 22 Hinlah naosen teni chu anu naobu sunga ahung kiboi jing lhonin hichun amanu Pathen dong dingin achen hiche hi itidan ham? ati.  
\v 23 Pathen'in amanu ahoulimpi in, “Naobu sunga naocha teni chu nampi ni hung hi ding hiche nam teni hi abulla patna hung kitohmo peh lhon ding ahi, nam teni lah a khat hung hat intin, nacha teni lah a aupan anaopa chu ahin jenle ding ahi”. \x + \xo 25:23 \xt Rm 9:12\x*  
\v 24 Chuin nao neina ding phat ahung lhin chun Rebekah in naoni avop chu ahin kihet chen bep in ahi.  
\v 25 Chuin ahung peng masa pa chu asanin atahsa pumpi chu amulin atom in hichun ama chu Esau asah tauvin ahi.  
\v 26 Phat chomkhat jou chun asopipa ahung penglha tan akhut teni achun a upa keng atuh chah kheh in, hichea chun amapa min chu Jacob asah un, ajinun amani ahinpeh pet hin Isaac chu kum som gup ana lhingtai.   
\s1 Esau in mi upa hina akijoh  
\p
\v 27 Chapang teni chu ahung khanglen lhonin, Esau chu gamleng sakap them gam vahmi ahung hikhan, Jacob vang chu mi mong khat ahin pondal buh a um jing mi ahi.  
\v 28 Isaac in asadelsa hin pohlut aneh jing jeh in Esau angailun, hinlah Rebekah in Jacob chu alungset lheh in ahi.  
\v 29 Nikhat chu Jacob in changchim ahon pet in Esau chu agamlen na a kon'in ahunglhung in, nasatah in agil akeltan atha alhasam lheh tan ahi.  
\v 30 Hijeh chun Esau in Jacob jah a hitin aseitai, “Kagil akel valtai na changchim hon salenglung chu them khat neipe tan” ati. Hijeh a chu amapa min Edom kisah ahi.  
\v 31 Aphai, tin Jacob in adonbut in, “Amasapen in upa nahina chu neipe doh tan,” ati.  
\v 32 Esau in hitin aseiye, “Keima gilkella thi dinga um kahi tan hiche mi upa chu ipi kaphat chompi ding ham?”  
\v 33 Jacob in asei kit in, “Amasa pen a nakihahsel angaiye,” hichun Esau chu akihahsel tan mi upa ahina chu Jacob kom'a akijoh doh tai. \x + \xo 25:33 \xt Heb 12:16\x*  
\v 34 Hichun Jacob in Esau chu changlhah toh changnoi apetan hichun aman anevan adon chimset in akithoudoh in achetai, Hichun Esau in mi upa ahina chu akijoh dohtai.   
\c 26  
\s1 Isaac le Abimelech  
\p
\v 1 Chuin gamsunga chun nasatah in kel ahung lhatan, hiche kellhah chu Abraham damlaiya ahah tobangin, Isaac chu Gerar langa Philistine lengpa Abimelech heng a achetai.  
\v 2 Chuin Pathen'in Isaac chu ahoulimpin hitin aseiye, “Keima thusei ngaiyin, Egypt langa nache thei louding ahi.  
\v 3 Chule nangma hiche gam a hin gampam kholjin mi bangin um'in keiman hatah a phatthei kaboh ding nahi. Chule gam jouse hi nangma le na chilhah te jouse kapeh ding nahi, ajeh chu keiman napa Abraham kom'a kakihahselna kamolso tei ding ahi. \x + \xo 26:3 \xt Semtilbu 22:16-18\x*  
\v 4 Keiman na chilhah te van chunga ahsite jat banga kapunsah ding, hiche gam ho jouse hi kapeh ding, chule nangma chilhah te a konna vannoi mijouse phatthei kaboh ding ahi.  
\v 5 Hiche ho jouse hi kabol ding ahi. Ajeh chu Abraham'in kathu angaiyin, ka thulhahna ahin, ka thupeh ahin, ka chondan thu ahin, chule ka danthu anitsoh keiyin ahi.  
\v 6 Hichun Isaac Gerar gam'a acheng tan ahi.  
\v 7 Hiche gam'a cheng miho chun Isaac jinu Rebekah chu koi ham tia adoh ule aman adonbut in, “Kasopinu ahi ati peh e,” Ajeh chu hiche miho hin Rebekah jeh hin, “Keima eitha lo get uvinte tia anagel jeh a ka sopinu ahi anati ahiye. Ajeh chu amanu amel-hoi jeh ahi.” \x + \xo 26:7 \xt Semtilbu 12:13; 20:2\x*  
\v 8 Hinlah ni phabep jou chun Abimelech Philistine lengpan bangkot a kon agahven ahile vetan Isaac in Rebekah aji bol'a akinoupi pet amudoh tai.  
\v 9 Hichun gang tah in Abimelech in Isaac chu akouvin, “Amanu chu na jinu hilou ham! Ibola amanu chu ka sopinu ahe tia nasei ham?” Isaac in adonbut in, “Ka seina ajeh chu ahile ka innneipi jeh a koi tobang khat in eitha lo ding ham kati ahi.”  
\v 10 Abimelech in aseiye, “Ipi dinga hiti pia chu neibol'u hitam? Ilouthem khat in ka mite lah a khat touvin na jinu chu ana kipui hen ana luppi kha tahen lang hileh nangma jeh a kei hon chonset lentah a neilhah sah ding'u hita chula em.”  
\v 11 Hichun Abimelech in danpi khat asemin mipi jouse henga aphongdoh in ahi, “Koi hijongleh hiche mipa hihen ajinu hijongleh ahin tongkha asuse aum leh thina chan a gotna kipe ding ahi.”  
\v 12 Hiche kum chun Isaac in muchi akitun ahile kum dang sang'in ajat jakhat val jena tamjon aki-at e, hiti chun Pakaiyin ama phatthei ana boh e.  
\v 13 Chua kon chun Isaac chu nei le gouvin ahung haodoh tan, anei le agou hatah in apunbe cheh, apunbe cheh jengin ahi.  
\v 14 Hitobang chun nei le gou keu hilouvin kelngoi jong, keltah jong, bonghon jong chule soh le kol jong tamtah ahin neitan, hiche ho jeh hin Philistine miten nasatah in ahung engse tauvin ahi.  
\v 15 Hichun Philistine miho chu athangthip jeh un Isaac twikhuh jouse chu abonchan asuhbing peh tauvin ahi. Hiche twikhuh ho sese hi apa Abraham adamlaiya asohten analai hou chu ahi.  
\v 16 Chuin Abimelech in achaina in Isaac kom'a aseiye, “Nangma keiho kom'a kon'in chedoh tan ajeh chu nangma keiho sang'in natha lhing jotai,” ati.  
\v 17 Hichun Isaac chu amaho kom'a kon'in achen Gerar phaicham ah amaho ponbuh akison uvin hiche mun achun acheng tauve.  
\v 18 Chuin Isaac in Apa Abraham thi jouva Philistine mipiten ana huhbing peh u twikhuh ho sese chu alaihong kit in apa Abraham'in ana minsah twikhuh min ho chu avelsah kit in asemhoi sah kit tai.  
\v 19 Isaac sohten Gerar phaicham chu twikhuh alai uva ahile twisam phungkhat alaidoh tauve.  
\v 20 Ahin Gerar gam'a kelngoi chinghon Isaac kelngoi chingho kom'a chun “Hiche twikhuh hi keiho twikhuh ahi,” atiuvin akinelpi tauvin ahi; hichun Isaac in hiche twikhuh chu “Esek” asah in hichun avetsah chu “Kiboina mun,” tina ahi.  
\v 21 Hichun Isaac sohten twikhuh adang khat alaikit un ahile hiche mun jong chu boina ahung um kittan hichun Isaac in “Sitnah” (Tichu kitomona mun tina ahi) asah tan ahi.  
\v 22 Chuin Isaac in hiche mun chu adalhan akichon in twikhuh chom beh khat alai kit in ahile hiche mun a vang chun akinahpi tapouvin ahi, hijeh chun Isaac in hiche mun chu “Rehoboth” asah tai. “Ajeh chu tun vang Pathen'in eiho dingin gam eihon peh tauve, agamsung ahin eiho cha le naovin pungjal tau hite,” ati.  
\v 23 Hiche mun a pat chun Isaac chu Beersheba ah akichon kittai.  
\v 24 Hiche jan lele chun Isaac henga Pathen ahung kilah in “Keima napa Abraham Pathen chu kahi. Imacha kichatna nei hihbeh in ajeh chu keiman nangma kaumpi jing nai, chule phatthei kaboh ding nahi, nason na chilhah te jong hatah a ka punsah ding amaho nam lentah kaso ding ahi. Hiche ho hi kasuh bulhing ding ahi. Ajeh chu kasohpa Abraham kom'a kana kitepnasa ahi.”  
\v 25 Hichun Isaac in hiche mun achun maicham asemin Pathen ahou tai, chule aman aponbuh jong asongdoh kit in asohten twikhuh khat alaikit un ahi.  
\v 26 Nikhat chu Abimelech jong Gerar gam'a pat na semangpa Ahuzzath chule asepai lamkai Phicol akipuiyin Isaac to kimuto dingin ahungtai. \x + \xo 26:26 \xt Semtilbu 21:22\x*  
\v 27 Isaac in amaho chu adongin, “Ipi dinga ka henga hung nahiuvem?, Nei vetda uva nagam uva patna nei nodoh u hitalou hamm,” anatin ahi.  
\v 28 Ama hon adonbut un, “Keihon Pathen'in nangma na umpi hi phate chan kamu chen tauve. Hijeh chun nangho le keiho kikah a kihou cham ding kanom ui, chule ikah uva kitepna khat sem kanom uve.  
\v 29 Ahithei le kihou chamna inei thei ding'u dei aum lheh e, keima hon jong nangho chunga imacha bolse pou ving'e, kei hon nangho ka ngailu jing uve. Chule lung damsel a ka soldoh joh nahiuve. Chule tun nangho Pathen'in nasatah in phatthei naboh tauve.  
\v 30 Hichun Isaac in kinoptona ankong nehkhomna asemin ama hon abonchauvin anekhom un adonkhom un ahi.  
\v 31 Ajingin jingpi matah in akithouvun amaho khat khat in kitepna anei uvin, hichun Isaac in amaho chu a inlam uva asolkit tan, amaho jong lunglhai sel in akinung le tauve.  
\v 32 Hiche ni ma ma chun Isaac sohten twisam thah khat alaidoh u chu thu ahung peuvin ama hon aseiyun, “Keihon twisam thah khat kamu uve,” ahung tiuve.  
\v 33 Hichun Isaac in twisam thah chu Shibah asah tai (hichu kinoptona tina ahi). Hiche nia patna chu tuni gei a hi Beersheba khopi kiti ahiye.  
\v 34 Esau chu kum somli alhin chun Hit mite numei Beeri chanu Judith le Hit mi mama Elon chanu Basemath chu ji dingin akipui jin ahi.  
\v 35 Amavang Esau ji teni chu Isaac le Rebekah din thohlel aum lheh jeng lhonin ahi.   
\c 27  
\s1 Jacob in Isaac phatthei aboh  
\p
\v 1 Ateh a kho amu chenlou nung hin nikhat hi Isaac in achapa alenjo pa chu akouve.  
\v 2 “Ka chapa! Keima hi ateh kahitai, itih a thi ding kahim kasei thei tapoi,  
\v 3 Hijeh chun tun nangma kigong inlang na manchah nathalpi kigot inlang gamlah a kei ding sa gakap in.  
\v 4 Chutengleh keiman kadu lamtah in hin hon inlang hinchoi jin keiman kaneh ding chutengleh nangma hi kahinkho abei masanga phatthei kaboh ding nahi ati.  
\v 5 Ahin Isaac le Esau kihouna chu Rebekah in guhthim chan ana ngaijin hichun Esau chu gamleng dinga akondoh phat in;  
\v 6 Rebekah in Jacob jah a hitin aseiye, “Ngaijin, napa Isaac in na upa Esau hitin ahoulimpi kaja e,” ati.  
\v 7 “Sa neiga delpeh inlang kadu lamtah in hin hon inlang hinchoijin keiman ne ingting chule Pathen masanga phatthei kaboh ding nahi, kahinkho abei masang'in,” ati.  
\v 8 Hijeh chun tun kachapa ka thusei hi phate chan ngaiyin ka thusei ho hi najui ding ahi.  
\v 9 “Nangma kelngoi hon lah a gachen lang ahoitah cheh anouni hin kaijin chutengleh keiman napa dulamtah a kahon peh ding ahi.  
\v 10 Hiche teng chule nangman napa kom'a nachoi ding aman aneh a aneh jou teng phatthei naboh ding ahi, ama ahinkho adampet ahi,” ati.  
\v 11 Ahin Jacob in anu Rebekah adonbut in ajah a, “Vetem in ka upa Esau a tichung amulin ahin keima vounem a timullou kahi.  
\v 12 I kati ding ham? Kapa in eihin jut le ta le jou a kabol ahin hetdoh leh koi phatthei chan sanga sapsetna joh kachan joh ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 13 Hinlah anu Rebekah in adonbut in, “Sapsetna ho aum le abon'in keiman kipoh tang kate ati, chapa bol in kati ho hi nabol angaiye, che inlang kelngoi chu kahenga hin kailut loiyin ati!”  
\v 14 Hichun Jacob jong achen kelngoi chu anu kom'a ahin kailut tai. Chuin anun jong apa dulam tah in ahon peh tai.  
\v 15 Hichun Esau vonho lah a aphapen chu insunga kon'in agala doh in achapa aneojo pa Jacob chu avonpeh tan ahi.  
\v 16 Chule kelngoi nou teni mul chu akhut teni le angong amul bei lai achun atompeh in ahi.  
\v 17 Hichun Rebekah in sa tuitah a ahon chule changlhah ama semsa chu achapa Jacob khut a apetan ahi.  
\v 18 Hichun Jacob in changlhah le kelsa chu apa aga pen “Hepa” atileh aman jong “Hoiyo koipen nahim ka chapa?”  
\v 19 Jacob in adonbut in, “Keima Esau na chapa apeng masa chu kahi,” ati. “Keiman kahin subulhit tai nei ngansena chu lungset tah in kithou inlang kahin choi sa tuitah a kihon hi ne inlang phatthei neiboh tan,” ati.  
\v 20 Chuin Isaac in achapa chu adonbut in, “Iti dan ham? Man gangtah in nahin vaidoh loijen in ka chapa,” atile aman jong adonbut in “Pakai na Pathen'in gangtah a eihin lolhin sah ahi bouve,” ati.  
\v 21 Hichun Isaac in Jacob henga, “Hung kikhin naijin katham phah theina din, nangma hi ka chapa Esau nahi mong hinam nahilou ham na jutle tem inge.”  
\v 22 Hijeh chun Jacob in apa Isaac anailut in ahile ahin jutle tan ahi, “A awso hila Jacob awso ahin, akhut teni vang hi Esau khut ahi ngal in,” atin ahi.  
\v 23 Amavang Jacob ahi chu ahetchen theilou ahitai, ajeh chu Jacob khut chu a upa Esau khut tobanga mul ahijeh in hichun Isaac chun Jacob chu phatthei abohtan ahi.  
\v 24 Isaac in adong pha kit leuvin, “Nangma hi kachapa Esau nahi mong hinam?” atile, Jacob in adonbut in “Ka hinai,” ati.  
\v 25 Chuphat in Isaac in aseiye, “Ka henga hin domnai tan nangma phatthei kaboh theina dingin ka chapan gangtah a naga matsa nahon chu ne ing kate,” ati, chuin Jacob in ahin doppeh phat in anen chule lengpitwi jong ahin doppeh in ahile Isaac chun adon tai.  
\v 26 Hichun apa Isaac chun ajah a “Eihin nailut inlang neihin bengchop tem in ka chapa,” atile,  
\v 27 Jacob in anai pheijin apa chu abengchop tai, chuin Isaac kivonna ho gimnam chu anah le len chuin achapa chu phatthei aboh in hitin aseiye, “Ah! Kachapa gimnam hi Pakai phatthei bohsa gamlah gimnam abang'e! \x + \xo 27:27 \xt Heb 11:20\x*  
\v 28 Tun Pakai Pathen'in van'a kon'in daitwi na chap jing hen, leiset a leipha lailai nachan sah jing hen; chule chang le mim chule juning ninglhin sah jing hen.  
\v 29 Nam simsen louvin naja hen chule mihem tamtah nangma noija kun cheh hen lang, nasopi ho chunga vai hin hom jingin lang; nanu sunga peng doh pasal jouse jong na henga kun cheh uhen. Nangma na gaosapte chu gaosap chang hen, chule nangma phatthei na bohte chu phattheiboh chang hen,” ati. \x + \xo 27:29 \xt Semtilbu 12:3\x*  
\v 30 Isaac in Jacob phatthei aboh chai chai jin, Jacob in apa angsung agah dalhah ding kon chet in a upa Esau chu agam lenna a kon'in ahunglhung pai jeng tai.  
\v 31 Chuin Esau in jong neh ding a althet in ahonpeh in apa henga ahin doppeh in apa jah a aseitai. “Hepa, hung kithouvin lang, na hai hai pet a phatthei neiboh na dingin na chapa thasa hi hung ne o,” ati.  
\v 32 Ahin Isaac in adonbut in, “Nang koi nahim?” Esau in adonbut in, “Na chapa apeng masa, Esau kahi,” ati.  
\v 33 Isaac hatah in ati akithing tan aseiye, “Koiham ijo langa hin dom a hunga chu? Keiman ama hin dop chu kana ne tai. Nangma hung lhun masang jep chun phatthei jong ka boh joutai; phattheina jouse jong ama achang jou tai!”  
\v 34 Chuin Esau in apa thusei jouse chu angai chai sohhel phat in Esau jong ha kan akap in hatah in alunghang in apa kom'a atao kit in, “Hepa, keima jong phatthei nei boh teitei in ong,” ati.  
\v 35 Hinlah Isaac in aseiye, “Na sopipa ahungin eihung lhemlha tai, nang phatthei na chan ding jouse na lahpeh gamtai.”  
\v 36 Esau in adonbut in, “Hiche jeh a chu amin Jacob kisah hitei jinte ong? Ajeh chu aman nivei jen eilhep lhah ahitai, phat masa in ka upat hina eina lahpeh in, tun ka phatthei chan ding ana kilah doh kit e, atin hichun keiya dinga phatthei khat beh jong neina khen pehlou hitam?” atile, \x + \xo 27:36 \xt Semtilbu 25:29-34\x*  
\v 37 Isaac in Esau adonbut in, “Keiman Jacob chu nangma chunga vaihom dingin kakoi tai, chule asopite jouse ama noija kun cheh diu, chule chang le mim ahin, juning ahin, haotheina jong kapeh ahitai, tua hijat nunga nangma ipi kabolpeh thei nahlai ding ham kachapa?” atitai.  
\v 38 Ahi vang'in Esau in apa jah a “O hepa, phattheina khat chabeh jong umlou hitam? Phatthei neiboh teiteijin ong, hepa!” atin apengin akaptai. \x + \xo 27:38 \xt Heb 12:17\x*  
\v 39 Chuin apa Isaac in ahoupin ajah a “Nangma leichung phalou lah lah a cheng ding nahi tan, chule van daitwi in jong hin chapkha taponte. \x + \xo 27:39 \xt Heb 11:20\x*  
\v 40 Nangma na chemjam a naki vah ding chule na sopipa noija na um ding ahin nangma na hung ki-ondoh teng vang leh nangong chang'a konna ama namkol chu na pailhah ding ahitai,” ati. \x + \xo 27:40 \xt Semtilbu 36:8; 2 Lengte 8:20\x*   
\s1 Haran gam'a Jacob kisol mang  
\p
\v 41 Hiche phat a pat a chu Esau in Jacob chu hatah a ahin vetda pan ahitai; ajeh chu apa Isaac in phattheina jouse Jacob aboh jeh ahi. Chule Esau in alungthim sunga hitin agel tan, “Kapa hin nikho jong hi sot tapon tin akichai tengleh keiman ka naopa Jacob hi katha ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 42 Ahin achapa alenjo Esau lungthim tohgon jouse chu Rebekah jah a aki seidoh khah tan ahin Rebekah in mi asol'in achapa neojopa Jacob chu aga kousah in ajah a aseipehtai, “Ngaiyin, na upa Esau khun nang thana dingin lungthim tohgon anei tai.  
\v 43 Chapa, chingthei tah in ngai jin, tun kigong inlang kasopipa Laban kom Haran langa jam tan.  
\v 44 Hiche mun achun ni ijat hijongleh na upa Esau lungdam kahsen ga umtan.  
\v 45 Ama ahung lungdam a na bolsetna ho asuhmil hel'a ahung lungdam mong mong tengleh keiman mi hinsol ing ting nahung holdoh sah nang'e. Nang ni ucha nikhat a na manthah lhon ding ka nompoi.”  
\v 46 Hichun Rebekah in Isaac kom'a aseiye, “Keiman hiche Hit mite numei ho ka theichim behseh jeng tai! Ijem tin Jacob in hiche numei ho jin ahin kipui kit ding kagel theipoi kathilo tei ding ahi,” ati.   
\c 28  
\s1 Esau le Mahalath kichen  
\p
\v 1 Hichun Isaac in Jacob akouvin, phatthei aboh in chule athulhah in ajah a hitin aseiye, “Nangman hiche Canaan numei ho hi jia nakipui thei louhel ding ahi;  
\v 2 Hijeh chun gangtah in kipatdoh inlang Padan-Ram a nanu upa Bethuel in a chen chukoma kon chun nanu sopipa Laban chanute joh ga kipui tan.  
\v 3 Pa Pathen'in phatthei naboh hen lang nacha nanao thalhinsah hen, napunsah hen, chule amaho chu nam lentah hung himaiyu hen.  
\v 4 Pathen'in nangma le na chilhah te chunga phatthei naboh uhen, napu Abraham kom'a ana kitepna ho chu tua nangma na khopemna gam jong hi nahin losoh ding ahi, ajeh chu Pathen'in Abraham ana pehsa ahitai. \x + \xo 28:4 \xt Semtilbu 17:4-8\x*  
\v 5 Chule Isaac in Jacob chu asol mang tai, ama jong Paddan-aram langa Jacob le Esau hingnu Rebekah sopipa Laban, Aramea mi Bethuel chapa henga achetai.  
\v 6 Esau in ahechen tai apa Isaac in Jacob phatthei aboh a Paddan-aram langa numei ji a gakipui dinga aphatsah a, chule phatthei aboh pet a agihsal a “Nangman hiche Canaan numei ho ji a nakipui ahi,” tia aseipeh jong aja tai.  
\v 7 Chule Jacob in apa le anu thu angaiyin Paddan-aram lam'ah achetai.  
\v 8 Chule Esau chun Canaan numei ho chunga apa Isaac alunglhai poi ti ahechen tai.  
\v 9 Hichun Esau jong apu Ishmael henga achen Abraham chapa Ishmael chanu Nebaioth sopinu Mahalath chu aji masa teni belap dingin aga kipui ben ahi.   
\s1 Bethel'a Jacob mang  
\p
\v 10 Chule Jacob in Beersheba chu adalhan Haran lang ajontai.  
\v 11 Hiti chun gamkimlai khat ahung geidon hin nisan alhumden tan, hichun ama jong jan chun chukom mun'a ageh dentai, agena mun'a songho khat chu alan lukhap in aneiyin ahi.  
\v 12 Ama hiti chun alup lhah chun amanga kalbi saotah kido amun leiset apat vanthamjol geiya kidolut amun, hichun Jacob in Pakai vantil te akaltou akumsuh jingu chu amun ahi. \x + \xo 28:12 \xt Jn 1:51\x*  
\v 13 Chule kalbi achung langa chun Pakai adingin hitin aseiye, “Keima Pakai Pathen napu Abraham Pathen napa Isaac Pathen kahi. Tua naki choldona mun ho hi nangma leh na chilhah te kapeh doh ahitai. \x + \xo 28:13 \xt Semtilbu 13:14,15\x*  
\v 14 Na chilhah te chu tol'a leivui ja kaphahsah ding amaho chun solam, lhumlam, sahlam, lhanglam aboncha ahin lodim soh dingu ahi, chule leiset chunga nangma le na insung mite jeh a vannoi phatthei kaboh ding ahi. \x + \xo 28:14 \xt Semtilbu 12:3; 22:18\x*  
\v 15 Itih chan hijongleh nangma kaumpi jing ding nache nachan a nikhat teng hiche gam'a hi kahin nung puilut kit ding nahi, ajeh chu kakitepna jouse kasuh bulhit masangse a donlouva kakoi louhel ding nahi.  
\v 16 Hichun Jacob a imutna kon'in ahung khangdoh in hitin aseiye, “Hikom ahin Pathen aum mong'e tihi kana hetphah lou ahi.”  
\v 17 Hinlah ama chu tijatnan adimin hitin aseiye, “Hiche lai mun hi Pathen In ahilouleh thil dang imacha ahi tapoi; chujongleh hiche lai hi van gam kelkot phung ahi bouve,” ati.  
\v 18 Hichun Jacob jingkah matah in athouvin alukhap song chu alan khom phun aphut in achunga chun thao twi asun khumin ahi.  
\v 19 Hiche mun chu Bethel asah tai (hichu “Pathen Hou-In” tina ahi), phat masalai chun Luz tin ana kihei.  
\v 20 Hichun Jacob in kigahna khat aneiyin, “Keima Pathen'in eiumpi jing le kakhol jinna hi kaneh ding bu chuleh sil le chen eipeh ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 21 Chule keima kapa in damsel a einung puilhung kitleh ama chu ka Pakai Pathen dihtah mong ahi tia ding det kahitai.  
\v 22 Chule hiche song khomphu a ka phudoh hi Pathen houna in kiti ding ahi. Chuleh Pathen'in eipeh jouse hi hopsom a hopkhat nangma kapeh ding ahi, ati.   
\c 29  
\s1 Jacob in Rachel amudoh  
\p
\v 1 Hichun Jacob akhol che chu abanjom in solam mite gam chu ahunglhung tai.  
\v 2 Chuin aman agahven ahile loulaiya twisam amun akom'a chun kelngoi hon loi thum'a akol jong amun hiche gancha ho chu twikulla don ding twi ngah ahiuve, chule twisam chu songpi lentah in adal khum ahi.  
\v 3 Hitia chu kelngoi hon ho abkonna ahung kisuhkim tengu leh kelngoi ching hon twikhuh kamsin songpi chu akhindoh jiuva kelngoi te twi achipsah jiuva achipva teng ule song chu akikoina ngai ngai twikhuh kam a chu ale khinlut kit jiu ahi.  
\v 4 Chuin Jacob in amaho jah a “Sopite ho hoiya hung kon nahiu ham?” Atile ama hon adonbut un “Keiho Haran gam'a hung kon kahiuve,” ati.  
\v 5 Amapan adong kit in “Nahor chapa Laban chu nahet khah hih uvem?” atile “Ama hon jong kahe nauve,” atiuve.  
\v 6 Chuin Jacob in ajah uva “Ama chu dam dam a hinam?” tia adoh leh ama hon “Henge, adam jingnai; ven, tua hung kelngoihon toh hung kilhon khu achanu Rachel hija khu,” atiuve.  
\v 7 Jacob in amaho jah a “Tuhin nisa sangtah hinalaija gancha hoi khom phat bon hilou lai, kelngoi hon chu twi chipsah uvin lang gavah pha uvin,” ati.  
\v 8 Ama hon adonbut un, “Gancha ho jouse ahung kikim tokah in twi kipe thei ponte atiuve, hichun kelngoi chingho chun songpi chu twisam kot apat chun atangdoh un kelngoi hon jouse twija ka vahva ding ahi,” atiuve.  
\v 9 Ama hon hitia akihoulim pet tah uchun Rachel chu apa kelngoi hon hotoh ahung kijot luttai, ajeh chu amanu jong kelngoi chinga pang ahiye.  
\v 10 Hichun Jacob in anu sopipa Laban chanu Rachel le anu sopipa Laban kelngoite amu phat in anailut in twikhuh kamsin songpi chu alihdoh in apupa kelngoi hon chu twi achip sah in ahi.  
\v 11 Hichun Jacob in Rachel chu abeng chop in awging tah in akap e.  
\v 12 Jacob in Rachel jah a apa sopinu Rebekah chapa ahi thusim aseipeh tan ahile Rachel chu achen apa aga hetsah tan ahi.  
\v 13 Laban in Jacob asopinu chapa ahung lhun ahet chun akimupin akoijin achop jengin chuin a inlama ahin puilut tai. Hichun Jacob in ima jouse thusim ho chu aseipeh tai.  
\v 14 Chuin Laban in Jacob henga aseiye, “Nangma hi kagu ka chang chule kaphe kavou mong nahi,” ati. Hichun Jacob chu apu Laban kom'a lhakhat sung aumtai.  
\v 15 Laban in Jacob henga aseiye, “Nangma hi ka insungmi nahi vang'in mohseh a tohman beiya naum ding chu adih theipoi, natoh man ipi hi ding ham nei seipeh temin tin adong tai.”   
\s1 Jacob in Leah le Rachel akichenpi  
\p
\v 16 Laban in chanu ni aneiyin, alenjo nu min chu Leah ahin, chule aneojo nu min chu Rachel ahi.  
\v 17 Ahin Leah mit chu aleng thimin amavang Rachel chu amel-hoi jin, amaiso jong lungset aum lheh jenge.  
\v 18 Jacob in Rachel chu hatah a adeichat jeh in hitin aseiye, “Na chanu neojo nu Rachel khu kaji dia neipeh ding leh keiman kum sagi nana tong ing kate,” ati.  
\v 19 Laban in adonbut in, “Hithei nante,” ati. “Ajeh chu keiman midang ho kapeh sanga nangma kapeh ding chu thilphajo ahi bouve, Hijeh chun keima kom'a um jingtan,” ati.  
\v 20 Hichun Jacob in kum sagi sungin Rachel man toh kitoh dingin na atong tan, hinlah Jacob in Rachel angailut behset jeh chun ni chomcha toh abahsah in ahi.  
\v 21 Chujouvin Jacob in Laban jah a hitin aseiye, “Keiman ka kitepna ho jouse ka subulhit tai, kajinu tun neipe tan kaluppi nom tai,” tin ahung thum tai.  
\v 22 Hichun Laban in jet le veija cheng ule nao jouse akou khom sohkeiyin kichenna golvah chu aboltai.  
\v 23 Hinlah hiche jan ahung thim phat chun Laban in Leah chu Jacob kom'a aga that lutpeh tan, Jacob in hichenu chu alupkhompi tai.  
\v 24 Laban in asohnu Zilpah jong chu Leah kithopi a pang dingin apehtha tai.  
\v 25 Ahin jingkah matah in Jacob ahung kitho leh Leah joh anahin, Jacob in Laban jah a aseiyin, “Ipi iti a hitia hi neibol hitam? Kum sagi nangma noiya na kana toh chu Rachel man dinga katoh hilou ham! “Ibol a nei jou lhep ham?” tin aseiye.  
\v 26 Laban in adonbut in “Keiho chondan a a unu umpet a hi anaonu jinei doh theilou ahi.”  
\v 27 “Hiche hapta khat sung hin jinei dan hi subulhit tadin, hiche teng chule Rachel jong kapeh ding nahi, ahin nangman kum sagi ma kana natoh kit ding ahi” ati peh e.  
\v 28 Chuin Jacob in Leah chu hapta khat lhingin akichenpin hiche jou chun Laban in Rachel jong ajinu dingin apetai.  
\v 29 Laban'in asohnu, Bilhah jong chu achanu Rachel jenle a pang dingin apehtha tai.  
\v 30 Hichun Jacob in Rachel jong alupkhompi tan, aman Rachel chu Leah sang'in hatah in adeijon, hichun Jacob in kum sagi ma Laban na atongkit in ahi.   
\s1 Jacob chate  
\p
\v 31 Ahin Pathen'in Leah kihot bol chu amudoh tan, hijeh chun anaobu ahondoh peh in, amavang Rachel chu achiingin chanei louvin aumtai.  
\v 32 Leah vang chu achung agih tan; chapa khat ahingin amin Reuben asah tai, Ijeh inem itile, “Pathen'in kagimna ho eihetpeh tai, hiche jeh a hi kajipan eilungset ding ahitai,” ati.  
\v 33 Chuin aman nao avop kit in chapa khat ahing kittai, ajeh chu “Keima eikihot bol hi Pakaiyin ajah doh phat a chapa hiche jong hi eipeh kit ahiye” atin hijeh chun amin Simeon asah tai.  
\v 34 Hichun Leah achung gih in, nao avop kittan amanun hitin aseiye, “Tu apat a hi kajipa toh thakhat tipum khat kahi lhon ding ahitai, ajeh chu keiman cha pasal thum kahinpeh tai hichun naosen chu amin chu Levi asah tai.”  
\v 35 Chujouvin Leah in nao avop kit in chapa khat ahingin, “Tuchunga vang Pakai ka thangvahna ding ahi,” atin hijeh chun amin Judah asah tai, chujou apat in vang cha abang tan ahi.   
\c 30  
\p
\v 1 Hichun Rachel'in Jacob cha ahinpeh lou akihetchet phat in asopinu athangset pin, hijeh chun Jacob kom'a atao tan, “Keijong cha le nao nei hinpeh in achuti louleh keima thi ding kanom jotai!” atin ahi.  
\v 2 Jacob chu Rachel chunga alunghang jah jengin, “Keima Pathen kahipoi Ama ahi chanei louva nakoi, na naobu khah tan achu!” ati.  
\v 3 Hichun Rachel in adonbut in, “Kasohnu, Bilhah hi, galup khompi tan, chutile amanun nao eihinpeh intin chua konna chu keiman jong ka chilhah insung kaki semdoh thei ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 4 Rachel in Bilhah, asohnu chu, Jacob ji din apetai chuin Jacob in Bilhah chu akitimatpi tai.  
\v 5 Bilhah in nao ahinvop in Jacob dingin chapa khat ahinpeh tai.  
\v 6 Hichun Rachel in aseiye, “Pathen'in ka lunggel eisuh bulhitpeh tai! Chule kataona jong eisanpeh in chapa eipe tai” atin hijeh chun naosen min chu Dan asahtai.”  
\v 7 Chuin Rachel sohnu Bilhah chun nao avopkit in Jacob chapa anina ahinpeh kittai.  
\v 8 Hichun Rachel'in, “Keiman ka sopinu toh hatah a kaki set delna lhon a keiman kajou tai!” atin hichun naosen min chu Naphtali asah tai.  
\v 9 Leah in nao aneikit tah louding ahin kihetdoh phat in asohnu Zilpah chu jidin apetai.  
\v 10 Hijeh chun Leah sohnu Zilpah chun Jacob dingin chapa khat ahinpeh tai.  
\v 11 Hichun Leah in hitin aseiye, “Hamphat aum bouve,” atin naosen min chu “Gad” asah tai.  
\v 12 Hichun Leah sohnu Zilpah chun Jacob chapa anina chu ahinpeh kit in ahi.  
\v 13 Leah chun aseiye, “Keiya din iti thanop um hitam! Tua hi numei dang jousen hatah a eikipapi diu ahitai,” atin hiche naosen min chu Asher asah tai.  
\v 14 Nikhat Reuben chu suhlou chang vohlai in akondoh in ahile loulai achun *Joldei-Ai amun anu Leah ahin pohpeh in ahile, hichun Rachel in Leah kom'a “Lungset tah in na chapa Joldei-Ai hinpoh chu kei jong nei hom thei ding ham,” tin athum tai.”  
\v 15 Hinlah Leah in Rachel jah a “Ka inneipu nei lahpeh jong thil neocha a nabol ham? Tua jong kachapa Joldei-Ai hinpoh jong lahpeh ding neigot kit ham?” atileh Rachel in adonbut in, “Chuti ahile na chapa Joldei-Ai poh man dingin tujan Jacob in nangma na lupkhompi thei nante,” ati.  
\v 16 Hiche nilhah chun Jacob phailei lama konna ahung kinungle phat in Leah achen aga kimupin, “Tujan hi keima toh ilupkhom ding ahi, ajeh chu tujan a dinga ka chapan nao neitheina ahinpoh a tujana dinga ka choh nahitai,” hichun Jacob chu hiche jan chun Leah to ageh lhontai.  
\v 17 Pathen'in Leah taona chu asanpeh tan, nao ahin voptan Jacob chapa nga lhinna ahinpeh tai.  
\v 18 Hichun Leah in asei tan, “Ka sohnu chu kajipa ka pehdoh jeh in Pathen'in ka chohdoh man eipetai,” atin hichun naosen min chu Issachar asah tan ahi.  
\v 19 Chujouvin jong Leah chun nao avop kit in Jacob dingin chapa gup lhinna ahinpeh kit tai.  
\v 20 Hichun Leah in asei tan, “Pathen'in keima numei thilken phatah tah eikenpeh tai, tu apat a kajipan ngailutna sangtah einei ding ahitai, ajeh chu chapa gup kaneipeh tai,” hichun amanun naosen min chu Zebulun asah tai.  
\v 21 Ahin phat chomkhat jouvin nao numei khat ahingin amin chu Dinah asah in ahi.  
\v 22 Hichun Pathen'in Rachel chu asumil pon Pathen'in ataona asanpeh in anaobu chu ahonpeh tai.  
\v 23 Hijeh chun Rachel in jong nao ahin vop in chapa khat ahin neitai; hichun Rachel in hitin aseiye, “Pathen'in ka jachatna jouse asubei tai,” ati.  
\v 24 Rachel'in anao min chu Joseph asah in hitin aseiye, “Pakaiyin chapa dang khat jong eihin sah kit teitei hen o!” ati.   
\s1 Jacob le Laban kinoptona  
\p
\v 25 Rachel in Joseph ahin neijou phat chun, Jacob in Laban kom'a aseitai, “Nei nungsol tan kagam lang uva,” ati.  
\v 26 Kajite kachate neipe dohtan phat sottah nangma in'ah lhachan kapang tan, tua hi keima ki nungle phat ahung hitai, chule itobanga nangma na katohpeh nahim nangman nakihet nai, ati.  
\v 27 Ahin Laban in Jacob jah a aseiye, “Ahithei ding leh lungset tah in nei dalha hih in ajeh chu nangma ka insunga na hunglut apat in Pathen'in phatthei eiboh lheh jengin ahi.  
\v 28 Chule Jacob in aseijin, “Natoh man ding ijat ham nei seipeh tan keiman kapeh ding nahi” ati.  
\v 29 Chuin Jacob in adonbut in, “Nangman nahenai, itobanga nangma na katoh a na gancha ho hung pung thei ham?” ati.  
\v 30 “Ajeh chu keima kahung masang chun themcha bou na neijin tun apung jal tan, Pathen'in hatah in phatthei na boh tan ahi. Ahile itih phat hi ding ham? Keima insunga ding katohna ding,” ati.  
\v 31 Chule Laban in adong kit in, “Ipiba kapeh ding ham?” Jacob in aseiye, “Imacha neipe hih in, ahin thil khat nei bolpeh le chun keiman nagancha na vettup peh nang'e ati.  
\v 32 Tun keiman na gancha kelngoi ho gakhol sohkei jing ting, amaho lah achun apol jouse hin lhengdoh inting, chule keltah ho lah a jong apol thim hihen hapol apol jouse hin lheng doh ingting, hichengse chu keima natoh man in nei bolpeh tan, ati.  
\v 33 Khonung teng ka natoh man sutoh dinga nahung teng ka kitahna nahin muchen theina dingin, kelchate lah a apollou hihen, hapol a pollou akimu doh khah a, kelngoi lah a jong apollou khattou aum khah a ahile hiche ho se chu nangma a konna kaguh a kisim jeng thei ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 34 Hichun Laban in adonbut in, “Apha lheh jeng'e nangman nasei bang chu himai tahen,” ati.  
\v 35 Hinlah Laban in hiche nikho ma ma chun kelcha achal asandup apol, chule abeh beh a kang kelcha anu apol ho, chule kelngoi avom ho jouse chu achapa kom'a abon'in agathah doh sah sohkei in ahi.  
\v 36 Hichun aman Jacob to nithum jen lampi a kigamlat in asolmang tai, chule Jacob in Laban gancha akithah lou jouse chu aching jom jing tan ahi.  
\v 37 Chuin Jacob in Almond le Shiga phung bah ho chu amalngim in hiche thingbah avel akang lai ho chu kelcha ho amusah in ahi.  
\v 38 Hichun Jacob in thingbah amalngim ho chu kelngoi ho twi dkonna konga akoiyin, kelngoite twichip dinga ahungji teng ule kijangmatji ahijeh uva akoi ahi.  
\v 39 Kelngoi ho chu thingbah akang lai masanga chu kijangmatji, chuteng chule kelngoite chun akangpol jong, hapol a pol jong ahin hing doh doh tauve.  
\v 40 Jacob in kelngoi ho chu ahoikhen in Laban kelngoi hon lah a akangpol ho leh avom ho chu ahoikhen in ama chan ding chengse chu atum in akhendoh in, Laban a lah achun ahoilut tapoi.  
\v 41 Hiti chun kelngoi lah a asapha ho chu akijangmat teng ule thingbah ho amu uva, akijangmat theina ding uvin Jacob in jong thingbah ho amasang uva twi lonna kom laiya aga jampeh jin ahi.  
\v 42 Hinlah Jacob in kelngoi atahsa phalou ho ahi tengleh aga jamle jipoi, ajeh chu Laban a chu asapha lou jeng ahin, Jacob a vang chu asapha jeng ahiuve.  
\v 43 Hijeh chun Jacob chu ahung hao thei lheh tan, kelngoi tamtah ahin neitan, soh numei ahin soh pasal ahin tamtah aneiyin, chule sangan le sangangsao jong tamtah anei doh tai.   
\c 31  
\s1 Jacob apu Laban akon ajammang  
\p
\v 1 Jacob in Laban chapa te ama chung'a alung damlou u thu ajatan ama hon aseiyun, “Jacob in ipau thil jouse akilah tan, chule anei agou athilkeo jouse khu ipauva konna akilamdoh ahi,” ati tauve.  
\v 2 Chujongleh Jacob in Laban maiso aven ahile alung lhailou lungthim chom agel jong ahe chen tan ahi.  
\v 3 Hichun Pathen'in Jacob chu ahoulimpin, “Nangma kinungle kit tan, napu napa chule na sopite chenna gam'a keiman kaumpi jing ding nahi,” ati.  
\v 4 Hichun Jacob in mi asol in loulam a akelngoi chin nauva Rachel le Leah aga kousah tan ahi.  
\v 5 Chuin Jacob in hitin aseiye, “Keiman ka hechen tai, napa lhon maiso kavet le lungthim chom chom aneitai, masang tobang ahi tapoi, hijongleh kapu kapate Pathen'in eiumpi jingnai.  
\v 6 Nangnin jong nahe lhon nai, katha neisun kajo chan a napa lhon ding natoh katonge.  
\v 7 Hinlah aman eijou lhep tan, kanatoh man jong somvei tobang eikhel pehtai, amavang Pathen'in keima chunga vang thil phalou imacha alhunsah pon ahi.  
\v 8 Aman hitin aseiye, 'gancha apol ho jouse chu nangma nikho thaman hitante' atile gancha ho chu apol jeng hatah in ahung pung tul tul kit tan, hichun aman alunggel akhel kit in 'gancha availang jenga pol ho' atikit leh gancha anou jouse chu adung le avai langa pol bou apeng kit tai.  
\v 9 Hitia hi Pa Pathen'in napa gancha ho jouse alah a keima eipehsoh ahitai.  
\v 10 Chuin phat chomkhat jou kelngoite kijangmat laijin jan mang khat kaneiyin, ka khodah in ahile kelpi chunga kaldoh kelchal ho chu apol ho leh adup ho aki timatpiu kamui.  
\v 11 Chuin hitia mang kanei pet in Pakai vantil khat in eihin houpin 'Jacob!' eihin tin kenjong 'Hoijo hikom'a kaum'e,' kati.  
\v 12 “Chuin Pakai vantil chun, 'Dah inlang gahve temin, kelpi ho chunga kaldoh kelchal ho khu apol, adup, akangpol, availanga pol jengin amat e, ijeh inem itile Laban in na bolsetna jouse keiman abonchan ka musoh keitai.  
\v 13 Keima na Pathen Bethel mun'a song khom thao nanu a na kigahna Pathen chu kahi, tun kipatdoh in hiche gam hi dalhan lang na penna gam langa kile kit tan.'” \x + \xo 31:13 \xt Semtilbu 28:18-22\x*  
\v 14 Chuphat in Rachel le Leah in adonbut in, “Keinin imacha boina kanei lhonpoi; kapa lhon nei le gou chanvou ka chan lhon ding um beh ham?”  
\v 15 Aman dalpam mi a eigel lhon hilou ham? Ajeh chu aman eijoh doh lhon in keini kichohna sum jouse jong eisuh mang peh tauve.  
\v 16 Chule nei le gou jouse Pathen'in kapa lhona kon a alahmang peh ho jouse chu eiho le ichate ho a ahi bouve. Hijeh chun tun Pathen'in najah a asei jouse chu ipi hijongleh bol jengin,” ati lhon tai.  
\v 17 Hichun Jacob akipat doh in ajite le achate jouse chu Sangan chunga atoudoh sah sohkei tan;  
\v 18 chule aganchaho jouse amasang lam uva ahoiyin Paddan-aram gam'a anei agou jouse aki suhtup in Canaan gam'a apa Isaac henga che dingin aumtai.  
\v 19 Chuin Laban chu kelngoi mulvou dinga akondoh phat in Rachel in apa insung'a semthu pathen chu ana kiguh mang tai.  
\v 20 Jacob in jong Aramea mipa Laban chu alhem lhan, ajamdoh dingu jong aseipeh pon ahi.  
\v 21 Hichun Jacob in anei agou jouse akipoh in Eupharate vadung apal galkai in Gilead thing lhang lam ahin jontai.  
\v 22 Ahin nithum jouvin Jacob ajammang tai tithu chu Laban ahin seipeh un;  
\v 23 Chuin Laban in asopi ho cheng akou khom in, Jacob chu ahin nung del tauvin ahile, nisagi lhin ni chun Gilead lhang gamsunga ahin juilut tan ahi.  
\v 24 Hinlah Pathen'in Laban Syrea mipa chu janin ana kimupin hitin aseiye, “Kichih theijin Jacob chu imacha nalo theilou ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 25 Hichun Laban'in Jacob chu ahin phatan, chule Jacob in thinglhang lah a chun aponbuh akison tauvin, chuin Laban le a-u anaoten jong Gelead thinglhang a Jacob to kigamlat louvin aponbuh u akison tauve.  
\v 26 Chuin Laban in Jacob jah a aseiye, “Ibola hitobanga hi neijou lhep hitam ati, chule iti dana ka chanu teni jong gal a sohchang ho banga nabol jeng ham?  
\v 27 Ibola guhthim cha a najam mang uham? Ibol'a neijou lhep ham ati, chule nache ding iti dan a nei hetsah loubeh ham? Neina hetsah le chun thupitah a kilhahna ankong le la ngaitah tah kisan tin, tumging to kithoa kivailhah tadinga ati.  
\v 28 Na thilbol ho hi ngolna in na dimset e, ka chanu teni cha katute jong kabeng chop man tapon, kilhahna jong kana bol thei tapoi! ati.  
\v 29 Tua hi nangma ka suhbei thei nahi, hinlah napu napate Pathen'in janhi nilhah in eina kimuto pin gihna jong eineiyin Jacob chu na suhboi theilou ding ahi eiti!  
\v 30 Nangma lunggel na inlam a nache ding na thanopna chu ka hethem lheh e, kham thei jong nahipoi, napa insung miho toh kimuto kal na ngalel jong kahe nai, hinlah ibola ka pathen houna doiphung chu naguh ham? ati.  
\v 31 Jacob in adonbut in, “Keiman nangma kana ging lheh in ahi, ajeh chu nangman, nachanu teho chu hunam a nei lahpeh ding ham tia kana gel ahi.  
\v 32 Amavang na doibom vang chu ahile nangman hol inlang na mudoh thei leh namuna mi chu koi hile ahinkho subei jeng tan ati, chule nangma thil ho jong keima sopiho ana lakha aum leh kanung peh ding nahi; Jacob in vang Rachel in ana lah chu ana hetlou ahi.  
\v 33 Laban chu doibom hol in Jacob ponbuh a ache masapen in , aban'in Leah kom'ah, hiche jou chun Leah soh teni kom'ah achen, hinlah imacha amudoh pon, achaina in Rachel ponbuh a alut in ahi.  
\v 34 Rachel in apa insung doibom chu ana ladoh in Sangan pho kah a chu ana sel'a chule achunga chu ama ana tou ahi, hichun Laban in ponbuh sung aning akah aphet vang'in imacha amudoh tapon ahi.  
\v 35 Amanun apa kom'a aseitai, “Lungsettah in nei ngaidam in ka pakai keima numei hina lhinna kaneijin kadin theilou ding ahi,” Laban vang ahol chu atang dehpon amavang insung doibom chu amudoh pon ahi.  
\v 36 Hichun Jacob hatah in ahung lunghang tan Laban'in apupa jah a asei tan ahi, “Keima ipi ka guchatna ka jkonna umham?” atitan, “Chule ipi mong kabol khel a hichan geiya hi kanung neihin del a keima migucha banga nei bol hitam?  
\v 37 Nangman kanei kathil koina jouse aning akah geiyin naphet in, tun nang thil nakimudoh ho chu neivet sah un, sopi ule nao ho masang laitah ahin hin podoh in, ama hon eini kahlah a thutanna nei mai uhen!” ati.  
\v 38 “Nangma kom'a kum som ni na gancha ho kana vettup peh in, na gancha ho kelngoi ahin na kelcha ho ahin imacha boina ana umpon hiche kum hijat kana vettup sunga chun kelngoi khat jong kana kilah khapoi.  
\v 39 Keiman gamsa in, gancha ho athasa jong kahin polut khapon, athi amang ho jong keima nikhotha toh suhto din kana boljin, gancha ho sun hileh jan hileh amang ho jouse chu keima lhalo toh suhto din nei kahpeh jin ahi.  
\v 40 Hiche hi keima dinmun anahi. Hitipi chun sun teng nisan eihalvampai gon, jan tengleh dap kathoh jin, kamit tenin la imutna him him amupha pon ahi.  
\v 41 Hitobanga chu kum somni nangma insunga kana kimanchah ahi. Keiman kum som le kum li nangma insunga lhacha in kana pangin, na chanu teni lona in kum gup kana tohbe in gancha ho lona in chule kana toh man somvei tobang nei khelpeh in ahi.  
\v 42 Kapate Pathen, Abraham Pathen, kapa Isaac ginpa chun eipanpi lou hile tua hi nangman khut keohel tahbah a neina solmang ding ahitai. Pathen'in ka gentheina le kakhut tah a ka tohgimna hi amua jan nilhah a chu na gihsal ahiye,” ati.   
\s1 Laban le Jacob kah a kitepna  
\p
\v 43 Hichun Laban in hitin Jacob adonbut in, “Hiche numei ho hi ka chanu ahin, hiche chapang ho jong katute ahi, chule gancha ho jouse jong abkonna keima gancha ahi. Chule ipi hitale namu phah chan hi aboncha keiya jeng ahi cheh nai. Amavang keiman tua hi ka chanute chule achate ho chunga ipi kabol ding hitam? ati.  
\v 44 Hijeh chun hungin eini kikah a kitepna nei hite hichun eini eikan khom cheh lhon ding ahi.”  
\v 45 Hichun Jacob in hetjingna dingin song khom khat aphutdoh tai.  
\v 46 Hichun Jacob in asopi ho lah a aseiyin, “Songho hin chom khom un,” ati, ama hon song chu khat chunga khat asethop un, hichun Jacob le Laban song kise thop kom'a atou lhonin kitepna ankong chu anekhom lhon tan ahi.  
\v 47 Songlhuh kise chu Laban in Jegar-sahadutha asah in (hichu Aramaic paova “hettohsah songthop” tina ahin), hiche ma ma chu Jacob in Galeed asah e (hichu Hebrew paova “hettohsah songthop” tina ahi).  
\v 48 Hichun Laban in, “Tuni nikhoa hiche song lhuh hi kei le nang kah a sakhia panga ahitai,” tia, hiche jeh chun amin jong Galeed asah in ahi.  
\v 49 Hiche mun jong hi Mizpah akiti tai, aman aseiyin, “Ajeh chu nangma le keima jong khonung teng jongleh gamla tah a umjongleh hen Pathen'in eiumpi jing lhon hen.”  
\v 50 Ka chanute ho nahin suh gentheija numei dang ho jia nahin kipuiya ahile, koima chan muhih jongleh abonchan Pathen'in amusoh keiye, Pathen hi nang le kei kikah a kitepna a hiche thua hi pang jing ding ahi.  
\v 51 Hiche song athopma kise ho hi Jacob in Laban jah ah, “Vejingin kei le nang kah a kihet themna hijing ding ahitai.  
\v 52 Hiche song kise thop hile songphu hi sakhi a pang ahin, ken jong nangma suse dinga hiche hi kahin khokhel louhel ding, nangin jong keima suse dinga hiche hi nahin khokhel louhel ding ahi.  
\v 53 Abraham Pathen, Nahor Pathen chule amani Pa Pathen chu eini kah a thutan ding ahitai,” ati. Hijeh chun Jacob jong apa Isaac ginpa minin akihahsel tai.  
\v 54 Hichun Jacob in hiche molchunga chun Pathen henga maicham asemin kitepna ki hetthemna ankong jong asemin, anneh anei jou uchun hiche jan machun molchunga chun ageh tauve.  
\v 55 Laban ajing chun matah in athoudoh in achanute ho le atute ho jouse abonchan achop sohkeiyin, chule abonchauvin phatthei aboh sohkeiyin, hichun ama a inlam ma aki nungle kittai.   
\c 32  
\s1 Jacob le Esau kimuto  
\p
\v 1 Jacob chu akhol jinna amachal jingin, chule Pakai vantil ten ana lamto uvin ahi.  
\v 2 Jacob in amaho amu chun hitin aseyin, “Hilai mun hi Pathen kicholdona mun ahi!” ati. Hiche mun chu Mahanaim asah tai.  
\v 3 Hichun Jacob in Edom gamsunga Seir gamkaiya a upa Esau henga dingin thupo dingin mi asol masan ahi.  
\v 4 Aman hitin athumop in, “Kapu Esau kom'a hitia hi nasei ding ahi: 'Na sohpa Jacob in hitin aseiye, tuni gei hin Laban kom'a kaum jing nalaiye.  
\v 5 Keiman gancha bong hon ahin, sangan hon ahin, kelngoi hon ahin, kelcha hon ahin, soh le kol jong tamtah kanei tai. Tua ka pakai pa masanga kahung tao ahi hichu nangma mitmua ngailut kachan theina ding tia nangma seipeh dinga mi kahinsol ahiye ati, tin gasei tauvin,'” ati.  
\v 6 Thu hettohsah ho ahung kinungle chun, Jacob kom'a hitin aseiyun, “Nasopi pa kaki mutopi uvin, tua hi ama nang toh kimuto dingin mi jali toh ahung kondoh in ahi.”  
\v 7 Ahin Jacob chu hiche thu ajah chun akicha lheh tan, hichun aman a insung mite ahin, gancha kelngoi ho jouse ahin, keltah ho se chule sangongsao hose ahin hopnin ahom khenin ahiye.  
\v 8 Jacob in hitin agel lin, “Esau vin honkhat chu ahung bulu tah jongleh honkhat pa beh asohcha theiye,” ati.  
\v 9 Hichun Jacob ataovin, “Vo kapu Abraham Pathen, kapa Isaac Pathen, O ka Pakai, 'Nangin na sopite leh nagam lang uva kinungle kit tan' tin nei seipeh in chuleh 'Keiman nang dingin aphat phat nan bolpeh nange' tin kitepna naneiye.  
\v 10 Nasohpa nei musah longlou ngailutna ho le nakitahna ho chu chang din lhinna imacha kaneipoi. Ajeh chu ka tenggol keoseh puma hiche Jordan hi hung galkaiya kahin, tun mihem loini lhingset ka lamdoh tai.  
\v 11 O Pakai, lungset tah in ka sopipa Esau khut a kon'in nei huhhing teiyin, keima kati aja lheh jeng'e; ajeh chu aman kajite ho chule ka chate ho jong eihung nokhum ding ahitai.  
\v 12 Hinlah nangman, nang dingin aphat phat nan bolpeh nange, na chilhah te jeng jong twikhanglen panga neldi jat hin phantin, tam behseh jenga kisim jou louding ahi,’ tin nana kitep e,” ati. \x + \xo 32:12 \xt Semtilbu 22:17\x*  
\v 13 Jacob chu hiche mun'a chun ajan geh in athil poh ho lah achun alhengdoh in asopipa Esau peh dingin:  
\v 14 kelpi jani, kelchal somni, kelngoipi jani chule kelngoi chal somni toh,  
\v 15 sangongsao pi somthum toh anoute se toh, bongpi somli toh, bongchal som toh, sanganpi somni toh, chule sangan chal som toh alheng doh e.  
\v 16 Hichun Jacob in hiche gancha ho chu hopni in ahom in amaho vekol ding chun soh khat cheh anganse in, hichun asoh ho jah a hitin aseiye, “Nang hon hiche gancha hotoh hin keima masanglam a che tauvin. Hinlah gancha hon teni kikah a chun mun ong umsah un,” ati.  
\v 17 Hichun ama hon lamkaipa jah achun hitin aseiye, “Ka sopipa Esau to nakimuto lhon teng aman thu nahin doh teng, 'Nangho hi hoilam jon ding nahiuvem? Chule nangho koi gam mi nahiu ham? Tua gancha ho ahung masa ho chu koiya ham?' ahin ti tengleh,  
\v 18 Hiche teng chule hitia hi amaho na donbut dingu ahi, 'Hiche gancha ho se hi na sohpa Jacob a ahi, amaho hi kipa thilpeh adia kapu Esau a dinga kahin poh ahiye. Chule ama jong kanung lam uvah ahung e,'” tiuvin ati.  
\v 19 Hiti chun Jacob in soh masa pa athuhil bang chun anina pa ahin, athumna pa geiyin gancha ho vetup lamkai jouse chu aseipeh cheh tan, “Esau toh nakimuto tengu le na thusei hou chu kibang cheh ding ahi.  
\v 20 'Chujongleh vetan na sohpa Jacob jong keiho nunga ahung'e, tia na seipeh ding'u ahi,'” atin ahi. Ijeh inem itile Jacob gel a chu, “Ka masanga kitol thilpeh chengse hin ama jol lungdam thei khat ingting, ajou teng amai kamu thei ding ahi; ijem atile bon eina sang jeng khat inte,” tia angaito ahi.  
\v 21 Jacob in ngailut thilpeh ho chu ache masang'in asol tan ahi, amavang hiche mun achun ajan geh in akhovah dentai.   
\s1 Peniel mun'a Jacob in Pathen akibotpi  
\p
\v 22 Hiche jan chun Jacob in aji teni chule asoh teni chule achate pasal som le khat chu athoudoh tan Jabbok Vadung chu agalkaipi tan ahi.  
\v 23 Hichun Jacob in amaho chutoh vadung agalkai phat chun anei agou jouse toh asol tan ahi.  
\v 24 Hichun Jacob chu achangin adalha tauvin, pasal khat in ama chu khovah geiyin akibotpin ahi. \x + \xo 32:24 \xt Hosea 12:3,4\x*  
\v 25 Pasal akibotpi pa chun ajo louding phat chun Jacob konggu homlai tah chu asuhboh pehtan ahi.  
\v 26 Hichun mipa chun aseijin, “Nei lhatan kho hungvah ding ahitai!” Amavang Jacob in adonbut in, “Phatthei neiboh tokah a nangma kalha louding nahi,” ati.  
\v 27 Mipa chun adongin, “Na min ipi ham?” ati, hichun aman adonbut in, “Jacob ahi,” ati.  
\v 28 Mipa chun, “Na min hi Jacob hitalou ding, tua patna Israel kiti ding nahitai. Ajeh chu nangma Pathen toh na kibot in jong nahat in, mihemte jong na hinjo ding ahi,” atipeh e. \x + \xo 32:28 \xt Semtilbu 35:10\x*  
\v 29 Jacob in adongin, “Lungset tah in namin nei seipeh in,” ati, mipa chun adonbut in, “Ibola kamin chu nahet nom ham,” ati. Hichun aman Jacob chu hilai mun a chun phatthei abohtan ahi. \x + \xo 32:29 \xt Thutan Vaihom Ho 13:17,18\x*  
\v 30 Hichun Jacob in hiche mun chu Peniel (hichu “Pathen mai” tina ahi) asahtai, “Ajeh chu keiman Pathen kaki maitopi tan chule ka hinkho jong eihuhdoh peh in ahi.”  
\v 31 Jacob in Peniel adalhah chun nisa ahung sohdoh tan ahi, ajeh chu akonggu anat jeh ahi.  
\v 32 (Hiche jeh chun tuni geihin Israel chaten akonggu to kijopmatna khelgu hom sunga thapigui hi anepouve; ipi jeh inem itile aman Jacob konggu hom sunga thapigui ana hebal peh in ahi.)   
\c 33  
\s1 Jacob le Esau kichamna  
\p
\v 1 Hichun Jacob akhodah in avet a ahile Esau chu mihem jali jen to ahung amutai. Chuin Jacob in jong achate chu Leah le Rachel chule asoh numei teni ahop peh sohkeiye.  
\v 2 Hichun asoh numei le achate ho jouse amasat sah in, abanin Leah le achate achesah in, chule achaina in Rachel le Joseph apansah e.  
\v 3 Chuin Jacob ama mong mong amaho jouse masanga chun achen, aupa heng ahin phah tokahsen sagi vei jen tol'a abohkhup in ahi.  
\v 4 Hichun Esau alhai pheijin apumkoi jengin, chule angong koiya achop a ahile ani lhonin akika lhon tai.  
\v 5 Hichun Esau in numei ho chule achate ho chu aven adongin, “Amaho hi koi hiuva ham,” ati. Jacob in adonbut in, “Hiche chapang ho hi Pathen'in na sohpa phatthei eibohna ahi,” ati.  
\v 6 Hichun soh numei teni le achate hon ahin nailut un Esau masanga chun abohkhup tauvin ahi.  
\v 7 Leah le achate jong ahin nailut uvin abohkhup in asalam uve; chule anukhah penin Joseph le Rachel ahung nailut lhonin abohkhup lhonin salam abol lhon tai.  
\v 8 Esau in adong tan, “Ahile hiche kahin kitopi gancha honpi chu ipi nabolna ham?” ati. Jacob in adonbut in, “Nangma masang'a lunglhaina kamuna tei ding kati ahi,” ati.  
\v 9 Esau in adonbut in, “Kanao, keiman jong tamtah kanei nai” atin, “Nangma thil chu nang dingin kikoi tan,” ati.  
\v 10 Ahin Jacob in asei teiyin, “Ahipoi, nangman hiche kipa thilpeh ho hi nalah louva hitheilou ahi, keiman nangma mai kamu hi Pathen mai mu tobang kahi, nangma mai kamu theiya nanui awgin kajah hi thina a konna galkai kahitai! ati.  
\v 11 Lungset tah in hiche thilpeh ho hi nei sanpeh teiyin, Pathen'in ka ngaichat jouse eipetai.” Hichun Jacob in ahasei behset jeh chun Esau chun thilpeh ho chu asang tai.  
\v 12 Esau in, “Aphai,” “Keiman na lamkai jing ting eini che tahite.”  
\v 13 Jacob in adonbut in, “Ka pakai, neihet them peh mai jin, chate ho hi alhasam thei lheh na laiyun, gancha bongnou ho leh kelnou ho jong ahonpi toh ki khen thei lou lai ahiuvin, nikhat sunga hatah in kihoi pai taleh gancha honte aboncha thigam jeng thei ahiuve.  
\v 14 Hijeh chun lungset tah in, na sohpa masanga kapu ana masa jengin lang keiman olcha chan ka masanga gancha ho ki kalvan bang ule chapang te kikalvan bang bangu hin, Seir gam'a kapu heng kahin phah kahsen hung nange, ati.  
\v 15 Apha lheh jenge tin Esau in adonbut in, “Hinlah ka mite ho themkhat tou dalhang kating nangho lamhil ding chule boina le hahsatna a pan lathei ding.” ati, Jacob in adonbut in, “Hiche ho chu ngai ponte, lungset umtah a kapun neina lamdot hi alhingset in ka sange!” ati.  
\v 16 Hichun Esau chu akinung heijin Seir gam jon ding chun hiche ni mama chun achekit tai.  
\v 17 Jacob vang chu ahile Succoth lama achen hiche mun'a chun inlim gancha ho din asong in, chule ama chenna dingin jong in aki sahtai. Hiche jeh a chu hiche mun chu Succoth (tichu chenna mun tina ahi) kiti ahi.  
\v 18 Phat chomkhat jouvin Jacob chu Paddan-aram lammah kon'in Shechem Canaan gam ahunglhung tan, hiche khopi phah masanga chun ngahmun khat asem kittai.  
\v 19 Jacob in Shechem pa Hamor chate khut a kon chun gam leiset phabep sum jakhat in akichoh in hikom'a chun ponbuh akison tai. \x + \xo 33:19 \xt Joshua 24:32; Jn 4:5\x*  
\v 20 Hichun aman maicham atungdoh in amin chu *El-Elohe-Israel asah tai.   
\c 34  
\s1 Dinah kisuh thang jeh a phu kilah  
\p
\v 1 Jacob le Leah chanu Dinah chu nikhat apotdoh in hiche gam'a cheng numei khangthah hotoh kimuto din achen ahi.  
\v 2 Ahin hiche gam’a Hiv mi leng Homar chapa Shechem kitipa chun Dinah chu aman in aluppi tan ahi.  
\v 3 Ahin amapa chun ahin ngailu lheh tan, hichun aman thudihtah a kihoulimpi a nopsah ding chu adei lheh tai.  
\v 4 Shechem in apa Homar jah a asei tan, hiche numeinu hi neipuipeh un kaji din kadeiye ati.  
\v 5 Phat chomkhat jouvin, Jacob in thusoh aja tan Shechem in Dinah aluppia asuhset chu ahetan, ahin Jacob in achate gamlah a gancha ho ching ahijeh u chun amaho ahung lhun angah in kamcheng khat jeng cha jong akehpoi.  
\v 6 Hamor Shechem pa chu Jacob henga kihoulim dingin achedoh tai.  
\v 7 Chuin Jacob chate loulam a kon'in ahunglhung tauvin ama hon hiche thu ho ajah uchun alung nommo lheh un kidang jong asa lheh uvin hatah in alunghang uvin, asopinu Dinah Shechem in asuhset a Jacob insung asuhboi chu bollou ding khat ahiye atiuve.  
\v 8 Hamor in Jacob le achate akihoulimpin, aman aseiye, “Kachapa Shechem in na chanu alungset lheh jengin ahi, lungset tah in amani chu kichensah uhite.  
\v 9 Ahithei ding leh eiho chate kila tou hite, keihon nangho chanu ho kipui uvingting, keima ho chanute ho jong nangho chapa te ho din kipui un ati.  
\v 10 Hiche gamsunga hi ichenkhom theiyu ahi, chule khosa uvin bolthei toh thei tongun, nanop chanu nei le gou jong na kilam theiyu ahi.”  
\v 11 Shechem chu Dinah sopiho le apa jah a ataotan, “Lungset tah in nei khotouvin, ahithei ding le kaji din kakipui nom e chule nang hon na thum chan uchu keiman kapeh ding nahiuve.”  
\v 12 Numei nu chu kaji dinga nei peh pou ule keiman ipi thilpeh hijongleh suhto thei ding alen aneo hileh kapeh ding ahi, ati.  
\v 13 Hinlah Shechem in Dinah ana luppi a asuhset tah jeh chun Jacob chate chun Hamor le achapa Shechem chu lungphalou tah in ahoulimpi tauve.  
\v 14 Ama hon adonbut un, “Hiche hi keima ho moh nop lhah thei kahi pouve, ajeh chu nangho hi chep tanlou nahiuvin, ka sopinu u nang hon nakipui dingu chu keiho dinga jachat umtah khat hung hi ding ahi.  
\v 15 Hinlah kihoucham theina khat vang aum'e, hichu ahileh na pasal ho jouse achep natan thei diu le atiuve.  
\v 16 Hiche teng chule ka chanu te ho'u kapeh theiyu, chule nangho chanu ho jong keima hon jong kakipui thei dingu ahi.  
\v 17 Ahin nangho pasal hon acheptan ding anoplou ule ka sopinu'u kapeh theilou dingu ahi, atiuve.  
\v 18 Hamor le achapa Shechem chun amaho thilgon chu pha asa lhonin ahi.  
\v 19 Shechem chu alunglhai lheh in bol ding ho chu ageisang tapon, ajeh chu Jacob chanu Dinah adei behset jeh chun Shechem chu amaho insung milah a jathei umdol tah khat ahi.  
\v 20 Chuin Hamor le achapa Shechem khopi kelkot a ahung lhonin mipi ho lah a akihou nau kinoptona ho chu ahung phong doh lhonin hitin asei lhonin ahi.  
\v 21 Amanin aphongdoh lhonin hiche miho hi mipha eiho mi ahi ati lhon e, veuvin gam jong lentah inei uvin amaho chenna thei ding, amaho toh chengkhom uhitin, bolthei thei bol uhitin, eihon jong amaho chanute ijon thei ding'u chule ama hon jong eiho chanute akichenpi thei dingu ahi,” ati.  
\v 22 Amaho toh eiho ichen khom theina diuvin thil khat aum'e, hichu ahileh eiho pasal jouse amaho banga chep ikitan tengu le ichen khom thei ding'u ahi.  
\v 23 Hinlah thilpha khat ihet dingu chu ichen khom tengu le agancha hou, anei agou hou jouse aboncha a eiho a hung hithei ahi. Hijeh chun ama hon adei atup hou chu bolpeh leuhen amaho jong eiho lah a chen ding thanom tah a hung cheng diu ahitai.  
\v 24 Hichun khopi sunga cheng aching athem jouse Hamor le achapa Shechem thupeh chu anom cheh tauvin, chule pasal jousen achep akitan sohhel tauvin ahi.  
\v 25 Ahin nithum jou don chun amaho chep tanna maha jong damtheng loulai in Jacob chateni Simon le Levi asopinu Dinah toh pengkhom teni chu ahung kon lhonin hiche khopi sunga pasal jouse chemjam in asatlih lhon tan ahi.  
\v 26 Hiche athi ho lah achun Hamor le achapa Shechem jong ajao lhon tai, hichun Dinah chu Shechem in mun'a kon'in amaho inlam a ahinpui lhon tan ahi.  
\v 27 Phat chomkhat jouvin Jacob chate ho ahunglhung cheh tauvin, ama hon khopi sunga mipi athi amang akithat ho chu asopinu u kisuhthangna khopi chu achom theng hel uve.  
\v 28 Ama hon akelngoi hou ahin, abongchal hou chule asangan hou jouse phaicham khopi sung le tollhang a thil keo jouse akilah tauve.  
\v 29 Anei agou jouse jong alahpeh sohkeiyun, amaho jite chate jong alahpeh un, amaho hetkhah nalouva apuimang tauve.  
\v 30 Jacob in phat chomkhat jouvin Simon le Levi kom'a hitin aseiye, “Keima hi nei suhmang lhon ahitai! Hiche gam mite le Canaan mite le Periz mite kom'a hin kanamse in kaui lheh tai. chule eiho lhomcha ihiuvin amaho ahung kihoutoh tengule eiho eisuh mang dingu ahi. Keima kahin ka insung pumpi ka kichaihel ding ahitai,” ati.  
\v 31 Ama hon lunghang tah in aseiyun, “Ipi bol'a chu isopinu u chu numei kijoh banga abolset ham?” atiuve.   
\c 35  
\s1 Bethel mun'a Pathen'in Jacob phatthei abohna  
\p
\v 1 Hichun Pathen'in Jacob ahoulimpin, “Kithouvin lang Bethel lama kinungle kit inlang hikom'a chun gacheng tan, chule na upa Esau kom'a nahung jampet a nahenga hung kilah Pathen ding chun hikom'a chun maicham khat gasemin,” ati. \x + \xo 35:1 \xt Semtilbu 28:11-17\x*  
\v 2 Chuin Jacob in a insung mite ahin midang akom'a cheng ho jah a hitin aseiye, “Doiphung jouse paimang un, natahsa kisuhthengun, vonthah kivonun,  
\v 3 Tua eiho Bethel lama iche diu Pathen henga maicham kasem ding ahi. Ajeh chu Pakaiyin ka hahsat laitah a kataona eisanpeh in, Aman kachena ka lamjotna jousea eiumpi jinge ati.  
\v 4 Hichun ama hon gamdang mite indoi akoi jouseu chule abil uva abilba u abonchan Jacob apeuvin ahile Jacob in abonchan Shechem nai vel'a thingphunglen noi khat ah aga vuimang tai.  
\v 5 Amaho ahung kondoh uchun Pathen a konna tijatna mipi adimun, hijeh chun Jacob insung mite bulu din koimacha ahung kondoh ngam tapoi.  
\v 6 Jacob le a insung mite Luz kiti (Bethel tia jong kihe) Canaan gamsung alhungun ahi.  
\v 7 Chule hikom'a chun Jacob in maicham khat asemin, hiche lai mun chu El-bethel asah in ahi (hichu “Bethel Pathen” tina ahi). Ajeh chu aupa henga konna ahung jamdoh a chu hikom'a chu Pathen ama mong mong ahenga hung kiphong ahi.  
\v 8 Rebekah jenle nu Deborah athi a chu Bethel noiya gangpi phungnoi khat ah ana kivui ahin, hiche jeh a chu hiche min chu Allon-bacuth kisah ahiye (hichu “Lhilonna gangpi phung” tina ahi).  
\v 9 Hichun Pathen'in Jacob Paddan-aram a konna ahung chun ana kimutopi kit in, chuin Bethel mun'a Pathen'in phatthei abohkit in ahi.  
\v 10 Pathen'in ahoulimpin ajah a, “Namin hi Jacob ahin tunia patna hi nangma Jacob na kiti talou ding ahi. Amavang Israel kiti ding nahitai,” hichun Pathen'in ama pa min chu Israel asah tai. \x + \xo 35:10 \xt Semtilbu 32:28\x*  
\v 11 Hichun Pathen'in aseiye, “Keima El-Shaddai kahi. Pathen hattah kahi, hatah in ga un, hatah in pung tultul un, nam lentah kaso ding nahi, chule chilhah jong tamtah kapeh ding nahi,” ati. \x + \xo 35:11 \xt Semtilbu 17:4-8\x*  
\v 12 Chule khatvei Abraham, Isaac kapeh gam chu nangma le na insung mite kapeh kit ding nahi, khonung teng jongleh nangma kapeh ding nahi.  
\v 13 Hichun Pakai vantil chu Jacob akihoulimpi na a kon'in achemang tai.  
\v 14 Jacob in Pakai to akimuto melchihna dingin hiche mun'a chun songkhom khat aphutdoh kit in, hiche khom chunga chun kilhaina ju asun khumin, chule hiche chunga chun Olive thao twi asun khume. \x + \xo 35:14 \xt Semtilbu 28:18,19\x*  
\v 15 Chule Jacob in hilai mun chu Bethel (hichu “Pathen In” tina) asah tan ahi.   
\s1 Benjamin pen le Rachel thi  
\p
\v 16 Jacob le a insung miten Bethel chu adalhauvin, Ephrath lam ajot laitah un Rachel chu anaovop nat ahung kipan tan, akhol chenau jong lhung joujep loulai ahiuvinn, amanu soh dingin hanat in ahung natai.  
\v 17 Rachel chu soh dinga hanat a anat pet chun anaodom a pang asoh numei ho chun hitin ahoulimpi uve, “Nangma kicha hih in, lungneo hihbeh in, chapa khat na neibe ding ahi,” atiuve.  
\v 18 Hinlah Rachel chu alhagao apotdoh tai, ajeh chu amanu athia ahitan ahi; hijeh chun aman jong nao min chu Ben-oni asah in (Ben-oni tichu ka thoh gimpet a kacha tina ahi), apan vang Benjamin asah tai. (Benjamin tichu, kajet lama pang chapa tina ahi).  
\v 19 Rachel chu athitan Ephrath (hichu Bethleham) lampia avui tauvin ahi.  
\v 20 Jacob in angailut hetjing nan Rachel lhan song asempeh in, tuni gei hin hiche Rachel lhan hi aum jing nalaiye.  
\v 21 Hichun Jacob chu achen pondal buh chu Migdal-eder inting vum geiyin atung doh e.   
\s1 Jacob chapa te ho  
\p
\v 22 Ama chuche gamsunga achen laiyin Reuben in apa thaikemnu Bilhah chu ana luppin, hiche thu chu gangtah Jacob in ana jan ahi. Hiche ho hi Jacob chapa som le ni ho min chu ahi: \x + \xo 35:22 \xt Semtilbu 49:4\x*  
\v 23 Leah chapa te chu Reuben (Jacob chapa apeng masa pen), Simeon, Levi, Judah, Issachar chule Zebulun ahiuve.  
\v 24 Rachel chapa teni chu Joseph le Benjamin ahi lhon'e.  
\v 25 Rachel sohnu Bilhah chapa teni chu Dan le Naphtali ahi lhonin,  
\v 26 Leah sohnu Zilpah chapa teni chu Gad le Asher ahi lhone. Hichengse hi Jacob in Paddan-aram gamsunga ahindoh achapa te chu ahiuve.   
\s1 Isaac thi le akivuina  
\p
\v 27 Hichun Jacob apa Isaac kom'a ahung kinungle kit tan Mamre a Kiriath-arba gam (Hebron tia jong kisei) phat khat laiya Abraham le Isaac maljinna ana umna'u mun chu ahi. \x + \xo 35:27 \xt Semtilbu 13:18\x*  
\v 28 Isaac chu akum kum jakhat le somget ana lhing tan ahi.  
\v 29 Hichun Isaac ahaitan in teh kembet in ahinkho ana lhan, akhangguiya chemasa ho toh thinan akigom tai. Chuin achapa teni, Esau le Jacob in avui lhon tan ahi.   
\c 36  
\s1 Esau chilhah ho  
\p
\v 1 Hiche hose hi Esau phunggui ahi (Edom tia jong kisei) .  
\v 2 Esau in Canaan nungah ni aji din ana kipuijin khat nu chu Hit mi Elon chanu Adah ahi, anina nu chu ahile Anah chanu Oholibamah ahin Hiv mi Zibeon dinga atunu ahi. \x + \xo 36:2 \xt Semtilbu 26:34\x*  
\v 3 Chule Esau in asopinu Basemath jong jidin akipuiyin, Ishmael dia achanu, Nebaioth dia anaonu ahi. \x + \xo 36:3 \xt Semtilbu 28:9\x*  
\v 4 Adah chun Esau din chapa Eliphaz ahinpeh in, Basemath chun chapa Reul ahingin ahi.  
\v 5 Oholibamath chun Canaan gam'a achen laiyin chapa thum Esau din ana hinpeh in, amaho min chu ahile Jeush, Jalam, chule Korah ahiuve.  
\v 6 Esau in ajite le achate cheng abonchauvin, agancha ho jouse, abongchal ho jouse, chule anei agou thil jouse Canaan gam'a achen laiya alamdoh jouse toh mun chom ajon tan, asopipa Jacob chu adalha tan ahi.  
\v 7 Ijeh inem itile anei agou lhon, agancha lhon chuleh adinmun lhon jeh chun aumkhom lhon theina dia gam chu ninglhing joulou ahitai.  
\v 8 Hijeh chun Esau (Edom) chu thinglhang lam a Seir kiti mun'a acheng tai.  
\v 9 Hiche hi Esau chilhah Seir thinglhang gam’a cheng Edom mite chu ahi.  
\v 10 Hiche ho hi Esau chapa te min ahi: Eliphaz kitipa hi Esau loinu Adah in ahin, chule Reul kitipa hi Esau loinu Basemath in ahin ahiye.  
\v 11 Eliphaz chilhah ho Teman, Zepho, Gatam chule Kenaz ahiuve.  
\v 12 Timna, Eliphaz thaikemnu chapa khat ahingin amin chu Amalek ahi. Amaho se hi Esau jinu Adah in ahin ama hung kikhailha chilhah ho ahiuve.  
\v 13 Reul chapa te ho chu Nahath, Zerah, Shammah chule Mizzah ahi. Amaho se hi Esau jinu Basemath chilhah ho ahiuve.  
\v 14 Esau chate ho Oholibamah in ahin ho chu, Jeush, Jalam, chule Korah ahiuvin, Oholibamah hi Anah chanu Zibeon dinga atute ahung hitai.  
\v 15 Hiche ho hi Esau chate chilhah te phung choma hung lamkai ho ahiuve, Esau chapa tahpen chilhah ho Eliphaz a hung kikhai lha ho, Teman, Omar, Zepho, Kenaz ahin,  
\v 16 Korah, Gatam chule Amalek amaho se hi Eliphaz phung lamkai Edom gamsunga cheng ahiuve. Amaho jouse hi Esau jinu Adah chilhah a konna hung peng doh ahiuve.  
\v 17 Esau chapa Reul a konna hung pengdoh phung lamkai ho chu, Nahath, Zerah, Shammah chule Mizzah ahiuve. Amaho cheng hi phung lamkai Edom gamsunga Reuel chate ahi. Hiche ho jouse hi Esau jinu Basemath chilhah a konna hung peng doh ahiuve.  
\v 18 Esau chate ho Oholibamah toh ahin ho Jeush, Jalam chule Korah ahiuve. Amaho se hi phung lamkai cheh jong ahung hitauvin, hiche phung lamkai ho sese hi Esau loinu Oholibamah kitinu Anah chanu chilhah a hung kon doh ahiuve.  
\v 19 Hiche phung ho hi Esau a konna hung kondoh (Edom mi a jong kiheu) phung lamkai hon ahetpeh ho chu ahiuve.   
\s1 Seir chilhah le ason  
\p
\v 20 Hor mi Seir kitipa chilhah chengse Edom gam'a ana cheng ho chu amaho hi ahiuve: Lotan, Shobal, Zibeon, Anah,  
\v 21 Dishon, Ezer, chule Dishan ahi. Amaho hi Edom gam'a cheng Hor mi Seir chilhah a phung lamkaiho chu ahiuve.  
\v 22 Lotan chilhah ho chu Hori le Hemam ahi. Lotan sopinu min chu Timna ahi.  
\v 23 Shobal chilhah ho chu Alvan ahin, Manahath ahin, Ebal ahin, Shepho ahin, chule Onam ahi.  
\v 24 Zibeon chilhah chu Aiah le Anah ahi lhon'e. (Anah kitipa hin apa gancha sangante achin pet a gamthip lah a twisamputna ana mudoh ahi).  
\v 25 Anah chilhah chu achapa Dishon le achanu Oholibamah ahi lhone.  
\v 26 Dishon chilhah ho chu Hemdan, Eshban, Ithran chule Keran ahiuve.  
\v 27 Ezer chilhah ho chu Bilhan ahin, Zaavan ahin, chule Akan ahiuve.  
\v 28 Dishan chilhah chu Uz le Aran ahi lhone.  
\v 29 Hor mite upa lamkai ho chu Lotan ahin, Shobal ahin, Zibeon ahin, Anah ahin,  
\v 30 Dishon, Ezer chule Dishan ahiuvin aphungmin uhi phung lamkaiho min dungjuiya kisah Seir gamsunga cheng ho chu ahiuve.   
\s1 Edom lengte ho  
\p
\v 31 Hiche lengho hi Israel mite lah a lengvaipo ana um masanga Edom gamsunga lengvaipo ho chu ahiuve.  
\v 32 Beor chapa Bela chun Edom gamsunga lengvai anapon, ama khopi chu amin Dinhabah ahiye.  
\v 33 Bela athi jou chun Zerah chapa Jobab chapa chu Bozrah gamsunga vaipon ahung pangin ahi.  
\v 34 Jobab athi jou chun Teman mi Husham mipa chun lengvai ahin hom kittai.  
\v 35 Husham thi jou chun Bedad chapa Hadah chun lengvai ahinpon, ama chenna khopi Avith a pat in Moab gamsunga Midian ho jouse gal'a ahin joutan ahi.  
\v 36 Hadad thi jou chun Masrekah khopi a cheng Samlah in apanmun ahinlo kittai.  
\v 37 Samlah thi jou chun vadung a um Rehoboth khopi a cheng Shaul chun apanmun alon ahi.  
\v 38 Shaul thi jou chun Achor chapa Baal-hannan kitipa chun lengvai ahipo kit in ahi.  
\v 39 Acbor chapa Baal-hannan thijou chun Hadar in Pau khopi apat in lengvai ahipo pantan, Hadar jinu min chu Mehetabel ahin Matred chanu Me-zahab dinga atunu ahi.  
\v 40 Amaho phung lamkai jouse hi Esau chilhah a konna hung kondoh cheh ahiuvin, Timna gam'a cheng ahiuvin, mi upa Alvah ahin, mi upa Jetheth ahin,  
\v 41 Mi upa Oholibamah ahin, mi upa Elah ahin, mi upa Pinon ahin,  
\v 42 Mi upa Kenaz ahin, mi upa Teman ahin, mi upa Mibzar ahin,  
\v 43 Mi upa Magdiel ahin, chule mi upa Iram ahi; hicheng hi leiset atoupha na gamsung uva akho mun dung jui uva Edom chilhah a kon a mi upaho chu ahiuve.   
\c 37  
\s1 Joseph le asopite  
\p
\v 1 Hichun Jacob Canaan chu apa khopemna Canaan gamsunga anung chen kit tai.  
\v 2 Hiche thusim ho hi Jacob insung mite a ahi, Joseph kum som le sagi alhinin apa kelngoi ho asopi ho toh achingtup jingin avahva jingun, asopi ho apa jithah chate ho Bilhah le Zilpah chate ho toh natong khom jing ahiuve. Ahin nikhat chu Joseph in asopiho umchan phatlou dan apa kom ahin lhut tan ahi.  
\v 4 Amavang asopi te hon Joseph chu avetda cheh un ahi, ajeh chu apan midang ho sanga Joseph angailutna jeh in ama hon Joseph henga ngailut thucheng thupha seiding hahsa asa lheh un ahi.  
\v 5 Joseph in nikhat mang aneiyin amang chu asopiho aseipeh le ama hon avetda cheh un ahi.  
\v 6 Aman aseijin, “Hiche mang hi ngaiyun,” ati.  
\v 7 “Ehon lou lama changphal ikan khom un, hiche tah chun hetman louvin keima changphal ho chu ading doh in, nangho changphal ho chu keima changphal masanga abohkhup uve,” ati.  
\v 8 Hichun asopi hon adonbut un, “Amapa chun keiho chunga vaihom ding kigong nahim? Ahilouleh keiho chunga thanei ding kigo mong nahim,” atiuve. Hichun ama hon amang nei toh athusei doh ho jeh in hatah in avetda uvin ahi.  
\v 9 Joseph in mang khat aneibe kit in chuin asopi ho chu aseipeh kit in aman aseiye, “Ngaijun mang khat kaneibe kit e,” ati. “Nisa, lha, chule ahsi som le khat ho jong keima masanga abohkhup cheh uve,” ati.  
\v 10 Tua mang aneipa hi Joseph in apa chule asopi teho jouse jong abonchan aseipeh sohkeiyin ahi. “Hiche mang chu ipi tina ham?” tin adongin, “Nanu toh kei chule nasopi te ho jouse atahbeh a kahung uva nang masanga kahung bohkhup dingu ham?” tin apan aphoh thip e.  
\v 11 Amavang Joseph sopiho chu alunghang lheh un athangthip thei lheh un, apa vang chun hiche mang chu ipi tina ham tin alungdong lheh in ahi. \x + \xo 37:11 \xt Act 7:9\x*   
\s1 Joseph kijoh doh  
\p
\v 12 Phat chomkhat jou chun Joseph sopiho chu Schechem lama apa kelngoi ching dingin achekit tauvin ahi.  
\v 13 Amaho chedoh jou phat chomkhat jouvin, Jacob in Joseph kom'a aseiye, “Nasopi te hon Schechem lam a kelngoi hon ho aga vah un ahin, nangma naga chelou khoh ahi atin, Joseph in adonbut in, “Keima kaga che ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 14 Jacob in adonbut in, “Nangma gache inlang na sopi te ho chule kelngoi ho iti hinauvem gaven ati. Amaho thusoh kajah nom kitne, Hebron phaicham apat in asol tan, hichun Joseph hiche Schechem chu ahunglhung tan ahi.  
\v 15 Ahin vetan gamlah a lampi akimansah a avakoile na a mi khat in atoh khan mipa chun adongin “Ipi ham nahol le?” atile.  
\v 16 Joseph in adonbut in, “Ka sopi te ho kahol ahi atin, hoi langa gancha ho achin uham nei seipeh thei ding ham,” ati.  
\v 17 Mipa chun adonbut in, “Amaho kihoulimna kajan eiho Dothan lama chetau hite,” akitiuve.  
\v 18 Joseph ahung chun asopi hon gamla thimtah ahivangin ahepai tauvin, ama ahung lhun masang'in asopi te hon Joseph thadohna ding tohgon anei tauvin ahi.  
\v 19 “Tuhin mang neipa ahung tai,” atiuve.  
\v 20 “Hungun ama hi that doh taute, chule hiche kotong ho sung khat a paimang utin ipau kom'a hitin seiyu hite, “Gancha khat in Joseph chu a nedoh tai, chule eihon veu hite ama amang ho chu hunggui lhung nam,” atiuve.  
\v 21 Ahin Reuben in amaho tohgon lungthim ho chu ahet phat in Joseph kithopi dingin ahungin, “Aman aseitai Joseph hi tha datau hite,” ati.  
\v 22 Ibola thisan imoh lonsah ding'u ham? Hilai kotong gamgo lah a seplut leuhen ama chamin eihon that hih jong leuhen ama thi talou ding ham. Reuben chun alungthima Joseph chu huhdoh tei ding tichu ama dei ahi.  
\v 23 Hichun Joseph ahung lhun chun asopi te hon a sangkhol chol hoitah chu asut lhah peh pai tauvin ahi.  
\v 24 Hichun ama hon Joseph chu aman uvin kotong sunga aseplut tauvin, hiche kotong chu imacha umlou twi jong veilou ahi.  
\v 25 Chule amaho anne dinga aum laitah un, aga dadoh uva ahile vetan Gilead a konna hung sumkol veile Ishmael miho a sangan ho toh hung kilhona bego le thingthao namtui toh chule lou namtui hinpoa Egypt gam lang jonsuh ding amu uvin ahi.  
\v 26 Hichun Judah in a sopiho jah a aseiyin, “Isopi pau itha doh uva ipi apha chom ding um ham? Chule athisan iselmang uva chu ipi phachom ding ham?  
\v 27 Hung uvin Joseph hi Ishmael te kom'a johdoh tau hite, isopi nah nah iphe ivou nah nah chu achunga jong ikhut lhapou hite,” atile asopi ten jong asei angai cheh tauve.  
\v 28 Hiti chun Egypt gam'a kivei miho chun apui tauvin Joseph chu asopi hon kotong a kon'in a kaidoh un, Ishmael miho Midian miho kom'a dangka somni in akijoh doh tauve. \x + \xo 37:28 \xt Act 7:9\x*  
\v 29 Phat chomkhat jouvin, Reuben chu kokhuh langa chun achekit in ahile Joseph chu kokhuh sunga ana um tapoi, hichun Reuben chu alung akham lheh jengtan asangkhol ho chu abottel in ahi.  
\v 30 Hichun Reuben asopiho lah a akinungle kit in lungkham tah in, “Joseph chu aum tapoi! tua hi keiman ipi kabol ding hitam?” ati.  
\v 31 Hichun Joseph sopihon kelnou khat athat uvin, athisan chu Joseph sangkhol a chun anu tauve.  
\v 32 Ama hon hichu sangkhol thisan anu uchu apau Jacob athot un, mihon jong apau henga achoi uvin, “Hiche pihi ka mudoh uve, vetemin na chapa sangkhol chol hilou ham?” atiuve.  
\v 33 Jacob in gangtah in ahedoh paijin, hitin aseitai, “Hiche hi kachapa sangkhol ahi monge gamsa khat in vang anehdoh ahitai, Joseph vang hi aphe avou lahthei hita ponte,” ati.  
\v 34 Hichun Jacob in apon ho chu abottel in khaodip pon akikhu khum tan, Aman nisottah lunghemin genthei tah in achapa pul adoutan ahi.  
\v 35 Jacob chate jouse le achanute jousen lhepbi ding agong un, ahin amavang lhepbi jou ahi tapoi, hitin amapan aseiye, “Keiman lunghem pum in kachapa lhankhuh jon tang kate,” tin Jacob chu akap e.  
\v 36 Phat chomkhat jou chun Midian miho chun Joseph chu Potiphar kitipa Pharaoh Egypt lengpa Semang Pachong pa kom'a ajoh doh tauve. Potiphar natoh chu ahile sepai lah a semang pachong ahi.   
\c 38  
\s1 Judah le amounu Tamar  
\p
\v 1 Hiche phat laitah chun Judah chun asopite adalhan Adullam kiti mun'a Hirah kitipa toh ana cheng khom lhonin ahi.  
\v 2 Chule Judah in Canaan numei Shua chanu chu akichenpin chule ana kitimatpi tan ahi.  
\v 3 Amanu chu ahung kivopmon chapa ahin neitan chule nao min chu Er asahtan ahi.  
\v 4 Chuin amanu akivopmo kit in chapa khat ahin hinbe kit in nao min chu Onan asah tai.  
\v 5 Abanin amanun chapa athum lhinna pa chu amin Shelah asah in, Shelah pen laitah a chu amaho Kezib kiti mun'a achen laitah u ahiye.  
\v 6 Phat chomkhat jouvin, Judah in achapa atahpen Er dingin numei khangthah amin Tamar chu ajidin apuipeh e.  
\v 7 Hinlah Er chu migilou miphamo tah ahijeh chun Pakaiyin ahinkho aladoh tai.  
\v 8 Hichun Judah in Onan kitipa, Er sopipa kom'a hitin aseiye, “Nangma che inlang Tamar khu gaki chenpi tan, ajeh chu pasal khat insunga ahinkho abeitah le dan in aphal ahi, asopipan avet thei ding, na sopipa dinga chilhah na semdoh peh tei ding ahi.”  
\v 9 Amavang Onan kitipa chu anompon ama chilhah ahilou ding chu, hijeh chun asopipa ji toh alupkhom lhona akitimat teng abotwi ho chu tollhanga abolha jin, hijeh chun Tamar chun nao avop thei tapon asopipa adin jong chilhah gou aumdoh jou tapon ahi.  
\v 10 Amavang Pakaiyin Onan umchan chu gilou engse asa lheh in asopipa athisa adin chapa ahin peh nomlou athangthip jeh ahi, hijeh chun Pakaiyin Onan hinkho jong asuh chom pehtai.  
\v 11 Hichun Judah in Tamar amounu jah a hitin aseiye, “Kachapa Shelah kikhanlhit kah in napa in'a meithaijin ga umdoh tan,” ati. Ijeh-inem itile asopi teni bangin ama jong thiget inte tia ana gel ahi. Hijeh chun Tamar jong achen apa innah aga chengtai.  
\v 12 Phat chomkhat jouvin Judah jinu jong athi tai; ahin Judah chu akilhep lungmong dom phat in agolpa Adullam mi Hirah chutoh Timnah a akelngoi mul vouho henga aga che tauve.  
\v 13 Koiham khat in Tamar chu aseipeh in, “Ven natehpu khu Timnah a kelngoi mul vou dingin ache touve,” atipeh e.  
\v 14 Chuphat in amanun jong ameithai von chu akhel loijin, ponlu akikhun, akitomjol in Timnah lampia Enaim lamkot a chun atou tai; ijeh-inem itile Shelah kikhanlhit ahitan, aji dinga amanu akipeh lou akimu ahitai.  
\v 15 Judah in amanu chu amun ahin amanun amai asel jeh chu numei kijoh ho ahisah in ahi.  
\v 16 Hichun ama akingapa in amounu ahilam chu helouvin amanu chu ajollin, “Keiman nangma kitimatpi inge” ati. Hichun Tamar in “Kei nei kitimatpi ding leh ipi ijat neipeh ding ham?” atileh,  
\v 17 “Keima kelchanou lah a khat nahin thah peh nang'e,” tin kitepna aneiyin ahi. Hichun amanun adongin, “Kelchanou nahin pehtei ding kihetna a ipi kitepna neipeh ding ham,” ati.  
\v 18 Judah in adongin, “Itobang kitepna nadei ham?” ati. Amanun adonbut in, “Na Mohor le nakhao toh chule nakhut a nachoi na tenggol chutoh,” ati. Hijeh chun amapan hichengse chu apen amanu chu aluppin ahile aman jong nao avop tai.  
\v 19 Phat chomkhat jouvin, Tamar a in lama a kinungle kit in a sangkhol chol akoi lhan masanga akivonna lui meithai sangkhol chu akivon in til a bang chun hinkho amang kittai.  
\v 20 Judah chun kelchanou chu aloipa Adullam mipa khut a numeinu henga khamgahna thil lhatdoh dinga aga thahsah a ahile, Adullam mipan amanu chu agaholmo tan ahi.  
\v 21 Hichun Adullam mipa Hirah in hikom'a cheng ho chu adongin, “Enaim jotna a tou numeinu aki johnu chu hoilam a che hitam, ama hon adonbut un, “Keima hon hikom'a hin numei phalou atahsa joh kamu kha pouve,” atiuve.  
\v 22 Hichun Adullam mipa Hirah ahung kinunglen thu umchan ho chu Judah aseipeh tan ahi, “Keiman amanu umna chu kahol doh jou tapoi, chule chua cheng mihon jong hitobang numei phalou atahsa joh aumpoi,” atiuve.  
\v 23 Judah in aseiye, “Thil kana pehho chu amanun eina koipeh mai tahen, kaki nopto nalhon dungjuijin kelchanou khat kapen ahin nangman na holmo tan, amanu chu inung hol kit le khosunga mijousen ei nuisat ding'u ahitai.”  
\v 24 Lhathum jou don chun Judah chu mihon aseipeh tauvin, “Tamar na mounu chu numei kijoh banga ana bol thu ahije, chule tuhin amanun nao avoptai,” atiuve.” Hichun Judah in aseiye, “Amanu chu hinpui doh unlang halvam tauvin,” ati.  
\v 25 Amavang ama hon Tamar chu tha dingin ahin puidoh tauvin, Tamar in atehpu thu athot in hitin aseiye, “Hiche thil neipa tenggol ahin, khaodip ahin, Mahor ahin, koi thil pen ham? Ipi dinga thip beh cha uma ham hiche neipa a konna hi nao kavop ahi,” ati.  
\v 26 Judah in gangtah in ama nei le gou chu amu mun ageldoh paitan ahi, “Tamar hi keima sanga chonpha jo ahiye ati. Ajeh chu keiman kachapa Shelah toh akichen lhon na ding imacha kana gonlou jeh ahi,” ati, chupet tah chun Judah chu Tamar toh apum kitimat tapoi.  
\v 27 Tamar dinga nao neina phat ahung naitan, amanun nao pasal ni pengkop ding ahi chu ahe tauvin ahi.  
\v 28 Naoso nat akipan tan hiche pet tah chun naocha teni lah a khatpa akhut ahung doh in hichun numei lhacha a pangho chun patsan akhut a akanpeh un, “Hiche pa hi hung peng masa ahi,” atiuve.  
\v 29 Hinlah hiche naocha chun akhut akailut kit tan, asopipa joh ahung peng masa tai. Hichun numei lhacha ho chun “Hiche hi ipi ham atiuve.” Nangin iti dan'a amasa a peng dingpa nahin chop khup ham atiuve.” Hichun amapa min chu Perez asah tauve.  
\v 30 Chujouvin, naosen patsan a akhut kikanpa chu ahung peng tan hichun amapa min chun Zerah asah tauve.   
\c 39  
\s1 Joseph le Potiphar jinu  
\p
\v 1 Joseph chu Egypt gam'a ana puijun hiche apat a chu Ishmael sum-kolvei mihon Potiphar kitipa kom'a ana joh un ahi. Potiphar natoh chu Egypt lengpa Pharaoh sepai lamkai a pang ahi.  
\v 2 Pathen'in Joseph chu aumpi jingin, hijeh chun Egypt gamsunga abol lam jousea alolhing jingin ahi. \x + \xo 39:2 \xt Act 7:9\x*  
\v 3 Joseph chu Pathen'in aumpi chu athil bolna jousea kon'in apupan ahin muchen tan ahi.  
\v 4 Hichun Potiphar chu Joseph chunga alunglhai lheh jengin, Joseph chu ama ban tah in akoi tan ahi. Chule Potiphar in Joseph chu a insung jouse chule anei agou jouse vetup dingin atungdoh tan ahi.  
\v 5 Hiche nia pat a chun Joseph chu apupa Potiphar in insunga ima jouse vetup in anganse tai, chule Joseph chonphat jeh chun Pakai phatthei bohna chu Potiphar insunga achutan ahi. Hiti chun a insung a thil ijakai akitup tan, chule alousohga ho ahin chuleh agancha ho jong apung thei tauvin ahi.  
\v 6 Hichun Potiphar in Joseph chu ama insung vetup ding le anei agou ho jouse vetup dingin thaneina jouse apedohtai, chule Joseph umjeh chun aman imacha ah akisaboi tapon, lungkhamna jong aum tapon, chule aneh ding anneh tilou thil dang athil dang imacha ahepha tapoi. Joseph chu mi mel-hoitah vetnom nom um khat ahi.  
\v 7 Chule phat chomkhat jouvin, apupa loinun Joseph chu ahin velel tan, “Hung in eini lumkhom hitin kitimat hite tin Joseph chu ajol tai.”  
\v 8 Amavang Joseph anom pon, Joseph in Potiphar inneipi chu hitin adonbut e, “Ka pupan hiche insunga thil ho jouse vetup dinga ei nganse ahi.  
\v 9 Hiche insunga hi keima tilou thanei dang aumpoi, kapupan nangma chunga thaneina eipe poi, ajeh chu nangma aloinu nahi jeh in hitobang thil phalou chu iti keiman katoh a Pathen douna a chonset kabol ding ham,” ati.  
\v 10 Hiti chun amanun aniseh in Joseph chu ano ano jengin, amavang Joseph chu amanu toh lupkhom a kitimat ding chu pum noplou ahin, ahithei chan a jammang ding joh chu agot ahiye.  
\v 11 Nikhat vang chu koimacha umlouna achun Joseph chu ama ngaiya natong dingin achen ahi.  
\v 12 Amanu chu ahung lut in asangkhol ah akaijin, “Hung loiyin eini ilup khom lhon ding ahi!” ati. Hichun Joseph in asangkhol asut lhan akitom doh tai. Ahin asangkhol chu Potiphar loinu khutna adalha den tan ahi.  
\v 13 Hichun Joseph la ajamdoh tan ahin amanun akhut a um asangkhol chu achoiyin,  
\v 14 Amanun insunga asohte jouse akou khom sohkeiyin, hiche phat chun pasal jousen ahin dellut cheh un, amanun hitin aseiye, “Veuvin! Ei ngolbol diuvin hiche Hebrew sohpa hi kajipan ahin puilut e! Amapa hi kei suse din ka insung denna ahunglut in, ahin keima o sangtah in kapeng in ahi.  
\v 15 Keima hatah a o sangtah a kapen phat in polam a ajamdoh in alhaimang tai, ahin aman asangkholchol chu kakom'a adalha dentai” ati.  
\v 16 Hiti chun amanun sangkhol chu aloipa in ahung lhun masang'in phate chan akoitup sellin ahi.  
\v 17 Hichun amanun aloipa kom'a thusoh ho chu aseitai; “Hebrew sohpa nahin puilut pa khun insunga ahung lut in suhset ding eigoi,” atitai.  
\v 18 Amavang keima o sangtah a kapen phat in polam ah ajamdoh in a sangkhol adalhah ahi.  
\v 19 Hichun Potiphar chun ajinu thusim Joseph in amanu chunga athilbol chu ajahdoh phat chun hatah in alunghang lheh tan.  
\v 20 Hijeh chun Potiphar in Joseph chu songkul'a akoitan chule lengpa songkul'a umho to akihen khom un, ama jong hiti chun aum den tai.  
\v 21 Ahin Pathen'in Joseph chu songkul'a jong aumpi jingin, angailutna ho jong avetsah jingin chule Pathen'in Joseph chu songkul ngahpa to jong kingailutna apekit tai. \x + \xo 39:21 \xt Act 7:9\x*  
\v 22 Phat chomkhat jouvin songkul ngahpan Joseph chu songkul'a umho lah a alenpen in akoitan, hiche songkul sunga thilsoh bouina jouse chu Joseph thaneina noiya akoitai.  
\v 23 Pathen'in Joseph chu aumpi jeh in imacha boina aum tapoi, athil bolna anatohna jouse alolhingsel in hijeh chun songkul ngahpa jong imacha aboi tapoi, ajeh chu thil jouse Joseph in anga jeh chun imacha aphamo ding aumpoi.   
\c 40  
\s1 Joseph in janmang ni alepeh  
\p
\v 1 Hicheng thilsoh kichai nung chun Pharaoh lengpa natong ju vaihompa le an vaihompan apupa Egypt lengpa doumah abol lhonin achonse lhontai.  
\v 2 Hiche lamkai teni chunga hin Pharaoh nasatah in alunghang tan ahi.  
\v 3 Chuin Pharaoh in amani chu Joseph umna lengpa songkul natong ho umna ah akoiyin ahi.  
\v 4 Songkul ngahpan amani chu Joseph thaneina noiya a umsah in Joseph in jong amani chu vetkolna anei jingin ahi.  
\v 5 Jan khat chun songkul sunga kihen teni Egypt lengpa ju vaihompa le an vaihompa chun mang khat cheh, amang ledohna toh kilhon cheh in anei lhonin ahi.  
\v 6 Ajing jingkah a Joseph in amani amu chun lungkham mel aput lhon chu ahedoh tai.  
\v 7 “Ipi dia hibanga lhungkham nahi lhon ham?” tin adong’e.  
\v 8 Amanin adonbut lhonin, “Janlhah in keinin mang kanei gel lhonin amavang koima chan kamang ipi kiseina ahi aledoh thei aumpoi,” ati lhon e, ahin Joseph in adonbut in, “Mang letheina kiti hi Pathen kin ahi.” Chule “Namang lhon chu neisei peh lhonin” ati.  
\v 9 Hichun khon dom le a pang lamkaipa chun Joseph chu amang ho chu aseipeh tai. “Ka mangin lengpi bah ka masanga kamun ahi.  
\v 10 Hiche lengpi phunga chun abah thum ajam kamun, gang tah in ahung mum in chuin apahlha tai, hiche aga ho chu lengpi theiga ahung hitai.  
\v 11 Pharaoh chakhon chu ka khut chunga ana um'in, hichun keiman lengpiga phabep chu atwi khon a chun kahehlhan ahi” ati.  
\v 12 “Mangin avetsah chu hiche hi ahi,” tin Joseph in aseijin. “Thingbah thum chu nithum vetsahna ahi.”  
\v 13 Nithum sunga hin Pharaoh in nadomtou intin, chule masanga na natohna a nanung koi kit ding ahi.  
\v 14 Chule nangma kom'a katao ahi, chanvou pha nahung chan teng neihin sumil hihbeh in Pharaoh kom'a hitobang ka thilbol ho hi eina seipeh in, ajeh chu songkul'a konna eilha doh theina dingin, ati.  
\v 15 Ajeh chu Hebrew gam a ka in apat a eikiman doh tua hiche songkul'a kaum hi mona neilou kahin bolkhel kaneipoi.  
\v 16 Hichun changlhah hom'a lamkaipa chun mang aphalam a hoitah a Joseph in ale chu amu le ama jong atha anom lheh in; Joseph jah ah hitin aseiye, “Keiman jong janmang kaneiye, ka manga chun paipeh thum changlhah dimset kalu chunga kapun ahi.  
\v 17 Pharaoh a dingin Paipeh achunga pa sunga chun changlhah ajat lhingsel in aum in, ahin vacha ho ahung lengun ka luchunga changlhah ho chu anedoh tauve.”  
\v 18 Joseph in amang chu alepeh tan, “Paipeh thum chun nithum ma avetsah ahin,  
\v 19 Nithum sunga hi Pharaoh in nalu adopsang ding thingphunga nakhai sanga, vachaten naphe anehchai ding'u ahi.”  
\v 20 Pharaoh in nithum jouvin ama penni kipapina in anoiya a semang pachonga pang jouse akou khom in hiche a pang dinga chu ju vaihom lamkaipa le an vaihom lamkaipa chu alhadoh gel in,  
\v 21 Ju vaihom pa chu aju vaihomna ma man apansah kit in, aman jong jukhon chu Pharaoh khut a agapetai.  
\v 22 Ahin an vaihom lamkaipa vang chu Joseph in amani henga mang alepeh bang chun akhai lih tan ahi.  
\v 23 Hichun ju vaihom lamkaipan Joseph chu ageldoh tapon asumil deltai.   
\c 41  
\s1 Joseph in Pharaoh mang ale peh  
\p
\v 1 Kumni nungin Pharaoh in mang aneiyin ahile, vetan ama Nile vadung panga ana dingin ahi.  
\v 2 Amanga chun bongchal sagi athao a thao cheh ahung kaldoh un hamhing lah a chun alhauvin ahi.  
\v 3 Chujou in amaho nunga chun bongchal sagi ma agon a gong cheh Nile vadunga kon chun ahung doh un, vadung panga bongchal sagi dang ho kom'a chun ading uvin ahi.  
\v 4 Hichun bongchal agong ho chun bongchal athao sagi ho chu aval lhum tauvin ahi! Hiche mang anei pettah chun Pharaoh chu ahung khang doh tai.  
\v 5 Ahin Pharaoh a imulhu kit in mang aniveina aneiyin, hiche amanga hin changphal sagi hoitah vetnom nom um phungkhat a konna hung kikhai lha amun ahi.  
\v 6 Hichun changphal sagi amanga amu kit in ahin hiche changphal ho chu ageo cheh chuh jengin, solam huijin amut geo lheh jeng ahi.  
\v 7 Chuin hiche geo cheh chuh changphal ho chun changphal lom sagi ahoi phungkhat a kikhai lha ho chu aval lhum kittai. Hichun Pharaoh ahung khangin ahile ajanmang ahi chu ageldoh in ahi.  
\v 8 Hiche ni jingkah apat in Pharaoh chu amang ho chun asuboi lheh in aum thei tapoi. Hichun Pharaoh Egypt gamsung a mitphel doi themho le miching jouse akou khomin amang chu aseitan, ahin amaho lah a khatbeh in jong ipi kiseina ham ti chu adonbut thei aum pouve. \x + \xo 41:8 \xt Daniel 2:2\x*  
\v 9 Phat chaina lang chun lengpa jukhon doma lamkai pa chu ahung ding doh in, “Tunia keiman geldoh khat kaneiye phat masa a kana chatvaina,” atin Pharaoh kom'a aseitan ahi.  
\v 10 Nangma nasoh teni chunga nana lunglhai pon changlhah hom lamkaipa le keima chunga, hijeh chun keini hi lengpa songkul'a neina koiyin ahi.  
\v 11 Nikhat chu changlhah hompa le keiman mang chom cheh kanei lhonin ka mang lhon jong chu thusim chom cheh kanei lhonin,  
\v 12 Hiche lai phat chun Hebrew khangthah khat lengpa songkul'a chun keiho toh ana um'in, ama chu lengpa semang pachong pa soh a jong ana pang ahi, kamang nei lhon chu kasei lhonin ahile aman kamang lhon chu eiledoh peh lhon e, ati.  
\v 13 Chule aman eiledoh peh lhon bang bang chun ahung guilhung cheh in ahi, keiman ka natoh ngai ngai eikitohsah in an vaihompa akikhai lihtan ahi.”  
\v 14 Pharaoh in Joseph chu ahol in mi asol paijeng tan ama chu agan a gangin songkul'a kon'in ahin puidoh jeng uvin, chuin avon ho akikhel in chule akhamul ho a kisuhtheng in, hichun ama Pharaoh toh kimuto din alut tai.  
\v 15 Hichun Pharaoh in Joseph kom'a aseitai, “Keiman janlhah in mang ka neijin koima chan aledoh thei pon ahin keiman kajah chu ahile mang kiti ho hi nangman hettheina nanei chu kana jai.”  
\v 16 Joseph in adonbut in, “Hiche ho chu keima a dinga thil hahsa ahi, ati. Amavang Pathen'in hiche ipi tina ham chu nahetsah theiye,” ati.  
\v 17 Chuin Pharaoh in amang chu Joseph kom'a aseitai, aman hitin aseiye, “Ka mangin Nile vadung panga kana dingin,  
\v 18 hiche a chun bongchal sagi hoitah kivah thao cheh vadunga kon chun ahung doh un chule hilaiya hampa dong ho chu anepan tauvin ahi.  
\v 19 Hinlah keiman chom khat jouvin bongchal adang sagi agon a gong ahoimo cheh ahung potdoh kit kamun, keiman hitobang gancha gong aphe umlou Egypt gamsunga ka hinkhon kana mukha hih laiye.  
\v 20 Hiche bong agong melse tah ho chun bongchal sagi athao ho chu aval lhum tan ahi.  
\v 21 Achuti jeng vang chun akikhel muthei aumpoi, ajeh chu amaho chu masanga bangin agong nalai un ahi. Chujouvin keima kahung khangdoh tan ahi.  
\v 22 Hichun keima ka imu lhukit in, chule keiman mang khat kaneibe kit in, hichea kamang achun changvui sagi vetnom umtah phungkhat a ga kamun ahi.  
\v 23 Chule changvui sagi ma chu akiveigeosa akeoseh cheh, nisolam khohui mut geosa cheh chu ahung kilahdoh in ahi.  
\v 24 Chuin changvui ageosa ho chun changvui hoitah ho chu avallhum kittan, hiche kamang ho hi doithem ho kom'a kaseiyin, hinlah kamang ho chu ipi kiseina ham koima chan eihil chen theipoi, ati.  
\v 25 Joseph in adonbut in, “Pharaoh mang teni hi thakhat ahi, Pathen'in Pharaoh hi ipi abol ding ahin hetsah masah ahi bouve.  
\v 26 Bongchal sagi athao ahoi ho chule changvui sagi vetnom nom uma, aga hon avet sah nom chu ahile kum sagi sunga hi neh le chah neng ding avetsah ahi,” ati.  
\v 27 Chule bongchal sagi agong ho leh changvui sagi ageosa aphunga goden solam huiyin asemgot den hon avetsah chu ahile kum sagi nasa tah a kel hunglha ding chu avetsah ahi.”  
\v 28 “Hiche ho hi keiman ka phondoh banga hung guilhung ding ahi, ajeh chu Pathen'in Pharaoh hi aphat ahung lhun masanga ipi abol ding ho chu ahin hetsah ahiye, ati.  
\v 29 Tu apat a Egypt gamsung'a hi kum sagi hatah a neh le chah hung neng ding ahi.  
\v 30 Amavang hiche jou le chun kum sagi ma kel nasatah in hung lhan tin, chuteng chule chun Egypt gamsung ima ma ana thalhing chu kisumil gam'a, kellhah chun agamsung abahgam jeng ding ahitai.  
\v 31 Hiche kel hung khoh hi gimnei lheh jeng ding kum tamtah neh le chah ana ning lhinna ho jouse chu koiman ageldoh louding ahitai.  
\v 32 Pharaoh mang teni ahung ki hetsahna thupi pentah chu ahile, Pathen'in na ahintoh vah ding ahi ti gontup sa ahitai, hunglhung vah tei ding ahi, ati.  
\v 33 Hijeh a chu Pharaoh in achingthei tah pasal chule thil hethem tah koitobang aholdoh a Egypt gamsung pumpia mopo thei ahol angai tai.  
\v 34 Hichun Pharaoh in agam agam a lamkai avetup ding mi lhengdoh henlang hiche teng chule louga sohho kum sagi neh anen sung chun hop nga lah a hop khat koidoh uhenlang,  
\v 35 Pharaoh thaneina noiya tu apatna neh le chah hiche kum sunga hatah a anen pet ahin changpang ahin koi dimset un, phate chan koitup uhenlang chule angah jong um jing hen, kho nung chan geiya khopi sunga neh le chah um jing theina din, ati.  
\v 36 Tua chang le mim ho jouse hi phate chan mun khat a gamsung pumpin koikhom uhen, chutile kum sagi sunga nasatah a kel ahung khoh teng Egypt gamsunga mipi jouse kihinso thei ding ahi.”   
\s1 Egypt gamsung'a Joseph vaihom  
\p
\v 37 Hiche lungthim tohgon hi Pharaoh ahin ama semang pachong hon jong pha asa cheh tauvin ahi.  
\v 38 Hichun Pharaoh in amaho chu adongin, “Eihon hitobang pasal Pathen Lhagao chenna hi imujou dingu hi nam?” ati.  
\v 39 Hiche pet chun Pharaoh in Joseph ahoulimpi in, “Ajeh chu Pathen'in ima jouse nangma nahetsah tah jeh in nang tobang koimacha ahethem le aching aum tapoi.  
\v 40 Nangma keima leng touna a natou ding ahitai, kami ten nangma thupeh jouse ajui cheh dingu ahitai. Chule thil khat bou ikikhehna ding chu keima ka lengvai pohna a bou lenjo ding kahi, ati. \x + \xo 41:40 \xt Act 7:10\x*  
\v 41 Pharaoh in Joseph jah ah aseitan, “Keiman nangma hi Egypt gamsunga thaneina le mopohna kapeh doh nahitai,” ati.  
\v 42 Hichun Pharaoh in akhut a sana khutjem chu aladoh in Joseph khut a abupeh tai. Aman vonkang hoitah akivonsah in chule sana khi jong angong a aki osah tai. \x + \xo 41:42 \xt Daniel 5:29\x*  
\v 43 Hichun lengpan Joseph chu asakol chunga atousah in amasanga chun “Mihon dilsu vo tin asam uvin ahi.” Hiti hin aman Joseph chu Egypt gam pumpi semang in ana pansah tai.  
\v 44 Chule Pharaoh in Joseph kom'a hitin aseiye, “Nangma phatsah louva Egypt gamsunga koima chan akhut alapthei louding, keima amin'a bou Pharaoh kahi ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 45 Hichun Pharaoh in Joseph chu Egypt te min Zaphenath-paneah asah in, chuleh Potiphera chanu Asenath chu Joseph ji din Pharaoh in agontup peh in ahi. Hiche apatna chu Joseph in Egypt gamsunga mopohna alah ahitai.  
\v 46 Egypt lengpa Pharaoh kom'a anatong dinga alut chun Joseph kum somthum alhing tai. Chuin Joseph chu Pharaoh angsunga kon'in apotdoh in Egypt gam leiset pumpi aga kholsoh keiyin ahi.  
\v 47 Ana kisei bang chun kum sagi sung chun neh le chah lousoh hatah in apungin ahi.  
\v 48 Hiche kum sagi sunga chun Joseph in chang le mim Egypt gamsunga kimu jouse chu mun khat a akoikhom sohkeiyin, chule khopi jousea akoina mun asem sohkeiyin ahi.  
\v 49 Hichun Joseph in chang le mim chu tamtah avum leovin akhol khom in, vadung panga neldi banga atamval tah jeh chun hetlut jou jong ahi tapon, achaina langa chun simsenglou ahitan sim jong asim tapouve.  
\v 50 Kellhah kum hung lhun masang chun On thempu pa Potiphera chanu Asenath chun Joseph dingin chapa ni ana hinpeh in  
\v 51 Joseph in achapa atahjo pa min chu Manasseh\f + \fr 41:51 \ft Manasseh: genthei tintang jouse suhmil na, chule insung mite jong mil jouta tina ahi\f* asah in, aman aseiyin, “Hiche hin ka Pathen'in kagentheina jouse eisuhmil sah tai, chule kapa insung jong abonchauvin kasumil sohtai,” tina ahi.  
\v 52 Joseph in achapa aneojo pa min chu Ephraim asah tai, aman hitin aseiye, “Ka Pathen'in ka hahsatna le ka gentheina jeh in lolhinna eipe tai,” ati.  
\v 53 Egypt gamsunga kum sagi sunga chang le mim mang ketkut a ga jouse chu ahung kichai gamtan ahi.  
\v 54 Hichun kum sagi kellhah ahung kipan tan, Joseph in ana seidoh ma bangin hiche a nasatah a kellhah chun anaivel a gam ho jouse jong asuboi sohhel tai, amavang Egypt gamsunga chun neh le chah ahahsatna imacha aumpoi. \x + \xo 41:54 \xt Act 7:11\x*  
\v 55 Egypt gamsunga kel ahung khoh lheh jeng tan, hichun mipi ho chu neh le chah ngaichat jeh in Pharaoh kom'a ahungun, hichun Pharaoh in Egypt mipi te ho chu “Joseph kom'a asol in aman bol un atiho chu bol uvin,” ati. \x + \xo 41:55 \xt Jn 2:5\x*  
\v 56 Hiti chun kellhah chu hatah in ahung khohse cheh tan gamsung jouse aboilou aum tapon, Joseph in changpang ho jouse chu ahong doh tan, Egypt mipite chu akichoh sah tai. Ajeh chu Egypt gamsunga kel khoh chu asang lheh in hitobang kellhah chu ana um khahih laiye.  
\v 57 Chule gam dang dang Egypt gam kimvel a jousen neh le chah akichoh theina diuvin Joseph heng ahin nailut tauve, ajeh chu hitobang kellhah chun vannoi leiset chung jouse asuhboi cheh ahi.   
\c 42  
\s1 Joseph sopite Egypt ahung  
\p
\v 1 Hichun Egypt ma anneh anen dan chu Jacob in ahetan, achate jah a aseitai, “Ibola nadin chet chut uva kiveto nahiu ham?  
\v 2 Keiman thusoh kajan Egypt gam lama chang aum'e, hijeh chun nangho cheuvin lang neh ding gacho tauvin, eima ho ikihinso theina ding uvin,” ati. \x + \xo 42:2 \xt Act 7:12\x*  
\v 3 Hichun Joseph sopite mi som ho chu neh cho dingin Egypt lama achesuh tauvin ahi.  
\v 4 Hinlah Jacob in vang Joseph sopipa Benjamin chu amaho lah a asol tapoi, aman aseiyin, keima katija lheh tai ajoleh kisuhkhahna le boina toh khante, ati.  
\v 5 Canaan gam kel hah aum tah jeh chun Jacob chate chu Egypt lama anneh hol din mijouse toh ahunglhung khom tauve.  
\v 6 Tua hi Joseph chu Egypt gam'a chu vaihom ahitan, chule chang johna dinga thaneina jouse kipe ahitan, hiche pettah chun asopite ahunglhung tauvin, amaho ahung lhun lhunun, hikom'a chun tol'a amaho abohkhup un akunsoh tauve.  
\v 7 Joseph in asopite chu amu phat in abonchauvin ahe sohkeiyin, ahivangin amaho chu hetphah lou bol in, hutot tah-in ahouvin, chule ajah uva, “Hoiya konna hung nahiuvem?” atile ama hon jong “Canaan gam'a kon kahiuvin, puhsui dinga hung kahiuve,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 8 Joseph in asopiho chu ahet vang'in ama hon ahe doh jou pouve.  
\v 9 Hichun Joseph in kum tamtah masanga asopi ho mang ana mat ho chu ahin geldoh in asopi ho kom'a hitin aseiye, “Nangho hi miphalou le migucha nahiuve, keima ho gam hi lahmang thei ham ahilou le akihongbit jou pouve, tia neihung khol leu ahi,” ati. \x + \xo 42:9 \xt Semtilbu 37:5-10\x*  
\v 10 “Ahipoi ka pakai!” tin ama hon asam un ahi. Nasoh te ho hi anneh cho ding bou kahi jouve.  
\v 11 Keiho jouse hi pa khat a hung peng cheh kahi bouvui, milung theng kahiuve, nasoh ho hi miphalou kahi pouve!”  
\v 12 Ahin Joseph in aseikit leuvin, “Ahipoi nangho hin ka gam'u hi gam ong kivaipoh achavaiye tia nei hung khol leu ahi,” ati.  
\v 13 Hinlah ama hon adonbut uvin, “Nasoh te ho hi ucha pasal som le ni kahiuvin, pa khatna hung peng kahiuvin, Canaan gam'a incheng tuchung hin aneopen pa hi kapau toh kahin dalha uvin, chule mi khatpa vang aum tapoi.”  
\v 14 Joseph in adonbut in, “Keiman kasei banga nangho hi michom miphalou nahiuve!” ati.  
\v 15 Hichea hi nangma ho kapatep ding nahiuve, Pharaoh hinlai sea kakitep ahin asopi pau alhumpen pa nahin puikah seuva Egypt hi na dalhah louding'u ah!  
\v 16 Nangho lah a mikhat kisol uvin lang amapa chun na sopi pau chun hinpui henlang, chule adang ho se songkul'a na um ding'u, na thusei'u hi dihnam tia ka khol chil ding ahi; amavang hichu ahi louleh Pharaoh ahin laisea nangho hi michom, miphalou kiti chu nahiuve.  
\v 17 Hichun Joseph in amaho chu abonchauvin songkul'a nithum jen ahen in ahi.  
\v 18 Nithum lhin nin Joseph in aseiyin, “Keiman Pathen ging mi kahi. Kasei nabol uva ahileh nakihinso diu ahi.  
\v 19 Nangho hi milung theng nahiu leh nangho lah a mikhat hi songkul'a umden uvin lang, ahin adangse se vang kinungle cheh uvin, na insung mite din chang le mim kipoh un chetauvin.  
\v 20 Chule na sopi pau alhumpen pa chu keima kom'a nahin pui dingu, na thusei hou chu dihnam tia kakhol chil ding ahi. Chule nangho nathi lou dingu ahi.” Hichu ama hon jong pha asauve.  
\v 21 Hichun amaho khat le khat akihou limun, “Adihtah a sei dingin eiho hin isopi pau Joseph ibolset jeh uva gotna ichan'u ahitai. Ajeh chu eihon imusoh keijun aman ahinkho huhdohna dingin ataovin, hinlah eihon inahsah pouve, hiche ho jeh a chu tua hi gotna ho hi eiho chunga hung chu ahitai,” atiuve.  
\v 22 Hichun Reuben in amaho chu hitin adonbut in, “Keiman kasei hilou ham, chapang chu imachan bolse hih un, ahin ka thusei nangai pouvin, tua eihon ama thisan man chu isah diu ahitai.” \x + \xo 42:22 \xt Semtilbu 37:21,22\x*  
\v 23 Amaho kikah a paole aum jeh chun Joseph in amaho ahetchet u ahilam chu ama hon ahedoh pouvin ahi.   
\s1 Joseph sopite Canaan gam akile  
\p
\v 24 Hinlah Joseph akihei doh in achom lang angan akaptai, ahin ama ahung kinung hei kit in avelin amaho jah thei dingin ahoulim in, hichun amaho lah a Simeon chu alheng doh in amaho mitmu tah in akan tup tai.  
\v 25 Hichun Joseph in thu apen, amaho dip sunga chun chang khum peh uvin, chule sum ho jong chu ama ama dip sunga nung hetpeh un, chule lampia aneh dingu jong gonpeh uvin hiti chun amaho din thil gontup in aumtai.  
\v 26 Hichun asopi hon sangan chunga chun neh ding chang chu ahengdoh un a inlamu ahin jon tauve.  
\v 27 Ahin jan na akingah nauva amaho lah a mikhat pa chun sangan anneh peh ding agotan adip sung chu agah hondoh le adip sunga sum chu ahin mudoh tan ahi.  
\v 28 “Veuvin!” tin asopiho jah a aseiyin, “Kasum ho hi ka dip sunga eiki nungkoi peh!” Hichun amaho chu alungu alhadeh tauvin kithing pum pumin khat le khat akihou khom un, “Pathen'in ipi eito sah u hitante?” atiuve.”  
\v 29 Hichun amaho apau Jacob heng Canaan gamsung ahunglhung kit tauvin, hichun ama hon Jacob kom'a thil ahinto hou chu aseipeh ui.  
\v 30 “Gamneipa chun hiti hin aw sangtah in keiho jah din asam in, chule keiho hi miphalou gamsunga thilse bol dingin eigingmo un ahi.  
\v 31 Hinlah keihon amapa chu ka donbut un, keiho hi milung theng mikitah kahi bouvui katiuvin, chule keiho miphaloute kahi pouve.  
\v 32 Chule keima ho hi ucha sopi som le ni solam a hung kon kahiuvin, Pa khat in eihin'u ahin, mikhat vang ahing tapon chule aneopen pa vang tuhin ka pau toh Canaan gamsunga kahin dalha uve.  
\v 33 Hichun gamsung a lamkai pipu pa chun hitin eisei peh uve, nangma ho hi hitia kabol ding mipha milung theng nahiu kahet doh nadin, nangho lah a khat kidalha uvin, chule adang hon anneh ding chang le mim pouvin lang na inkote kom lang nung che tauvin.  
\v 34 Hinlah na sopipau alhumpen pa chu ka henga nahin puilut tei ding'u ahi ati, chule keiman hiche jou teng chule nangho hi mipha midih tah nahiu, michom le mikhol nahi pouve tichu kahet chet ding ahitai. Hiche teng chule nasopi pau chu kanung peh kit diu chule nang hon boina um louva navahsel a an jong nakihol theiyu ahi,” ati.  
\v 35 Adip u chu alhei lha uvin ahile vetan amitakip sum chun chu ama ama dip sung cheh a ana umsoh keiyin; ama hon jong apauvin jong a sum chun chengseu chu amudoh phat uvin akihot lhul gam tauve.  
\v 36 Jacob chu tijatah in ahoulim in, “Nangho hin ka chate ho neiguh mang peh cheh dingu ahitai! Joseph jong aum tapoi! Simeon jong aum tapoi! Tua nang hon Benjamin kisan nei puimang peh kit diu. Thil jouse hi keima douna jeng ahitai!”  
\v 37 Hichun Reuben in apa Jacob chu adonbut in, “Benjamin chu kahin nungpui louleh kacha teni hi nadei dei nalo thei ahitai, chule keiman Benjamin na dingin mopo nang kate ati, chule thon louva kahin nungpui kit teitei ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 38 Ahin Jacob in adonbut in, “Ka chapa chu nangma toh chelou ding ahi, ajeh chu aupa Joseph jong athi tan, tua kanei ka lungmonpi ama bou ahitai; ijem tin lamkim lang nagei tengu le lamkah lah a toset tohkha tahen lang hile kasam kan nung jenga jong lunghem a thikhol khul a nei lhohlut pai tahbah dingu ahi bouve,” ati.   
\c 43  
\s1 Benjamin apui uva Egypt ajot u  
\p
\v 1 Tuhin Canaan gamsunga kellhah chu akhoh cheh cheh jengin ahi.  
\v 2 Egypt gam'a konna ahinpoh u anchang aneh chai phat un hichun apau Jacob in achate jah a aseitai, “Nung chekit unlang neh ding gacho kit tauvin,” ati.  
\v 3 Ahin Judah in apa Jacob adonbut in, “Gamsung lamkaipa chun hatah in eigah un, na sopi pau chu nahin puilou ule kamai namulou dingu ahi,” ati.  
\v 4 Benjamin keiho toh nasol khom le kache dingu anchang kaga choh dingu ahi, ati.  
\v 5 Amavang Benjamin che ding naphal louleh keiho jong kache louhel ding'u ahitai ti geldoh in, ajeh chu gamsung lamkai pa chun aseiye, “Na sopi pau alhumpen pa chu nahin puilou ule kamai namu lou dingu ahi atisa ahi.”  
\v 6 Hichun Jacob in adonbut in, “Ibol a nang hon nei suhgenthei uhitam, hiche gam vaipopa kom'a chu sopi khat kanei nalai uve tia nahin seidoh uham?” ati.  
\v 7 Ama hon adonbut un, “Hiche gamsung lamkaipa chun eiho insung thusim hoitah in thudoh eineijun, napau dam nalai em? Sopi pasal dang nanei nahlai uvem? tin eidong un, hiche a chun keihon amapa thudoh ho chu ka donbut cheh un, chule na sopi pau hinpui yun ati ding chu keihon iti kahet thei diu ham? ,” atiuve.  
\v 8 Judah in apa Israel kom'a aseitan, “Chapang pa chu hinsol in hiche teng chule keiho kaga che diu ahi, chuti louleh ikellih diu, nang le boipu geiya ithigam diu ahi.  
\v 9 Chule keima ka tahsa tah in mopo nang kate, ahin Benjamin chu kahin nungpui louleh boina jouse keiman mo kapoh ding ahi. Chule nangma angsunga thepmona jouse keima chunga chu jenghen.  
\v 10 Amavang eiho ana geisang hih leuhen tuphat a hi nivei tobang kilhung thei ding ahitai,” ati  
\v 11 Chuphat in apau Israel chun ajah uva, “Chuti ding mong ahiya ahile hiti hin kigong uvin, gamsunga thingga phalai cheh lheng khom uvin lang, thingnai, lou themkhat le khoiju them khat toh, thil namtui toh, theichang toh, chule jonmot chang toh nadip sung uva mipa peh ding chun posuh uvin.  
\v 12 Chule dangka jong athop in pohbe un, ajeh chu nadip sung uva ana kikoi chu koitobang khat in jong anabol khel jong himai thei ahi.  
\v 13 Hijeh chun nasopi pau hi puijun lang gamsung lamkai heng'a nungche tauvin.  
\v 14 Chule Hatchungnung Pathen'in phatthei naboh maiju hen, hiche gamsung vaipo mit mua jong ngailutna mel na chan thei uva na sopi pau Simeon chule Benjamin nahin lhadoh peh thei diu ahi. Keima vang ka chate jal'a thilo pai ding ka hitai,” ati.  
\v 15 Hichun ama hon Jacob thilpeh ho chu agongtup un, chule adipsung uva sum jong athop in apohbe uvin, Benjamin toh akilhon tauve; hichun amaho Egypt gam alhung tauvin Joseph masanga ading tauvin ahi.  
\v 16 Chuin Joseph in Benjamin amaho lah a ahung chu amutan, hichun aman a insunga lhacha a pangho jah a hitin aseiye, “Amaho tohin tunia an nekhom ding kahiuvin hijeh chun insung lama ana puilut un, chule gancha ana that un, kin thupi tah kimang ding ahi.”  
\v 17 Hichun lhacha hon Joseph in asei bang chun abol'un, amaho sese chu Joseph inlam a apui tauvin ahi.  
\v 18 Joseph insung'a akipuilut jengu ahetdoh phat un asopiho chu akichauvin, “Iche masah uva hilai mun a koiham khat in idipsung uva sum ana hetlut u ahi. Aman eihon iguh u banga agon a, eimat uva, asoh uva eisem uva, chuleh isangan hou jong eilahpeh u ahitai” akitiuve.  
\v 19 Asopiho chu Joseph insung lhachapa kom'a ache un akelkot kom'a,  
\v 20 “Pu,” Keiho hi phat masa chun Egypt gam'a anneh ding chon kahung uve.  
\v 21 Ahin keiho kaki nungle uchun jan ahia kakichol pet uva kadip sungu ka hondoh ule keihon ka dipsung cheh uva kathil chohna man cheh uchu ana umsoh keiye! Yuhin hiche dangka ho chu kahin nungpoh cheh nauve.  
\v 22 Chule keihon anneh chohbe na ding dangka jong ka hin pohbe uvin, koi tobang ham khat in dangka ho kadip sung uva ana koi jong chu ka pum het pouve.” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 23 “Imacha lungboina nei hih un,” tin insung lhacha pa chun aseiye, “Na Pakai na pate Pathen chun na dipsung uva nahin koipeh u ahi, na dangka hou jong keima kom'a aum nai.” Hichun aman Simeon chu alhakang in amaho lah a ahin puidoh tan ahi.  
\v 24 Insung lhacha pa chun miho chu Joseph leng insung lama apuilut tauvin ahi. Insung lhacha pan akengu kisil ngimna ding twi apen chule sangan ho ding anneh jong apeuvin ahi.  
\v 25 Hilai mun a chu an aneh ding thu u ahetdoh phat un, sun a Joseph ahung lhun masang'in ama hon thilpeh ho chu akigon tup tauvin ahi.  
\v 26 Hichun Joseph in ahung lhun chun ama hon athilpoh u chu ahin ladoh un Joseph masanga tol'a abohkhup tauvin ahi.  
\v 27 Ama hon alemjou chun adong tan a”Napau akum atamtai nati pau chu itoh bang nam, dam jinga hinam?” tin adong'in ahi.  
\v 28 Ama hon adonbut un, “Henge” tin adonbut un “Ka pau, nasohpa chu adam in ahing nalaiye,” tin Joseph masanga abohkhup kit uvin ahi.  
\v 29 Hichun Joseph in apenkhompi asopipa Benjamin chu aven, “Ama hi ham na sopiu alhumpen pa natiu chu?” tin Joseph in adong tai. “Pathen'in na umpi jingta hen, ka chapa.” ati.  
\v 30 Hichun Joseph kinloitah in insunga kon'in apotdoh e, ajeh chu asopipa amu chun ama akitimjou tapon, ama indan sungnunga alut in agakap tan ahi.  
\v 31 Chuin amai akiphet jouvin ama ahung potdoh kit in nasatah in akitim ham ham in, “Anneh ding hin thuh tauvin,” ati.  
\v 32 Hijeh chun ama hon Joseph ding atum in, amaho ding atumin, chule ama toh nekhom ding Egypt mite ding atumin ankong asem tauve, ijeh inem itile Egypt miten Hebrew mite toh an anehkhom ngailouvu, neh khom ding chu Egypt mite dinga bohna khat hiya ahiye.  
\v 33 Joseph in asopiho chu atouna diu akoi peh cheh in, ama hon jong ajalheh jengun, amaho tahsa kum alen penna pat aneopen pa geiyin atou nau agontup peh in atousah tan ahi.  
\v 34 Amaho chan ding chu Joseph chan lah a kon'in asoh doh uvin ahi; chujongleh Benjamin chan chu amaho khat chan jat sangin chan ajat ngan atamjoi. Hitobang chun ama hon Joseph chutoh an ane khom uvin adon khom tauvin ahi.   
\c 44  
\s1 Joseph khon kiholmo  
\p
\v 1 Hichun asopiho chu chedingin aki gong tauvin, Joseph in insung lhacha ho lah a aseitan, “Amaho dip sunga chun apoh thei jat u dimset in anchang kipoh sah un, chule dangka ahin kipoh hou chu nung hetpeh cheh kit un,” ati.  
\v 2 Chutengleh keima sum eng chakhon chu alhumpen pa dip sunga achungtho pena koijun chule chang choh na dinga sum ahin kipoh toh chun koi than, hiti chun insung lhacha pan jong Joseph in asei bang chun abol tan ahi.  
\v 3 Jingkah matah in akipat doh un ache tauve, a sangan hon jong vumset in neh ding apon alampiu majon dingin asol tauve.  
\v 4 Amaho chu khopia kon chun achedoh tauvin gamlapi agei masang uvin Joseph in jong a insung thil chingpa jah a chun, “Kipat doh inlang miho nung chu del loiyin, amaho chu naphah tengleh ajah uva, 'Ipi ding pen tah a ka phat nau thilpha chu git louva na lethuh uhitam ong?' Ipi dinga keima dangka khon chu nana guh mangu ham?  
\v 5 Nangho hin ibola kapupa sum eng chakhon naguh u hitam? Aman hiche chu amanchah a thil ahunglhung ding ho hetna a aneiji ahi; nang hon thil phalou tah na boldoh'u hitalou ham!'” ati.  
\v 6 Insung lhacha pan amaho chu amattup jouvin hitin aseitai.  
\v 7 Ama hon amapa kom'a hitin asei uve, “Keiho hi nasoh kahiuvin, chule keihon hitobang chu kabol loubeh ding'u ahi! atiuve.  
\v 8 Ven keiho Canaan gam'a pat in sum chu kahin kichoi cheh nauve, chule kadip sung uva ana umho chu ka pakai pa in a konna keihon iti dana sum eng chakhon chu kaguh doh thei diu ham?.  
\v 9 Nasohte lah a koi hijongleh ala ana umtah le ama jong chu thidoh mai tahen, chule keiho jong ka pakai pa kom'a sohchang ding kahi tauve.”  
\v 10 “Hiche chu apha lheh jenge,” tin ama pan adonbut e, “Hinlah ka chakhon gupa bou chu kasoh a pang ding ahi. Adang ho vang nache thei diu ahi,” ati.  
\v 11 Ama hon gangtah in adip hou chu sangan chunga kon'in adom lhauvin ahong doh un ahi.  
\v 12 Hiphat chun insung lhacha pan alenpen apat in aneopen pa geijin adipsungu ahin kholtan ahile sum eng chakhon chu Benjamin dipsunga ahin mudoh tan ahi.  
\v 13 Hichun ama hon asangkhol'u abottel tel tauvin, apot hou chu asangan chunga aheng doh kit un, khopi lam ahin nung jot kit tauve.  
\v 14 Judah le asopi ho ahung lhun uchun Joseph chu a inna anaum nalaiye, chule amaho Joseph masanga tol ah abohkhup tauvin ahi.  
\v 15 Chuin Joseph in amaho jah a aseiyin, “Ipi ham nang hon nabol'u hi? Hitobang mihem ho hi keiman akhonung dingu kasei thei nang hon nahet lou uham?” ati.  
\v 16 Hichun Judah in aseitai, “O, ka pakai, ipi kasei dingu hitam? Keima ho iti them ka kichan diu hitam? Pathen'in nasohte chonsetna ho hi ahin hetdoh sah ahitai. Ka pakai, hijeh chun sum eng chakhon kimatdohna pa seh hilouvin keiho ka boncha uva nasoh a pang ding kahi tauve.”  
\v 17 Hinlah Joseph in adonbut in, “Chuti ponte,” Keiman chutia chu thil kabol louhel ding ahi! Ka khon gupa bou chu kasoh a pang ding, adangse sevang damsel in napa kom'a nung che tauvin,” ati.   
\s1 Benjamin alhadoh dia Judah taona  
\p
\v 18 Hichun Judah in anaijin aseitai, “Lungset tah in, ka pakai, nasoh pan thu cheng khat tou sei inge. Lungset tah in, nangma Pharaoh toh nalalna lhon kibang jongleh nei lunghan khum hih in.  
\v 19 “Ka pakai, phat masa chun nasohte ho nei dong uvin, 'Nang hon sopi nanei uvem ahilou le napa'u umnalai em?' nati.  
\v 20 Chuin keihon ka donbut un, 'Henge, ka pakaipa, kapa'u jong adam nalaiye ahin amavang ateh lheh tai katiuve, chule achapa aneopen pa chu ateh jou nungsanga ahin ahi. Asopipa jong athi tan, ama bou chu anu sunga hing doh ahin, hijeh a chu apan jong hatah a angailut ahi,' ati.  
\v 21 “Kaheng uva naseijin, kahenga hinpuiyun amapa chu keiman kamit tah inkamu nom e, nati.'  
\v 22 Ahin keihon kana donbut un, 'Ka pakai, hiche chapang chun apa adalha theipoi, ajeh chu apa thilo thei ahi,'  
\v 23 Ahin nei thumop kit un, 'Nasopi pau alhumpen pa toh nahung kilhon lou ule nang hon kamai namu kitlou dingu ahitai,' nati.  
\v 24 “Hichun nasohpa, kapau koma kakile un, nasei chu kana lhut tauve.  
\v 25 Phat chomkhat jouvin, 'Cheuvin lang chang eiga chohpeh kit un,' atin  
\v 26 ‘Ka sopiu aneopen pa toh neisol lou ule kache lou diu ahi. Aneopen pa pui louva mipa mai chu kamulou diu ahi,' tia kadonbut u ahi.  
\v 27 “Hichun kapauvin kaheng uva aseijin, 'Ka loinun chapa ni eihinpeh nang hon naheuve,  
\v 28 amani lah a khat pan eidalha tan ahung kinungle tapoi; lung opkaina loubeh a gamsa hon atal adah a ajam'u ahi. Ama kanung mukit louhel ahitai.  
\v 29 Tua asopipa kakoma kon a napuidoh uva, boina ahinto khah le, lunghem pum a hiche samkang pa hi alhankhuh nalhut pai diu ahitai,’ ati.  
\v 30 Tun, ka pakai, keima kapa henga hiche chapang jao louvin kinungle thei pong kate. Kapa'u hinkho hi hiche chapang pa hinkho a hi kingam ahiye.  
\v 31 Kapan hiche chapang hi amulou le thilo tei ding ahi. Nasohte ho hin kapa'u samkan jouva thina kato sah kit dingu ahitai.  
\v 32 Amonga jong na sohpa hi kapa henga hiche chapang khel'a hung kipe doh jenga hitia hi, keiman ama hi naheng kahin nunglhut kit louva ahile nahenga hinkho lhumkeijin themmo chang jeng ing kate, kati ahi.  
\v 33 Hijeh chun kapu, lungset tah in ahithei ding leh hiche chapang khel in keima hi nangma soh din um tang kate, chule ahithei ding leh hiche chapang hi a uteho toh kinungle tauhen.  
\v 34 Keima hiche chapang pa beiya hi iti kapa kom'a kaki nungle kit ding ham? Kapan gim genthei athoh ding chu iti kavet jou ding ham,! ati.   
\c 45  
\s1 Joseph laina tah a akiphon  
\p
\v 1 Hichun Joseph anatoh khompi ho masanga ama le ama akitim jou tapon hichun awthong jejun akap tan, mijouse chukom'a kon chun asoldoh in ama asopi ho lah a akiphong doh tan ahi. \x + \xo 45:1 \xt Act 7:13\x*  
\v 2 Chuin ama hatah in akaptan ahile Egypt miten jong aja uvin, chule hiche thu kisei chu apet pet in Pharaoh in ajatan ahi.  
\v 3 Joseph in asopi ho kom'a aseiyin “Keima Joseph chu kahi! Kapa chu dam nalai hinam?” ati. Hinlah asopiho imacha seithei louvin aum gam tauve! Amasang uva ding Joseph ahi ahin hetdoh u chun alung kidang lheh jengun ahi.  
\v 4 “Lungset tah in, hung kikhin naijun,” ati. Hichun ama hon ahin nailut tauve. Chuin aseikit in “Keima hi Joseph, nasopi pau, Egypt gam'a najoh pau chu kahi.  
\v 5 Ahin tija hih un, chule keima hilaimun a neijohdoh jeh uva nangho le nang hon kilunghan jong bol hih un. Ajeh chu nangho hinkho huhdohna dinga Pathen'in hilai mun a hi eina sol masah joh ahi bouve.  
\v 6 Hiche gamsung a hi kumni bou kel hah hung kipan bep ahin, kum nga sung jen avat nalaiye.  
\v 7 Pathen'in nangho huhdoh dinga eina sol masat joh ahi, nangho le na insung mite thilouva lei chunga achi amanna louding ahi.  
\v 8 Hiche chu nang hon nabol'u ahipon, Pathen'in eina masol joh ahi! Chule Pathen'in Pharaoh hilthei ding ama lenggam Egypt gamsunga semanga pang kahitai.  
\v 9 “Tun gangtah in cheuvin lang kapa gaseipeh loiyun lang 'Nachapa Joseph in aseiye: Pathen'in Egypt gamsunga vaipo lenpenin eipansah tai. Hijeh chun kakom'a hungsuh loiyin! \x + \xo 45:9 \xt Act 7:14\x*  
\v 10 Keima toh kinai cha a nachate le natute jouse, na gancha ho le nanei nagou jouseu pumma Goshen gamsunga na chen theiyu ahi.  
\v 11 Hikom'a chu keiman kavetsui diu ahi, ijeh inem itile kellhahna ding hi kum nga jen aum nalaiye. Achuti louva ahile na insung pumpiu leh na gancha ho jouseuvin an angol diu ahi.'”  
\v 12 Hichun Joseph in athusei ajom in “Veuvin! Nang hon neimu chen uva sopi Benjamin in jong nei hetchenna din, keima Joseph chu kahi! ati.  
\v 13 Cheuvin lang Egypt gamsunga jabolna changa kaum hi kapa Jacob chu gaseipeh loiyun, thil namu jouseu seipeh un, chule aganna thei chanin hilanga hin puiyun,” ati.  
\v 14 Hichun Joseph in Benjamin chu angong koiyin akaptai, chuti ma chun Benjamin'in jong akoiyin akaptai.  
\v 15 Joseph in asopi ho chengse chu kappumin achop sohkeijin ahi, chujou chun ama hon chamlhat tah in akihoulimpi pan tauve.  
\v 16 “Joseph sopi ho ahunglhung tauve!” tithu chu Pharaoh leng inpi a gangtah in alhung tan, ama hon jong akipapi lheh un ahi.  
\v 17 Hichun Pharaoh in Joseph kom'a aseiyin, “Na sopi ho chu seipeh in gangtah in na sangan chung uva napot hou chu hengdoh unlang gangtah in Canaan gama kinungle loiyun,” ati.  
\v 18 Chule napa ahin adang insung mite jouse keima kom'a hin lepui loiyun Egypt gamsunga aphapen kapeh diu nahi; chule agam gasoh ahoipen naneh diu ahi,” ati.  
\v 19 Hichun Pharaoh in Joseph kom'a asei in, “Na sopiho chu seipeh tan ama hon kangtalai chu kipuiyu henlang chapang ho le a jite ho'u chule napa'u chu ka henga hin puiyun.  
\v 20 Nang hon nathil nei hou chu lunggimpi da tauvin, ajeh chu Egypt gamsunga ahoipen aphapen jouse nangho a ahitai,” ati.  
\v 21 Hichun Jacob chaten amaho thu kiseipeh bang chun abol'un, Pharaoh in aphatsah le athupeh dungjuijin Joseph in jong kangtalai ho chu agontup peh in, chule lamkah a neh le chah ding jong agontup peh in ahi.  
\v 22 Chule aman asopiho chu vonthah apecheh in, Benjamin vang chu golvah von nga chule dangka sum eng jathum toh apen ahi.  
\v 23 Joseph in apa din sangan chal som a Egypt gamsunga atui aphapen ho jouse apohsah in chule sangan anu som chu ahung kitol tengu leh lamkah a akihinso theina diuvin changlhah dimset apohsah un ahi.  
\v 24 Hichun Joseph in asopiho chu alhadoh in, amaho akipatdoh ding kon un, Joseph in amaho chu availhah in “Lampi najot lai un nangho kinapa hih un!” ati.  
\v 25 Chuin ama hon Egypt chu adalhauvin Canaan gam lang apa Jacob kom'a akile kit tauve.  
\v 26 Ama hon apau chu aseipeh un hitin atiuve, “Joseph ahing nalaiye!” Chule Egypt gam pumpia vaipoa khu ama hijah ahi!” atiuve. Ahinah vang chun Jacob in la amaho atahsan loujeh in alungthim akiloh dehpoi.  
\v 27 Ahin ama hon Joseph thusei chu avel vel in apau chu aseipeh un, chule Joseph in apa pohna dinga kangtalai chu agahven amu phat in apau Jacob lhagao chu akidodoh kittai.  
\v 28 Hichun Jacob in aphongdoh tai, “Ka chapa Joseph ahing nalaiye! Atah hinte! Ka hinkho bei masang'a kaga kimupi ding ahi,” ati.   
\c 46  
\s1 Jacob Leh A Insung Mite Egypt Jon'a Akitol U  
\p
\v 1 Hichun Jacob chu Egypt gam jon din akipatdoh tan anei agou jouse jong apon Beersheba ahung lhungin hiche jan chun apa Isaac Pathen min'in maicham asemin ahi.  
\v 2 Hiche jan chun Pathen'in gaova akihoulim pin, “Jacob! Jacob!” tin akouve. Aman jong, “Hikom'a kaume,” ati.  
\v 3 “Keima napu napate Pathen kahi,” tin ahoulim pin, nangma Egypt gam langa chesuh ding kicha hihbeh in ajeh chu Keiman nangma hiche mun'a chu nam lentah kaso ding nahi.  
\v 4 Keiman Egypt lama na chesuh teng ka kilhonpi ding nahi, chule keiman nangma ka hin nungpui kit ding Egypt a nathi ding ahi, ahin namit nasinna mun a chu Joseph in naumpi ding ahi, ati.  
\v 5 Hichun Jacob in Beersheba adalhan chule achate sen Egypt lama apui tauvin, kangtalai chunga ama ahin chapang naosen ho jong chule ajite ho chengse jong Pharaoh in ima ma agontup peh bangin apuisuh tauvin ahi.  
\v 6 Ama hon anei agou jouse chule agancha hou jouse Canaan gamsunga ana kilamdoh ho jouse jong apo tauvin ahi. \x + \xo 46:6 \xt Act 7:15\x*  
\v 7 Achate hou sese chule atute ho jouse jong chule achanute ho jong chule achanute chate jouse jong ama chilhah namkim jouse toh Egypt ahin jon tauve.  
\v 8 Tua min hung kipe ho chengse hi Israel chilhah Jacob chate Egypt gam'a ana cheho chu ahiuve: Reuben chu Jacob chate lah a atahpen ahi.  
\v 9 Reuben chapa te chu Hanoch, Pallu, Hezron chule Carmi ahiuve.  
\v 10 Simeon chapa te chu Jemuel, Jamin, Ohad, Jakin, Johar chule Shaul ahiuve. (Shual nu chu Canaan numei ahi).  
\v 11 Levi chapa te chu Gershon, Kohath chule Merari ahiuve.  
\v 12 Judah chapa te chu Er, Onan, Shelah, Perez chule Zerah ahiuve. (Er le Onan chu Canaan gam'a ana thi lhon tajongleh) Perez chapa te chu Hezron le Hamul ahi lhon'e.  
\v 13 Issachar chapa te chu Tola, Puah, Jashub chule Simron ahiuve.  
\v 14 Zebulun chapa te chu Sered, Elon chule Zahleel ahiuve.  
\v 15 Hiche ho hi Paddan-aram gam'a achen lai uva peng Jacob le Leah chapa te ahiuve, chule amaho tilouva apenbe achanu, Dinah chu ahi; Jacob chate jouse numei le pasal abon'a Leah a konna hung peng doh jouse chu agoma somthum le thum ahiuve.  
\v 16 Gad chapa te chu Zephon, Haggi, Shuni, Ezbon, Eri, Arodi chule Areli ahiuve.  
\v 17 Asher chapa te chu Imnah, Ishvah, Ishvi chule Beriah ahiuve. Serah chu asopinu u ahi. Beriah chapa te chu Heber chule Malkiel ahi lhon e.  
\v 18 Hiche pasal ho sese hi Zilpah chate ho Leah sohnu akon a Jacob chilhah ho ahiuvin agom a som le gup ahiuve.  
\v 19 Jacob chilhah Rachel in ahinpeh chu Joseph le Benjamin ahi.  
\v 20 Joseph chate ni Egypt gam'a peng chu Mannaseh le Ephhraim ahi lhone, amani nu min chu Asenath Potiphera chanu On gam'a thempu pa chanu ahiye. \x + \xo 46:20 \xt Semtilbu 41:50-52\x*  
\v 21 Benjamin chapa te chu Bela, Beker, Ashbel, Gera, Namaan, Ehi, Rosh, Muppim, Huppim chule Ard ahiuve.  
\v 22 Hiche ho hi Rachel le Jacob a konna hung peng achapa te ahiuvin abonchauvin som le li ahiuve.  
\v 23 Dan chapa chu Hushim ahi.  
\v 24 Napthali chapa te chu Jahzeel, Guni, Jezer chule Shillem ahiuve.  
\v 25 Hiche pasal ho hi Bilhah in ahin peh Laban in Rachel soh dinga apeh nu akon ahiuve. Jacob in Bilhah toh ahin chu abon'un pasal sagi ahiuve.  
\v 26 Jacob chilhah te Egypt ma ama toh cheho chu achate jiho sim louvin mihem somgup le gup ahiuve.  
\v 27 Hiche tilou chun Jacob in Egypt ma cha pasal ni aneiben hijeh chun abonchauvin Jacob insung mite chu Egypt gam'a anachen laiyu chun mihem somsagi alhingset un ahi. \x + \xo 46:27 \xt Act 7:14\x*  
\v 28 Amaho alamjot nauva alhunna diu ahung naithim tan, Jacob in Judah chu Goshen jotna lamhil hedin asol in, phat chomkhat jouvin amaho alhung tauve.  
\v 29 Joseph a sakol kangtalai chunga atou doh in apa Jacob chu Goshen lama aga kimuto pitai. Hichun Joseph in apa Jacob amu phat chun phat sottah a ngongkoi in akap tai.  
\v 30 Hichun Jacob in ahin hou in, Joseph kom'a aseitai, “Keima tua hi thi thei kahi tai, ajeh chu nangma nana hing nalai in tuhin namai kamu tai,” ati.  
\v 31 Hichun Joseph in asopite le apa insung mite jah a “Keima chetou ing ting Pharaoh jah a thu galhut ing ka ting ajah a, ‘Canaan gam'a cheng ka sopite le kapa insung mite ka heng ahunglhung tauve.  
\v 32 Amaho hi kelngoi ching mi ahiuvin, chule ama hon anei thil jouse le agancha hou jong ahin kipui uve gati ing'e.'”  
\v 33 “Ahin Pharaoh in ipi na natoh u nahin doh teng ule,  
\v 34 na donbut dingu, “Keiho, nasohte hi, kapu kapa teu bangin kelngoi ching kahiuve,' nati diu ahi. Chuteng Pharaoh in Goshen lhanglam a nahin chen sah diu ahi; ajeh chu Egypt miten kelngoi chingho atheinom pouve,” ati.   
\c 47  
\s1 Goshen mun alo diuva kipe  
\p
\v 1 Hiti chun Joseph achelut in Pharaoh henga thu agalhut in, ‘‘Kapa le ka sopite Canaan gam'a kon'in ahunglhung tauve. Amaho akelngoi ho jouse le aganchau toh chule anei jouseu toh kilhonin tuhin Goshen gamsunga aum uve,” agati.  
\v 2 Chuin Joseph in asopi ho lah a mi nga alhengdoh in Pharaoh henga phondohna aneiyin ahi.  
\v 3 Chuin Pharaoh in amaho chu thu adong tan, “Nangho ipi natong nahiu ham?” ati. Ama hon adonbut un, “Keiho, nasohte hi, kapu kapate khanga patna kelngoi ching ka hiuve,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 4 Ama ho Pharaoh henga ahoulim un, “Hiche Egypt gam'a hi phat chomkhat cheng dinga hung kahiuve, ajeh chu Canaan gam'a hamdong jong aum tapoi. Khulam'ah kellhah jong akhohse lheh jenge. Hijeh chun lungset tah in, Goshen lhaanga nei chensah un,” atiuve.  
\v 5 Hichun Pharaoh in Joseph jah a aseiye, “Napa ahin, na sopiho nangma kom'a din ahung tauve.  
\v 6 Egypt gamsung pumpia amaho achen theina diuvin nangman lhenpeh tan, chule Egypt gamsung gam phalai pen chu pen. Goshen lhaanga chun cheng tauhen. Chule amaho lah a miching thepna nei aum leh keima gancha ho vetup din nei koipeh in,” ati.  
\v 7 Hichun Joseph in apa Jacob chu Pharaoh kom'a ahin puijin akihetto sah e. Jacob in Pharaoh phatthei aboh tan ahi.  
\v 8 Chuin Pharaoh in “Kum ijat nahi hitam tin Jacob chu adongin ahi.”  
\v 9 Jacob in adonbut in, “Keima kum jakhat le somthum hung kholjin kahitai. Amavang ka hinkho hi kapu kapate sang’in achomjo nalaiye,” ati.  
\v 10 Hichun Jacob in Pharaoh adalhah masang'in avelin phatthei abohkit in ahi.  
\v 11 Joseph in apa Jacob ahin asopiho abonchauvin Egypt gamsunga achensah tan, chule nei le gou jong apen gam jong apha pen Rameses lhaang chu Pharaoh thupeh dungjuijin ape tan ahi.  
\v 12 Chuin Joseph in apa ahin, asopite ahin abonchauvin ama hon angaichat dungjuijin ape sohkeijin, chule chapang neocha cha ho gei dingin jong ape jeng tan ahi.   
\s1 Joseph in kellhah sung'a Egyp gamvai ahom dan  
\p
\v 13 Phat chomkhat jouvin neh le chah ahah lheh jeng tan, anchang kikoi jouse jong anechai gam tauve, Egypt gamsung le Canaan gamsunga mipite jouse neh le chah hahsat jeh in mipi thi dingin aum gamtan ahi.  
\v 14 Joseph in sum le pai akhol doh jouse chu Egypt gamsung ahin Canaan gamsunga anchang achoh nau sum jouse chu Pharaoh gou kholna mun'a ahin polut tai.  
\v 15 Mipite jouse Egypt akon ahin, Canaan a kon ahin, sum le pai jouse alhahsam phat in Joseph kom'a ahung taovun ahi. Amaho akap un “Sum le pai Sana le dangka ho jouse akichai tai! an neh ding neipeh lou ule nangma mitmua thi ding kahi tauve,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 16 Hichun Joseph in adonbut in, “Na dangka hou abeitah le na gancha hou keima henga hinkaijun, keiman nangho gancha hotoh kitoh ding anneh ding kalheh peh ding nahiuve,” ati.  
\v 17 Hichun ama hon anneh toh lheh dingin agancha hou jouse Joseph kom'a ahin kaiyun, chule sakol hon ho ahin, kelngoi hon ho leh keltah hon ho ahin chule abong hon ho le sangan ho jouse jong Joseph kom'a alheh cheh un hichun aman kum khat anneh ding apehbe kit tan ahi.  
\v 18 Amavang hiche kum chu akichai kit tan, kumthah ahunglhung kittan hichun ama hon a seikit tauve, “Ka pakai, nangma a kon'in imacha ka imthei tapouve. Ajeh chu ka dangka hou se la akichai tan, ka gancha hou ka bong hou la abeitan, tu hin keima hon imacha peh ding kanei tapouve, tua hi ka tahsau le ka leiset ubou aumtai.  
\v 19 Nangma mitmua iti ka moh thi thei diu ham? Keima ho tahsa ahin ka leiset u ahin anneh ding toh lheh jeng tauvinge; ka leiset u ahin ka tahsau ahin Pharaoh soh in um tauving kate, hijeh chun kathi lou na diuvin anchang neh ding neipe uvin, chule gam leiset chu mohseh a umlou a asetna lou dingin,” atiuve.  
\v 20 Hichun Joseph in Egypt gamsunga leiset jouse Pharaoh din Egypt mite kom'a kon'in achodoh soh tan ahi.  
\v 21 Mipi ho vang chu ahile khopi a kon'in gam ong thinglhang lama asol in Egypt gamsunga mun khat a pat in mun chom a asol in ahi.  
\v 22 Gam leiset Joseph in ana choh lou chu thempu ho gam bou chu ahi. Amaho chun Pharaoh a konna anneh akisan'u ahijeh in agam leiset u jong ajoh u ngailou ahi.  
\v 23 Hichun Joseph in mipite lah a ahoulim in, “Veuvin tunia keiman nangho chule nagam leiset u Pharaoh adia ka chohdoh ahitai. Keiman nangho muchi kapeh ding nang hon na phailei uva chang natu theiyu ahitai.  
\v 24 Chule nangman chang na at teng hop nga lah a hop khat Pharaoh adia napeh ding hopli chu nangma muchi adia nakikoi diu, chule nangma ho insung mite anneh a pang ding aneocha cha ho geija kapeh nahiuve.  
\v 25 Ama hon aphong doh un, “Keima ho hinkho hi nangman nei huhdoh peh u ahi! Chule nangma phatsah bang hi jeng hen; chule lungset tah in ka pakai pa Pharaoh soh in pangmai jeng tauvinge,” atiuvin ahi.”  
\v 26 Chule Joseph in dan asemin Egypt gam'a tuni geihin akimang nalaiye, hichu ahile Pharaoh in hopnga lah a hopkhat ane jing nalaiyin, thempu ho a tilou chu gam leiset abon a Pharaoh a ahitai.   
\s1 Jacob lhahna thusei  
\p
\v 27 Hichun phat chomkhat jouvin, Israel mipite chun Egypt gamsunga Goshen lhanglam chu alodim tauvin, hichea pat chun ama hon nei le gou akilamdoh un, abol jouse'u jong nasatah in apung tul tul jengun ahi.  
\v 28 Hichun Jacob chu Egypt ahung lhun jouvin kumsom le kum sagi ahinbe in Jacob hin nikho abon bon'a kum jakhat le kum som li le kum sagi alhingin ahi.  
\v 29 Jacob chu athi tei ding nikho ahung nai tul tul phat in aman jong achapa Joseph akouvin ajah a “Namit mua nangma kalung lhaisah jouva ahile gunchu tah le kitah tah a nei bolna dingin kataipi gui noi tuh inlang Egypt gam'a neihin vui louhelna dingin kitep in; \x + \xo 47:29 \xt Semtilbu 49:29-32; 50:6\x*  
\v 30 Keima ka hinkho ahung beiteng lungset tah in ka tahsa hi Egypt a kon'in eipodoh inlang kapu kapate kivuina mun'a neivui in,” Hichun Joseph jong akihahsel in, “Keiman nangma seibang bangin hinbol peh nang kate,” ati.  
\v 31 Hichun Jacob in avel in aseikit in, “Nangma kitem in,” ati, hichun Joseph akihahsel tan, chuin Jacob chu alupna a abohkhup tan ahi.   
\c 48  
\s1 Jacob in Ephraim le Manasseh phatthei abohna  
\p
\v 1 Thusoh hichengse kichai nung phat chomkhat jouvin, “Napa chu alhasuh lheh jeng tai” tia Joseph ahung seipeh uleh; Joseph chu apa kimupi din achen acha teni Ephraim le Manasseh jong akipuiyin ahi.  
\v 2 Chuin Jacob chu aseipeh un, “Ven nachapa Joseph chun nangma kom ahinjon e.” Hichun Jacob atha ahung kido in alupna apat in athou doh in atoutai.  
\v 3 Hichun Jacob in Joseph chu ahoulimpin, “Pathen hatchungnung in Luz mun'a Canaan gam'a eiki mupi chun phatthei eiboh e. \x + \xo 48:3 \xt Semtilbu 28:13,14\x*  
\v 4 Aman kakom'a ana seiyin, 'Ven nangma ka chiphat sah ding chule kapun sah ding chujongle nangma chilhah tamtah a kasem doh ding nahi. Na chilhah te chu Canaan gam hi amaho nei le gou dia atonsot a kapeh ding ahitai,' tin eihoulimpi e.  
\v 5 “Keima hung lhun masanga Egypt gamsunga nacha teni Manasseh le Ephraim hi keima a hi ding ahi. Reuben le Simeon keija ahi tobanga hi amani jong hi keiya ahi lhon'e.  
\v 6 Hinlah chapang naosen tu khonunga peng ho vang nangma a hi ding ahitai, chule amaho se chu asopi ho goulo min lah a kisimtha ding ahi lhon e.  
\v 7 Phatkhat lai chun, keima Paddan-aram lama kahung kinunglen Rachel chu Canaan gam'a athi tai. Keima ho Ephrath toh kikah gamla thim lheh nalaiyin lungkham tah in Rachel chu Ephrath (chehi Bethleham ahi) lampi pam a kahin vuitai.” \x + \xo 48:7 \xt Semtilbu 35:16-19\x*  
\v 8 Hichun Jacob in chapang teni chu aven “Hiche teni hi nangma chapa ham?” ati.  
\v 9 Joseph in adonbut in “Heng'e,” “Hiche chapa teni hi Pathen'in Egypt gamsunga eipeh ahi.” Jacob in adonbut in “Amani chu keima kom'a hinpui nai uvin, phatthei kaboh ding ahi.”  
\v 10 Jacob chu akum atam phat in amittha jong alhasam lheh jeng tai. Ajeh chu aha muchen jou tapoi; hichun Joseph in acha teni chu apa kom Jacob nai deuvin ahin puijin chuin apan amani chu achop in akoiyin ahi.  
\v 11 Chuin Jacob in Joseph kom'a aseiyin, “Keiman nangma maichang mukit dinga hi kana kiginchat lou ahitai, ahin tuhin Pathen'in nacha teni jong eimusah tai!” ati.  
\v 12 Hichun Joseph in acha teni chu apa khup a kon'in akhindoh in amai in tollang angan abohkhup tai.  
\v 13 Chuin acha teni chu Jacob masanga agoltoh e. Akhut jet lamin Ephraim chu Jacob khut veilama chun akailut peh in, chule aveilam in Manasseh chu Jacob jetlam a akailut e.  
\v 14 Ahin Jacob in akhut apenton aluchung lhon'a akhut angamtai. Aneojo hijongleh akhut jetlam chu Ephraim achunga angam tan, chule apeng masa ahivangin Israel in akhut veilam chu Manasseh chunga angam tan ahi.  
\v 15 Hichun Joseph phatthei aboh in hitin aseiye, “Ka Pathen kapu Abraham kapa Isaac masanga lamkai jingpa ka Pakai kelngoi chinga hung pang jing ka hinkho pumpi tuni geiya eipui hoipa;  
\v 16 Thil gilou tinchenga konna eina lhatdoh jing vantil chun chapang teni hi phatthei hin boh hen; chule amani chunga hin keima min le kapu Abraham min, kapa Isaac min hung kihedoh jing jeng hen; chujongleh amani hi leiset vaipi jalah a mipi atama tam in hung pung lhon hen,” ati.  
\v 17 Ahin Joseph chu apan akhut jetlam Ephraim chunga angap jeh chun alung lhaimo lheh jenge. Ahin Joseph in apa khut chu atuh in ajetlam chu Manasseh chunga angap sah in, akhut veilam chu Ephraim chunga angap sah tai.  
\v 18 “Ahipoi, Hepa,” ati. “Amapa joh hi apeng masapa ahi. Na jetlam chu Manasseh chunga hin ngamin.”  
\v 19 Amavang apa Israel anompoi, “Ka henai, ka chapa; kanai.” tin adonbut e. Manasseh jong nam len hung hintin, ahin anaopa ama sanga hung lenjo ding ahi. Chule ama chilhah ho chu nam tamtah hung hi diu ahi.”  
\v 20 Hichun Jacob in chapang teni chu hiche phattheina toh aboh in: “Israel miten phatthei akiboh teng ule namin hi apat diu ahi. 'Pathen'in nangma hi Ephraim le Manasseh bangin na lolhinsah hen,'” ati diu ahi. Hiti chun, Jacob in Ephraim chu Manasseh masanga akoi tan ahi. \x + \xo 48:20 \xt Heb 11:21\x*  
\v 21 Hichun Jacob in Joseph kom'a aseitai, “Ven keima kathina ding anaitai, ahin Pathen'in naumpi intin, chule Canaan a napu napate gam'a nanung puikit ding ahi.  
\v 22 Chule hiche kal a chu nasopi te ho kapeh sanga lenjo ka chemjam le ka thalpi a Amor mite gam kalah chu kapeh nahi,” ati.   
\c 49  
\s1 Achate kom'a Jacob lhahna thusei  
\p
\v 1 Hichun Jacob in achate jouse akou khom in hitin aseiye, “Keima naivel a hung kikhom un, chule keiman nangho thuguh ka seipeh ding nahiuve, khonunga ipi hunglhung ding ham na seipeh uvinge,” ati.  
\v 2 “Hungun chule ngaijun, nangho Jacob chate ho; napau, Israel thusei ngaiyun.”  
\v 3 “Reuben, kachapa atahpen, ka thahatpen laiya kanei, ka khanghoi laitah a kahin chule nangma amasa penna jana chang chule nangma amasapen a thahat chang nahi.  
\v 4 Nangma twi kimang banga phatna najou tapoi, ajeh chu napa lupna jalkhun nasuboh tai.”  
\v 5 “Simeon le Levi sopi khat ahi lhon'e, chule amanchah lhon ho chu galsatna ding bou ahi.  
\v 6 Keima lhagao vang amani komah jaoda maihen, chule amani tohgon jong jahda ding kanom e; ahin amani alunghan teng le mihem hinkho ahin suhbei lhon ding ahi, chule amanin golseh a bongchal akipalsah lhon ding ahi.  
\v 7 Jacob chate ho lah a kahop khen ding keiman Israel sunga amani chu kathe cheh ding ahitai, alunghan nalhon sapset ahitai, ajeh chu tijat umtah, alunghan nalhon jong phalou tah ahi.”  
\v 8 “Judah nangma nasopi hon nathang-at uve. Nangman na melma te angonga na matchah ding, nasopi ho jouse nangma masanga kun cheh diu ahi.  
\v 9 Ka chapa Judah hi keipi bahkai nou in an anneh jou pet ahi. keipi bahkai banga kitaule a lumji tobang; keipi tobang chu kon athodoh jou ding ham? \x + \xo 49:9 \xt Minbu 24:9; Rev 5:5\x*  
\v 10 Leng tenggol chu Judah a konin kikhen kang pontin, vaihompa tenggol jong akhanggui mite chutoh kikhen ponte, aneipa akondohna mun ahung masangse a, nam jousen ajabol ding pa chu.  
\v 11 Aman a sangan chu lengpi thei phunga ahen in, chule sangan nou chu abah hoipen lengpi bah a ahen in, chule apon ho chu lengpitwiya asop in chule ama von ho chu lengpitwiya asop ngim e.  
\v 12 Amit teni chu lengpitwi sangin athimjon, chule ahatu jouse chu bongnoi sangin akangjon ahi.”  
\v 13 “Zebulun chu twikhanglen panga cheng ding chule ama kom'a chu kongho kinga ding; Sidon geiya agamgi akeh ding ahi.”  
\v 14 “Issachar vang chu ahile sangan hattah ahi, ama chu hahsatna molni kikah a um ahi.  
\v 15 Aman ngahmun khat amudoh in chule agam nop dan jong chu dei chat um ahi; hijeh chun aman thilpo dingin alengkou adon, hunam in soh dingin akipelut tai.”  
\v 16 “ Dan in Israel phungdang ho bang a amite chunga vai ahin hop ding ahi.  
\v 17 Dan chu lampi lhanglang a gul tobang ahi, chule lampi a gulse kijam tobang ahin, ama chun sakol keng achuh le achunga toupa akinung le lhah tai.  
\v 18 Keiman nangma katahsan e huhhingna kachan theina din, O Pakai!”  
\v 19 “Gad chunga mipi hon lam ajot diu ahin achaina aman amaho chunga lam ahin jot ding ahi.”  
\v 20 “Asher chu anneh neng ding chule lengho nehthei ding tah akhut a soh ding ahi.”  
\v 21 “Napthali chu sajuhpi nou hoitah neiya kichamlhat sah ahi.”  
\v 22 “Joseph hi lengpi thingga phatah tobang ahi, chule twinah phung thingbah ga phatah ahi, abah hon jong bang akhokhel gamtai.  
\v 23 Thalpi kapthem hon avetda lheh un, amapa akap un chule abol genthei lheh jeng uve.  
\v 24 Ahin amapa thalpi alhou lheh in, chule Kelngoi chingpa, Israel te Songpi, Jacob Thahatna chun aban thahat sah in ahi.  
\v 25 Napa panpi Pathen'in van chunga phattheina tincheng, chule leithol noilanga twi dim bang phattheina, chule noitwi le naobu a phattheina jouse naboh tahen.  
\v 26 Napan phatthei nabohna ho chu masanga napute phattheina ho sangin phatthei joh hi maihen, chule molsang pen ho sangin sangpen maihen. Hiche phattheina ho jouse hi Joseph chunga um jing tahen, ajeh chu ama hi asopite lah a dinga leng cha ahi.”  
\v 27 “Benjamin chu Sial tobang ahi, ajeh chu jingkah lam le amelmate chu aval lhum jin nilhah lam teng alotup ho chu ahomkhen jenge.”  
\v 28 Amaho se hi Israel phungsom le phungni ahiuve, hiche thucheng ho hi apan aseipeh u ahi; amaho jouse chu phatthei aboh in chule kilhahna thucheng aneiyin, chule amaho jouse khat khat in ama hina cheh in phatthei aboh cheh in ahi.   
\s1 Jacob thi le akivui  
\p
\v 29 Hichun Jacob in ahilchah un, “Kapu kapate kom jon a keima thivah ding kahitai. Hit mi Ephron louva kapa le kapu kivuina songko a chun neihin vuikhom’un.  
\v 30 Hiche songlhan chu Machpelah loumun Mamre nisolam Canaan gamsunga um ahin, Abraham'in lhan mun a man jing dinga Hit mipa Ephron henga ana choh ahi. \x + \xo 49:30 \xt Semtilbu 23:3-20\x*  
\v 31 Hiche mun'a chun Abraham le Sarah akivui lhonin, chule hiche mun chu Isaac le aloinu Rabekah jong akivuijin chule keiman jong hilai mun a chu Leah kana vui ahi. \x + \xo 49:31 \xt Semtilbu 25:9,10; \xt Semtilbu 35:29\x*  
\v 32 Hiche gam chu phaicham kotong lam chu kapu Abraham'in Hit mipa kom'a ana choh doh ahi.  
\v 33 Hichun Jacob chu achapa te athulhah chaijin jalkhun chunga akeng teni asep doh in ama ahaitan tai, chuin ama amite to akigom tan tai. \x + \xo 49:33 \xt Act 7:15\x*   
\c 50  
\s1 Joseph in apa pul adou  
\p
\v 1 Joseph chu apa senan akineiyin kap pumin akoijin achop in ahi..  
\v 2 Chuin Joseph in asohte louthem ho chu apa longdamsa tom din thu apen, hichun louthem ho chun atom tauvin ahi.  
\v 3 Hitobanga longdamsa kitom chu nisom li tobang lut jia ahi; chule Egypt mihon ama chu ni somsagi alunghem piuvin ahi.  
\v 4 Hichun lunghem na nikho ho chu ahung kichai tan, Joseph in lengpa Pharaoh insung mite chu ahoulimpin, “ Lungset tah in kadei khat Pharaoh kom’a ka khelin nei seipeh uvin.  
\v 5 Kapa in adamlai in eina kihahsel sah e. “Aman kajah a, “Ngaijin, keima ka hinkho beivah ding ahitai. Ka tahsa hi Canaan gam'a hin nung lhut teiyin lang, chule keima kivuina dia lhan ka kisemna mun'a neivui tei ding ahi.' Hijeh chun lungset tah in neisol inlang kapa ga kivui inge. Kavui chai tengleh kinomsot louva kahung kile pai ding ahitai.” \x + \xo 50:5 \xt Semtilbu 47:29-31\x*  
\v 6 Joseph ngehna chu Pharaoh in aphasah tai. “Napan nangma nakitep sahna bangin chen lang gavui tan,” ati.  
\v 7 Hichun Joseph chu apa vui din achetan ahile Pharaoh in alhonpi dingin Egypt gamsunga alen alal ho ahin asohte ahin, asemang pachong ho jouse toh asol than ahi.  
\v 8 Joseph in a insung mite ahin jouse apuijin ahi. Ahin chapang neocha ho leh gancha ho vang Goshen a adalhauvin ahi.  
\v 9 Sakol kangtalai tampia mihonpi chun Joseph alhonpi uvin ahi.  
\v 10 Jordan vadung koma Atad changphol ahunglhun un Joseph pa puldouna kin lentah nisagi sungin amangun ahi.  
\v 11 Agamsung mi, Canaan miten Atad changvohna mun'a amaho lunghem tah a aumu chu amu uvin, hiche mun chu (Jordan toh kinai ahi) Abel- Mizraim, tin akhel uvin, hichu “Egypt mite dia nasatah a puldouna mun” tin asei uve.  
\v 12 Hichun Jacob chaten apau thupeh bang bangin abolpeh un ahi.  
\v 13 Ama hon apa longdamsa chu Canaan gam'a apolut tauvin Mamre kom'a Macphelah loumun a Abraham'in hiche mun chu Hit mipa Ephron kom'a atonsot a kivui theina dinga ana choh na mun achun avui tauvin ahi. \x + \xo 50:13 \xt Act 7:16\x*  
\v 14 Jacob avuijou chun Joseph ahin asopi te ho jouse chule midang akilhonpi jouse Egypt gam'a ahung kinungle tauvin ahi.   
\s1 Joseph in avel'a asopite alhamkonna  
\p
\v 15 Ahin tua hi amaho apao umtah lou jeh chun Joseph sopi ho chu hatah in ahung tija tauvin, ama hon aseiyun, “Joseph chun alunghanna ho eihon ina bolset nau jouse chu ahin phulah ding ahi,” atiuve.  
\v 16 Hijeh chun ama hon hiche thucheng ho hi Joseph athot tauve: napan athi masang chun hitin eina thulhah uvin  
\v 17 Na heng'a kasei diuvin: na sopi ten na chunga thil gilou abol uva suhkhel anei nau chu ngaidam in.” Hijeh chun, keiho napa Pathen sohten, ka suhkhel nau chu nei ngaidamun tia katao u ahi.” Hiche thu thot amu chun Joseph akap tai.  
\v 18 Hichun asopi ho ahungun Joseph masanga akun tauvin ahi. “Ven, keiho hi nasohte kahiuve.” atiuve.  
\v 19 Ahin Joseph in, “Nangho tija hih un, keima Pathen beh kahia nangho kagimbol ding ham?” tin adonbut e.  
\v 20 Nang hon kachunga thil phalou nana gong un ahin Pathen'in aphalam tah in ahin gong e. Hiche panmun chan eilhut a tua ka mite mihem tamtah hinkho huhhing'a um thei ahi.  
\v 21 Ahipoi, nangho kicha hih un. Keiman nangho nahiuvin nachate hou ahin kavetkol jom jing diu ahi,” ati. Chuti chun aman asopi ho chu nunnem tah in alhamon kit un ahi.   
\s1 Joseph thi  
\p
\v 22 Chuti chun Joseph ahin asopi te ho jouse Egypt a acheng jing uvin ahi. Joseph chu atahsa kum jakhat le som alhing tan ahi.  
\v 23 Chuin Joseph in khang thum channa geiya Ephraim chilhah ho jong amun chujongleh Joseph thagui a peng Manasseh chapa Machir chate jong ana mupeh in ahi.   
\p
\v 24 Chuin Joseph in asopite jah a, “Keivang kathina ding anailam tai,” “ahivangin Pathen'in nangho nahungvil teiyun tin, Egypt gam a kon hin Abraham, Isaac chule Jacob henga ana kihahselna gama dingin nahin puitou vunte,” ati.  
\v 25 Hichun Joseph in Israel chate chu aki tepsah in chuin aman hitin aseiye, “Pathen'in nahin kithopiuva hiche mun'a konna nahung pui teng ule hiche mun'a konna kagu kachang \x + \xo 50:25 \xt Potdohbu 13:19; Joshua 24:32; Heb 11:22\x* ho hi na nungpoh teitei diu ahi,” ati.   
\p
\v 26 Hichun Joseph kum jakhat le kum som ahin ahinkho abeitai. Hichun Egypt miten Joseph longdamsa chu atom un athikong chu Egypt gamsunga thingkong sunga akoi tauve.   